hadiths[309]{hadithnumber,text}:
2782,"ham se Hasan-bin-Sabaah ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Muhammad-bin-Saabiq ne bayan kya, kaha ham se Maalik-bin-Mighwal ne bayan kya, kaha ke maine Waleed bin Eizaar se suna, unse Saeed bin Ayas abu-Amr Shebani ne bayan kya aur unse Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke Deen ke kaamon mein kon sa amal afzal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' waqt par Namaz padhnaa.'' maine puchha iske baad ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''waalidain ke sath nek sulook karnaa.'' maine puchha aur uske baad ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ke rastey mein jihad karnaa.'' phir maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada sawalat nahi kiye, warna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) isi tarah unke jawabaat inayat farmatey."
2783,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' fateh Makka ke baad ab hijrat ( farz ( nahi rahi albatta jihad aur niyat b-khair karna ab bhi baqi hain aur jab tumhen jihad ke liye bulaya jaey to nikal khadey hua karo.''
2784,(ummul-momeneen) ne ke unhon puchha ya Rasulullah! ham samajhtey hain ke jihad afzal aamaal mein se hai phir ham (auratein) bhi kyon na jihad karein? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''lekin sabse afzal jihad maqbool Haj hai jis mein gunah na hon.''
2785,"aik sahib (naam naa-maaloom) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey aur arz kya ke mujhey koi aisa amal bata dijiye jo sawab mein jihad ke barabar ho. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aisa koi amal mein nahi paata. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya tum itna kar saktey ho ke jab Mujahid (jihad ke liye) nikley to tum apni masjid mein aa kar barabar Namaz padhni shuru kar do aur (namaz padhtey raho aur darmyan mein) koi sustii aur kaahilii tumhen mehsus na ho, isi tarah rozey rakhney lago aur koi din baghair rozey ke na guzrey. un sahib ne arz kya bhala aisa kon kar sakta hai? Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Mujahid ka ghoda jab rassii mein bandhaa hua zameen ( par paon ( maarta hai to is par bhi uske liye nekiyan likhi jati hain."
2786,"arz kya gaya ya Rasulullah! kon shakhs sabse afzal hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''wo momin jo Allah ke rastey main apni jaan aur maal se jihad kare.'' sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha iske baad kaun? farmaya ''wo momin jo pahaad ki kisi ghaati mein rehna ikhtiyar karey, Allah Taala ka khof rakhta ho aur logon ko chhod kar apni burai se unko mehfooz rakhey.''"
2787,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke Allah ke rastey mein jihad karne waley ki misal . padhi. aur Allah Taala us shakhs ko khub janta hai jo ( Khuloos dil ke sath sirf Allah Taala ki raza ke liye) Allah ke rastey mein jihad karta hai. us shakhs ki si hai jo raat mein barabar Namaz padhta rahe aur din mein barabar rozey rakhta rahe aur Allah Taala ne apne rastey mein jihad karne waley ke liye uski zimme-dari ley li hai ke agar usey shahadat dega to usey be-hisaab-kitaab jannat mein dakhil karega ya phir zinda w salamat ( ghar ( sawab aur maale-ghanimat ke sath wapas karega."
2788,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif ley jaya kartey they (ye Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khala thin jo Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein thiin) aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif le gaey to unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein khana pesh kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar se juein nikalney lagiin, us waqt mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey, jab bedaar huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraa rahe they. umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya maine puchha ya Rasulullah ! kis baat par aap hans rahe hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat ke kuchh log mere samney is tarah pesh kiye gaey ke wo Allah ke rastey mein jang karne ke liye dariya ke beech mein sawar is tarah ja rahe hain jis tarah badshah takht par hotey hain ya jaisey badshah takhte-rawaan par Sawar hotey hain ye shak Ishaq rawi ko tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! aap dua farmaiye ke Allah mujhey bhi unhiin mein se kar de, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye dua farmai phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna sar rakh kar so gaey, us martaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey to muskuraa rahe they. maine puchha ya Rasulullah! kis baat par aap hans rahe hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya meri ummat ke kuchh log mere samney is tarah pesh kiye gaey ke wo Allah ki raah mein jang ke liye ja rahe hain pahley ki tarah , us martaba bhi farmaya unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya ya Rasulullah ! Allah se mere liye dua kijiye ke mujhey bhi unhein mein se kar de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke to sabse pehli fauj mein shamil hogi (jo pani ke rastey se jihad karegii) chunanche Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamane mein umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani ka safar kya phir jab samandar se bahar aaiin to unki sawari ne unhein nichey gira diya aur usi haadise mein unki maut ho gaee."
2789,"rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif ley jaya kartey they (ye Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki khala thin jo Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein thiin) aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif le gaey to unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein khana pesh kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar se juein nikalney lagiin, us waqt mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey, jab bedaar huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) muskuraa rahe they. umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya maine puchha ya Rasulullah ! kis baat par aap hans rahe hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke meri ummat ke kuchh log mere samney is tarah pesh kiye gaey ke wo Allah ke rastey mein jang karne ke liye dariya ke beech mein sawar is tarah ja rahe hain jis tarah badshah takht par hotey hain ya jaisey badshah takhte-rawaan par Sawar hotey hain ye shak Ishaq rawi ko tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya ya Rasulullah! aap dua farmaiye ke Allah mujhey bhi unhiin mein se kar de, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye dua farmai phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna sar rakh kar so gaey, us martaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey to muskuraa rahe they. maine puchha ya Rasulullah! kis baat par aap hans rahe hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya meri ummat ke kuchh log mere samney is tarah pesh kiye gaey ke wo Allah ki raah mein jang ke liye ja rahe hain pahley ki tarah , us martaba bhi farmaya unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine arz kya ya Rasulullah ! Allah se mere liye dua kijiye ke mujhey bhi unhein mein se kar de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke to sabse pehli fauj mein shamil hogi (jo pani ke rastey se jihad karegii) chunanche Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamane mein umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne pani ka safar kya phir jab samandar se bahar aaiin to unki sawari ne unhein nichey gira diya aur usi haadise mein unki maut ho gaii."
2790,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs Allah aur uske rasool par eman laey aur Namaz qaaim karey aur Ramazan ke rozey rakhey to Allah Taala par haq hai ke wo jannat mein dakhil karega chahe Allah ke rastey mein wo jihad karey ya usi jagah padaa rahe jahan paida hua tha. sahaba ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! kya ham logon ko uski bashaarat na de dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jannat mein so darjey hain jo Allah Taala ne apne rastey mein jihad karne walon ke liye taiyaar kiye hain, unke 2 darjon mein itna fasla hai jitna aasman w zameen mein hai. isliye jab Allah Taala se maangna ho to Firdaus maango kyonke wo jannat ka sabse darmyani hissey aur jannat ke sabse buland darjey par hai. Yahyaa-bin-Saaleh ne kaha ke main samajhta hun yun kaha ke iske uper parwardigar ka arsh hai aur wahin se jannat ki nehrein nikalti hain. Muhammad-bin-Fulaih ne apne walid se (aur uskey uper Rehman ka arsh) hi hai ki riwayat ki hai."
2791,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''maine raat mein 2 aadmi dekhey jo mere paas aaey phir wo mujhey lekar aik darakht par chadhey aur uske baad mujhey aik aisey makan mein le gaey jo bahut hi zyada khoobsurat aur bada pakeeza tha, aisa khoobsurat makan maine kabhi nahi dekha tha. un donon ne kaha ke ye ghar shaheedon ka hai.''"
2792,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ke rastey mein guzarney wali aik subah ya aik Sham (Syria) duniya se aur jo kuchh duniya mein hai sabse behtar hai.''
2793,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jannat mein aik (kamaan) hath jagah duniya ki un tamam chizon se behtar hai jin par suraj tuloo aur ghurub hota hai.'' aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ke rastey mein aik subah ya aik Sham (Syria) chalnaa un sab chizon se behtar hai jin par suraj tuloo aur ghurub hota hai.''
2794,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ke rastey mein guzarney wali aik subah w Sham duniya aur jo kuchh duniya mein hai sabse badh kar hai.''
2795,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''koii bhi Allah ka banda jo mar jaey aur Allah ke paas uski kuchh bhi neki jama ho wo phir duniya mein aana pasand nahi karta bhale hi uski saari duniya aur jo kuchh usmein hai sab kuchh mil jaey magar Shahid phir duniya mein aana chahta hai ke jab wo (Allah taala ke) yahan shahadat ki fazeelat ko dekhega to chaahega ke duniya mein dobara aaey aur phir qatl ho (Allah taala ke rastey mein) .
2796,"Allah ke rastey mein aik subah ya aik Sham bhi guzaar dena duniya aur jo kuchh usmein hai, sabse behtar hai aur kisi ke liye jannat mein aik hath ke barabar jagah bhi ya (raawii ko shuba hai) aik (qaid) jagah, (qaid) se murad kodaa hai, (duniya aur jo kuch usmein hai) se behtar hai aur agar jannat ki koi aurat zameen ki taraf jhank bhi ley to zameen w aasman apni tamam wusa'ton ke sath munawwar ho jayen aur khushbu se muattar ho jaaein. iske sar ka dupatta bhi duniya aur uski saari chizon se badh kar hai."
2797,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! agar musalmanon ke dilon mein us se ranj na hota ke main unko chhod kar jihad ke liye nikal jaun aur mujhey khud itni sawaariyaan muyassar nahi hain ke un sab ko sawar karke apne sath ley chalun to main kisi chhotey se chhotey aisey lashkar ke sath janey se bhi na ruktaa jo Allah ke rastey mein jang ke liye ja raha hota. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai! meri to aarzoo hai ke main Allah ke rastey mein qatl kya jaun, phir zinda kya jaun, phir qatl kya jaun aur phir zinda kya jaun phir qatl kya jaun aur phir zinda kya jaun aur phir qatl kar diya jaun."
2798,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khutba diya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''fauj ka jhanda ab Zaid ne apne hath mein liya aur wo Shahid kar diye gaey phir Jafar ne ley liya aur wo bhi Shahid kar diye gaey phir Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha ne ley liya aur wo bhi Shahid kar diye gaey aur ab kisi hidayat ka intizar kiye baghair Khaalid-bin-Waleed ne jhanda apne hath mein ley liya aur unke hath par Islami lashkar ko fateh huii.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aur hamein koi uski khushi bhi nahi thi ke ye log jo Shahid ho gaey hain hamarey paas zinda rahtey kyonke wo bahut aish w aaraam mein chaley gaey hain. Ayub ne bayan kya ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ''unhein koi uski khushi bhi nahi thi ke hamarey sath zinda rahtey, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aankhon se aansu jari they.''"
2799,"aik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere qareeb hi so gaey. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey to muskuraa rahe they, meine arz kya ke aap kis baat par hans rahe hain? farmaya meri ummat ke kuchh log mere samney pesh kiye gaey jo jang karne ke liye us bahte dariya par Sawar ho kar ja rahe they jaisey badshah takht par chadhtey hain. maine arz kya phir aap mere liye bhi dua kar dijiye ke Allah Taala mujhey bhi unhiin mein se bana de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye dua farmai. phir dobara Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey aur pahley hi ki tarah us martaba bhi kya ( bedaar hotey huey muskuraaey ( umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne pahley hi ki tarah us martaba bhi kaha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahi jawab diya. umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya aap dua kar dein ke Allah Taala mujhey bhi unhein mein se bana de to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum sabse pahley lashkar ke sath hogi chunanche wo apne shauhar Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath musalmanon ke sabse pahley behrii (paanii key) bedey mein Sharik huin Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamaney mein jang se laut'tey waqt jab Sham (Syria) ke saahil par lashkar utra to umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb aik sawari laai gaee taake is par Sawar ho jayen lekin janwar ne unhein gira diya aur usi mein unka intiqal ho gaya."
2800,"eik din Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere qareeb hi so gaey. phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey to muskuraa rahe they, meine arz kya ke aap kis baat par hans rahe hain? farmaya meri ummat ke kuchh log mere samney pesh kiye gaey jo jang karne ke liye us bahte dariya par Sawar ho kar ja rahe they jaisey badshah takht par chadhtey hain. maine arz kya phir aap mere liye bhi dua kar dijiye ke Allah Taala mujhey bhi unhiin mein se bana de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye dua farmai. phir dobara Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey aur pahley hi ki tarah us martaba bhi kya ( bedaar hotey huey muskuraaey ( umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne pahley hi ki tarah us martaba bhi kaha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne wahi jawab diya. umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya aap dua kar dein ke Allah Taala mujhey bhi unhein mein se bana de to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum sabse pahley lashkar ke sath hogi chunanche wo apne shauhar Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath musalmanon ke sabse pahley behrii (paanii key) bedey mein Sharik huin Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke zamaney mein jang se laut'tey waqt jab Sham (Syria) ke saahil par lashkar utra to umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb aik sawari laai gaee taake is par Sawar ho jayen lekin janwar ne unhein gira diya aur usi mein unka intiqal ho gayaa."
2801,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Sulaim ke 70 aadmi (jo qaari they) banu-Aamir ke yahan bhejey. jab ye sab hazraat ( Maoona kunwey par) pahunchey to mere maamun Haraam-bin-Milhaan (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, main ( banu-Sulaim ke yahan ( aagey jata hun agar mujhey unhon-ne is baat ka amn de diya ke main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baatein un tak pahunchaaun to behtar warna tum log mere qareeb to ho hii. chunanche wo unke yahan gaey aur unhon-ne amn bhi de diya. abhi wo qabeele ke logon ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki baatein suna hi rahe they ke qabila walon ne apne aik aadmi ( Aamir-bin-Tufail ( ko ishara kya aur us ne aap (Raziallahu anhu) ke jism par barchha pewast kar diya jo aarpaar ho gaya. us waqt unki zaban se nikla Allahu-akbar mein kaamyaab ho gaya Kaba ke rab ki qism ! iske baad qabeele waley haram (Raziallahu anhu) ke doosrey sathiyon ki taraf (jo 70 ki tadaad mein they) badhey aur sab ko qatl kar diya. albatta aik sahib jo ek hi taang se chal patey they, pahaad par chadh gaey. Hammam ( rawi hadis) ne bayan kya main samajhta hun ke aik aur unke sath (pahaad par chadhey they) ( Umar-bin Umayya zamrii) iske baad Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko khabar di ke aap ke sathi Allah Taala se ja miley hain to Allah khud bhi unse khush hai aur unhein bhi khush kar diya hai. iske baad ham (Qur'aan ki dusri aayaton ke sath ye aayat bhi) padhtey they ( tarjama) hamari qaum ke logon ko ye paigham pahuncha 2 ke ham apne rab se aa miley hain, to hamara rab khud bhi khush hai aur hamein bhi khush kar diya hai. iske baad ye aayat mansukh ho gaee, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chalis (40) din tak subah ki Namaz mein qabila Ra-al, zakwaan, banii-Lahiyaan aur bani Usba ke liye baddua ki thi jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nafarmani ki thi."
2802,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi ladai ke mauqe par maujood they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungli zakhmi ho gaee thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ungli se mukhaatab ho kar farmaya teri haqiqat aik zakhmi ungli ke siwa kya hai aur jo kuchh mila hai Allah ke rastey mein mila hai (Maulaanaa Waheeduz-zamaan marhoom ne tarjama yun kya hai) eik ungli hai teri hasti yahiitu Allah ki raah mein zakhmi huii
2803,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai jo shakhs bhi Allah ke rastey mein zakhmi hua aur Allah Taala khub janta hai ke uske rastey mein kon zakhmi hua hai, wo qiyamat ke din is tarah se aayega ke uske zakhmon se khoon bah raha hoga, rang to khoon jaisa hoga lekin usmein khushbu mashk jaisi hogii.''"
2804,"Hiraql ne unse kaha tha maine tum se puchha tha ke unke yani (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) ke sath tumhari ladaaiyon ka kya anjam rehta hai to tum ne bataya ke ladai dolon ki tarah hai, kabhi idhar kabhi udhar yani kabhi ladai ka anjam hamarey haq mein hota hai aur kabhi unke haq mein. anbiya ka bhi yahi haal hota hai ke unki aazmaish hoti rehti hai (kabhii fateh aur kabhi haar se) lekin anjam unhiin ke haq mein achchha hota hai."
2805,"mere chacha Anas-bin-Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) badr ki ladai mein hazir na ho sakey, isliye unhon-ne arz kya ya Rasulullah! main pehli ladai hi se ghayab raha jo aap ne mushrekeen ke khilaf ladii lekin agar ab Allah Taala ne mujhey mushrekeen ke khilaf kisi ladai mein haziri ka mauqa diya to Allah Taala dekh lega ke main kya karta hun. phir jab Uhud ki ladai ka mauqa aaya aur musalman bhag nikley to Anas-bin-Nazar ne kaha ke aey Allaah! jo kuchh musalmanon ne kya main us se ma'zirat karta hun aur jo kuchh un mushrekeen ne kya hai main us se bezaar hun. phir wo aagey badhey (mushrekeen ki taraf) to Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se saamnaa hua. unse Anas-bin-Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha aey Sa'd-bin-Muaaz! main to jannat mein jana chahta hun aur nazar (unke baap) ke rab ki qism mein jannat ki khushbu Uhud pahaad ke qareeb paata hun. Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ya Rasulullah (sl)! jo unhon-ne kar dikhaya uski mujh mein himmat na thi. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke iske baad jab Anas-bin-Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ham ne paya to talwaar neze aur teer ke taqriban assii zakhm unke jism par they wo Shahid ho chukey they mushrikon ne unke aaza kaat diye they aur koi shakhs unhein pehchan na saka tha, sirf unki behan ungliyon se unhein pehchan saki thin. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ham samajhtey hain (ya aap ne bajaey ( نرى ( ke) نظن ( kaha ( matlab aik hi hai ke ye aayat unke aur un jaisey momineen ke barey mein nazil hui thi ke من المؤمنين رجال صدقوا ما عاهدوا الله عليه‏''mominon mein kuchh wo log hain jinhoney apne us waadey ko sachcha kar dikhaya jo unhon-ne Allah Taala se kya tha.'' aakhir aayat tak."
2806,"Anas-bin-Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ki aik behan Rabe naam ke (Raziallahu anhu) ne kisi khatun ke aagey ke daant tod diye they, isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse qisaas leney ka hukm diya. Anas-bin-Nazar (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya ya Rasulullah! us zaat ki qism jisne aapko haq ke sath Nabi banaya hai) qisaas mein) unke daant na tootengey. chunanche muddaii taawaan leney par razi ho gaey aur qisaas ka khayal chhod diya, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah ke kuchh bandey hain ke agar wo Allah ka naam lekar qism kha lein to Allah khud unki qism poori kar deta hai."
2807,jab Quran Majeed ko aik musahaf ( kitabi ( ki sura mein jama kya janey laga to maine sura Ahzaab ki aik aayat nahi paai jiski Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se barabar aap ki tilawat kartey huey sunta raha tha jab maine usey talash kya to) sirf Khuzaima-bin-Saabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan wo aayat mujhey milii. ye Khuzaima (Raziallahu anhu) wahi hain jinki akeley ki gawahi ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 2 aadmiyon ki gawahi ke barabar qarar diya tha. wo aayat ye thii من المؤمنين رجال صدقوا ما عاهدوا الله عليه‏( sura Ahzaab : 23 ) ''mominon mein se kuchh mard aisey hain jinhoney wo baat sach kahi jis par unhon-ne Allah se ahad kya.''
2808,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aik sahib zirah pahney huey hazir huey aur arz kya ya Rasulullah! main pahley jang mein Sharik ho jaun ya pahley Islam laaun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya pahley Islam lao phir jang mein Sharik honaa. chunanche wo pahley Islam laey aur uske baad jang mein Shahid huey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke amal kam kya lekin ajr bahut paya.
2809,"umme-Rabee'-bint-Baraa (Raziallahu anhu) jo Haarisa-bin-Suraaqa (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida thin, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur arz kya, aey Allah ke Nabi ! Harisa ke barey mein bhi aap mujhey kuchh bataein . Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) badr ki ladai mein Shahid ho gaey they, unhein naa-maaloom samt se aik teer aa kar laga tha. ke agar wo jannat mein hai to sabr kar loon aur agar kahin aur hai to uske liye ro'oon-dho'oon. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aey umme-Haarisa! jannat ke bahut se darjey hain aur tumharey betey ko firdause-aa'laa mein jagah mili hai."
2810,"aik sahabi ( laahiq bin zameera ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke aik shakhs jang mein shirkat karta hai ghaneemat hasil karne ke liye, aik shakhs jang mein shirkat karta hai naam aur shohrat ke liye, aik shakhs jang mein shirkat karta hai taake uski bahaadurii ki dhaak baith jaey to unmein se Allah ke rastey mein kon ladtaa hai? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs us irade se jang mein Sharik hota hai ke Allah hi ka kalima buland rahe, sirf wahi Allah ke raaste mein ladtaa hai."
2811,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jis bandey ke bhi qadam Allah ke rastey mein ghubaar aalud ho gaey, unhein (jahannam ki) aag chhueyye naa-mumkin hai.''"
2812,"Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse aur (apne sahibzadey ( Ali-bin-Abdullaah se farmaya tum donon Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein jao aur unse hadison nabwi suno. chunanche ham hazir huey, us waqt abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) apne (razaaii) bhai ke sath baagh mein they aur baagh ko pani de rahe they, jab aap ne hamein dekha to ( hamarey paas ( tashrif laey aur (chaadar odh kar) gote mar kar baith gaey, iske baad bayan farmaya ham masjide-Nabawi ki iinetein ( hijrat nabwi ke baad masjid ki tameer ke liye) eik-eik karke dho rahe they lekin Ammar (Raziallahu anhu) 2-2 iinetein la rahe they, itney main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) udhar se guzrey aur unke sar se ghubaar ko saaf kya phir farmaya afsos ! Ammar ko aik baaghii jamat maaregii, ye to unhein Allah ki (itaa't ki) taraf dawat de raha hoga lekin wo usey jahannam ki taraf bula rahe hongey."
2813,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab jange-khandaq se ( farigh ho kar) wapas aaey aur hathiyar rakh kar ghusl karna chaha to Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) aaey, unka sar ghubaar se ata hua tha. Jibraeel (Alaihissalam) ne kaha aap ne hathiyar utaar diye, Allah ki qism maine to abhi tak hathiyar nahi utaarey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya to phir ab kahan ka irada hai? unhon-ne farmaya udhar aur banu-Quraiza ki taraf ishara kya. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne banu-Quraiza ke khilaf lashkar kashii ki."
2814,"As'haabe-Maoona kunwey (Raziallahu anhu) ko jin logon ne qatl kya tha un par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne tees din tak subah ki Namaz mein baddua ki thi. ye Ra'al, Zakwan aur Usba qabeelon ke log they jinhoney Allah aur uske rasool ki nafarmani ki thi. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke jo (70 qaari ( sahaba Maoona kunwey ke mauqe par Shahid kar diye gaey they, unke barey mein Quran ki ye aayat nazil hui thi jisey ham muddat tak padhtey rahe they baad mein aayat mansukh ho gaee thi (is aayat ka tarjama ye hai) ''hamaarii qaum ko pahuncha do ke ham apne rab se aa miley hain, hamara rab ham se razi hai aur ham us se razi hain.''"
2815,kuchh sahaba ne jange-Uhud ke din subah ke waqt sharab pi (raawii hadis) se puchha gaya kya isi din ke aakhiri hissey mein (unki shahadat hui) thi jis din unhon-ne sharab pi thi? to unhon-ne jawab diya ke hadis mein iska koi zikr nahi hai.
2816,"mere walid Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney laey gaey (Uhud ke mauqe par) aur kaafiron ne unke naak kaan kaat daley they, unki laash Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney rakhi gaee to maine aagey badh kar unka chehra kholnaa chaha lekin meri qaum ke logon ne mujhey mana kar diya phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne roney-peetney ki awaz suni (to malum farmaya ke kis ki awaz hai? ( logon ne bataya ke Amr ki ladki hain (shaheed ki bahan) ya Amr ki behan hain (shaheed ki chachii shak rawi ko tha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kyon ro rahi hain ya (aap ne farmaya ke) ro'ein nahi malaaika barabar un par apne paron ka saaya kiye huey hain. imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) kehtey hain ke maine sadqe se puchha kya hadis mein ye bhi hai ke (janaaza) uthaey janey tak to unhon-ne bataya ke Sufiyan ne kabhi-kabhi ye alfaz bhi hadis mein bayan kiye they."
2817,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya koi shakhs bhi aisa na hoga jo jannat mein dakhil honey ke baad duniya mein dobara aana pasand karey, chahe usey saari duniya mil jaey siwaey Shahid ke. uski ye tamanna hogi ke duniya mein dobara wapas ja kar das martaba aur qatl ho ( Allah ke rastey mein) kyonke wo shahadat ki izzat wahan dekhta hai."
2818,Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ne Umar-bin Ubaidullah ko likha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai yaqin jano jannat talwaaron ke saaey ke nichey hai. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Uwaisi ne ibne-abii-Zanaad ke waaste se ki unse Musa-bin-Aqba ne bayan kya.
2819,"unse Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Sulaimaan-bin-Daawood (Alaihissalam) ne farmaya aaj raat apni so ya ( rawi ko shak tha) ninyaanwe beeviyon ke paas jaaunga aur har biwi eik-eik shehsawaar janegi jo Allah Taala ke rastey mein jihad karengey. unke sathi ne kaha ke inshaAllah bhi keh lijiye lekin unhon-ne inshaAllah nahi kaha, chunanche sirf aik biwi haamla huin aur unke bhi aadha bachcha paida hua. us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki jaan hai agar Sulaiman (Alaihissalam) us waqt inshaAllah keh letey to (tamaam beeviyan haamla hotiin aur) sab ke yahan aisey shehsawaar bachchey paida hotey jo Allah ke rastey mein jihad kartey."
2820,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sabse zyada Husain (khoobsoorat) sabse zyada bahaadur aur sabse zyada fayyaaz they, Madina tayeba ke tamam log (eik raat) khof-zada they (aawaaz sunai di thi aur sab log uski taraf badh rahe they) lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt aik ghodey par Sawar sabse aagey they (jab wapas huey to) farmaya us ghodey ko (daudney mein) ham ne samandar paya."
2821,"wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath chal rahe they, aap ke sath aur bahut se sahaba bhi they. wadi Hunain se wapas tashrif la rahe they ke kuchh (baddoo) log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se lipat gaey. bil-aakhir aapko majbooran aik babool ke darakht ke paas jana padaa. wahan aap ki chadar Mubarak babool ke kaantey mein ulajh gaee to un logon ne usey ley liya (taake jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein kuchh inayat farmaein to chadar wapas karein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan khadey ho gaey aur farmaya meri chadar mujhey de do, agar mere paas darakht ke kaanton jitney bhi oont bakriyan hotiin to main tum mein taqseem kar detaa, mujhey tum kanjoos nahi paogey aur na jhoota aur na buzdil paogey"
2822,"Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) apne bachchon ko ye kalimaat dua'aiya is tarah sikhatey they jaisey muallim bachchon ko likhnaa sikhaataa hai aur farmatey they اللهم إني أعوذ بك من الجبن ، Mina padhi. وأعوذ بك أن أرد إلى أرذل العمر ، Mina padhi. وأعوذ بك من فتنة الدنيا ، Mina padhi. وأعوذ بك من عذاب القبر''aey Allaah! buzdili se main teri panah mangta hun, us se teri panah mangta hun ke umr ke sabse zaleel hissey (budhaapey) main pahuncha diya jaun aur teri panah mangta hun main duniya ke fitnon se aur teri panah mangta hun qabr ke azab se.'' phir maine ye hadis jab Musab-bin-Sad se bayan ki to unhon-ne bhi uski tasdeeq ki."
2823,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farmaya kartey they ''aey Allaah! main teri panah mangta hun aajizii aur sustii se, buzdili aur budhapey ki zaleel hudood mein pahunch janey se aur main teri panah mangta hun zindagi aur maut ke fitnon se aur main teri panah mangta hun qabr ke azab se.''"
2824,"main Tal'ha-bin-Ubaidullaah, Sa'd-bin-abii-Waqaas, Miqdaad-bin Aswad aur Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki sohbat mein betha hun lekin maine kisi ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis bayan kartey nahi suna. albatta Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke wo Uhud ki jang ke mutaalliq bayan kya kartey they."
2825,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke din farmaya tha Makka fateh honey ke baad (ab Makka se Madina ke liye) hijrat baqi nahi hai, lekin Khuloos niyat ke sath jihad ab bhi baqi hai isliye tumhen jihad ke liye bulaya jaey to nikal khadey ho."
2826,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(qiyaamat ke din) Allah Taala aisey 2 aadmiyon par hans dega ke unmein se aik ne doosrey ko qatl kya tha aur phir bhi donon jannat mein dakhil ho gaey. pahlaa wo jisne Allah ke rastey mein jihad kya wo Shahid ho gaya, iske baad Allah Taala ne qaatil ko tauba ki taufeeq di aur wo bhi Allah ki raah mein Shahid hua. is tarah donon qaatil w maqtool bil-aakhir jannat mein dakhil ho gaey. ''"
2827,"mein jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaibar mein thahrey huey they aur khaibar fateh ho chuka tha, maine arz kya ya Rasulullah ! mera bhi (maal ghaneemat mein) hissey lagaaiye . Saeed-bin-al-Aas ke aik ladkey ( Aban bin Saeed (Raziallahu anhu)) ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! unka hissey na lagaaiye . is par Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) boley ke ye shakhs to ibne-qotal (Naumaan bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu)) ka qaatil hai. Aban bin Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha kitni ajeeb baat hai ke ye janwar (yani Abu-Hurera abhi to pahaad ki choti se bakriyan charaatey charaatey yahan aa gaya hai aur aik musalman ke qatl ka mujh par ilzam lagata hai. usko ye khabar nahi ke jisey Allah Taala ne mere hathon se ( shahadat ( izzat di aur mujhey uske hathon se zaleel honey se bacha liya (agar us waqt main maara jata ( to dozakhi hota, anbasaa ne bayan kya ke ab mujhey ye nahi malum ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unka bhi hissey lagaya ya nahi. Sufiyan ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujh se saeedii ne apne dada ke waastey se bayan kya aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke saeedii se murad Amr-bin-Yahyaa-bin-Saeed-bin-Amr-bin-Saeed-bin-Aas hain."
2828,abu-Talha Zaid-bin Suhel (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein jihad mein shirkat ke khayal se ( nafli rozey nahi rakhtey they lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat ke baad phir maine unhein eidul-fitr aur eidul-Azha ke siwa rozey ke baghair nahi dekha.
2829,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Shahid panch qism ke hotey hain. taaoon mein halaak honey waalaa, pet ki bimari mein halaak honey waalaa, doob kar marney waalaa, dab kar mar janey wala aur Allah ke rastey mein shahadat paaney waalaa.''"
2830,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' taaoon ki maut har musalman ke liye shahadat ka darja rakhti hai.''
2831,"jab aayat لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنينnaazil hui to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Zaid-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) (jo kaatibe-wahi they) ko bulaayaa, aap aik chaudii haddi sath lekar hazir huey aur us aayat ko likha aur ibn-Umme-Maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) ne jab apne naa-beenaa honey ki shikayat ki to aayat yun nazil huii لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين غير أولي الضرر"
2832,"mein Marwaan-bin-Hakam (khaleefa aur us waqt ke ameere-Madeena) ko masjide-Nabawi mein baithey huey dekha to unke qareeb gaya aur pahlu mein baith gaya aur phir unhon-ne hamein khabar di ke Zaid-bin-Saabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khabar di thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse aayat likhwaaii لا يستوي القاعدون من المؤمنين والمجاهدون في سبيل الله unhon-ne bayan kya phir Abdullaah-ibne-maktoom (Raziallahu anhu) aaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt mujh se ye aayat likhwaa rahe they, unhon-ne kaha ya Rasulullah ! agar mujh mein jihad ki taqat hoti to main jihad mein Sharik hota. wo naa-beenaa they, is par Allah tabarak taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil ki. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raan meri raan par thi maine aap par wahi ki shiddat ki wjah se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki raan ka itna bojh mehsus kya ke mujhey dar ho gaya ke kahin meri raan phat na jaey. iske baad wo kaifiyat Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se khatm ho gaee aur izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah ne faqat (غير أولي الضرر) nazil farmaayaa."
2833,Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Umar-bin Ubaidullah ko) likha to maine wo tahreer padhi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai jab tumhari kuffaar se mudbhed ho to sabr se kaam lo.
2834,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maidaane-khandaq ki taraf tashrif le gaey (Khandaq ki jang ke shuru honey se kuchh pahley jab khandaq ki khudaaii ho rahi thi) , aap ne dekha ke muhajireen aur Ansar (Raziallahu anhu) sardi ki sakhti ke bawajud subah hi subah khandaq khodney mein masroof hain, unke paas ghulam bhi nahi they jo unki us khudaaii mein madad kartey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki thakan aur bhook ko dekha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai ''aey Allah ! zindagi to to aakhirat hi ki zindagi hai to Ansar aur muhajireen ki maghfirat farmaa!'' yani dar-haqiqat jo maza hai aakhirat ka hai maza. bakhsh de Ansar aur pardesiyon ko aey Allaah. sahaba ne iske jawab mein kaha ''ham wo hain jinhoney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath par us waqt tak jihad karne ka ahad kya hai jab tak hamari jaan mein jaan hai.'' apne paighambar Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye bait ham ne ki jab tak hai zindagii. ladtey rahengey ham sadaa ."
2835,"(jab tamam Arab ke Madina Munawra par hamla ka khatrah hua to) Madina ke ird-gird muhajireen w Ansar khandaq khodney mein mashghool ho gaey, mitti apni pusht par laad laad kar uthatey aur (ye rajzia ash'aar) padhtey jatey ''ham wo hain jinhoney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hath par us waqt tak jihad ke liye bait ki hai jab tak hamari jaan mein jaan hai.'' Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas rajz ke jawab mein ye dua farmatey ''aey Allah ! aakhirat ki khair ke siwa aur koi khair nahi, to to Ansar aur muhajireen ko barkat ata farmaa."
2836,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( khandaq khodtey huey mitti ( utha rahe they aur farma rahe they ke '' (aey Allah ! ( agar to na hota to hamein hidayat naseeb na hotii.'' yani to hidayat deney wala na hota to na miltii ham ko raah.
2837,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jange-Ehzaab ( khandaq (ke mauqe par dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mitti ( khandaq khodney ki wjah se jo nikalti thi) khud dho rahe they. mitti se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pet ki safedi chhup gaee thi aur ye sher keh rahe they لولا أنت ما اهتدينا wla تصدقنا wla صلينا‏ . Mina فأنزل السكينة علينا وثبت الأقدام إن لاقينا‏ . Mina إن الألى قد بغوا علينا إذا أرادوا فتنة أبينا''aey Allah agar to na hota to ham hidayat na patey aur ham na sadqa detey, aur na Namaz padhtey, to to ham par sakeenat nazil farma, aur jab ham dushman se muqaabla karein, to hamein Sabit qadam rakh, be-shak un logon ne ham par zulm kya hai, jab ye koi fasaad karna chahtey hain to ham unki baat mein nahi aatey.''"
2838,ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sath jange-Tabook se wapas huey.
2839,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik jang ( Tabook ( par they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke kuchh log Madina mein hamarey peechhey reh gaey hain lekin ham kisi bhi ghaati ya wadi mein (jihad ke liye) chalein wo sawab mein hamarey sath hain ke wo sirf uzr ki wjah se hamarey sath nahi aa sakey aur Musa ne bayan kya ke ham se Hammad ne bayan kya, unse Humaid ne, unse Moosaa-bin-Anas ne aur unse unke walid ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( farmatey hain ke pehli sanad zyada sahi hai."
2840,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they ke jisne Allah Taala ke rastey mein (jihad kartey huey) aik din bhi roza rakha Allah Taala usey jahannam se 70 saal ki masafat ki doori tak door kar dega."
2841,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jis shakhs ne Allah ke rastey mein aik joda (kisi cheez ka ( kharch kya to usey jannat ke darogha bulaaengey. jannat ke har darwazey ka darogha (apni taraf) bulaaeyga ke aey fulaan! us darwazey se aa, is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) boley. ya Rasulullah ! phir us shakhs ko koi khof nahi rahega. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya mujhey ummeed hai ke tum bhi unhein mein se hogey ."
2842,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) member par tashrif laey aur farmaya mere baad tum par duniya ki jo barkatein khol di jaaeingii, main tumharey barey mein unse dar raha hun ke (kahiin tum unmein mubtala na ho jaao) iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne duniya ki rangeeniyon ka zikr farmaya, pahley duniya ki barkaat ka zikr kya phir uski rangeeniyon ko bayan farmaya, itney mein aik sahabi khadey huey aur arz kya ya Rasulullah! kya bhalaaii, burai paida kar degi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par thodi der ke liye khamosh ho gaey. ham ne samjha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par wahi nazil ho rahi hai. sab log khamosh ho gaey jaisey unke saron par parindey hun. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chehra Mubarak se paseena saaf kya aur malum farmaya sawal karne wala kahan hai? kya ye bhi (maal aur duniya ki barkaat) khair hai? teen martaba Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yahi jumla dohraya phir farmaya dekho bahaar ke mausam mein jab harii ghaas paida hoti hai, wo janwar ko mar dalti hai ya marney ke qareeb kar deti hai magar wo janwar bach jata hai jo harii harii doob chartaa hai, kokhein bhartey hi suraj ke samney ja khada hota hai. leed, gobar, peshab karta hai phir uske Hazam ho janey ke baad aur chartaa hai, isi tarah ye maal bhi haraa bharaa aur sheereen hai aur musalman ka wo maal kitna umda hai jisey usne halal tariqon se jama kya ho aur phir usey Allah ke rastey mein (jihad ke liye) yatimon ke liye miskinon ke liye waqf kar diya ho lekin jo shakhs naajaaiz tariqon se jama karta hai to wo aik aisa khaney wala hai jo kabhi aasooda nahi hota aur wo maal qiyamat ke din uske khilaf gawah bin kar aayega."
2843,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jis shakhs ne Allah ke rastey mein jang karne waley ko saaz w saman diya to wo ( maano ( khud jang mein Sharik hua aur jisne khair khwaahaana tariqa par ghaazii ke ghar baar ki nigrani ki to wo ( maano ( khud jang mein Sharik hua.
2844,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina main apni beeviyon ke siwa aur kisi ke ghar nahi jaya kartey they magar Umme-Sulaim ke paas jatey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jab iske mutaalliq puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujhey is par raham aata hai, uska bhai (Haraam-bin-Milhaan) mere kaam mein Shahid kar diya gaya."
2845,"Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) Saabit-bin-Qais (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey, unhon-ne apni raan khol rakhi thi aur khushbu laga rahe they. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha chacha ! ab tak aap jang mein kyon tashrif nahi laaey? unhon-ne jawab diya ke betey abhi aata hun aur wo phir khushbu lagaaney lagey phir (kafan pahan kar tashrif laey aur baith gaey) murad saf mein shirkat se hai) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne guftgu kartey huey musalmanon ki taraf se kuchh kamzori ke aasaar ka zikr kya to unhon-ne farmaya ke hamarey samney se hat jao taake ham kaafiron se aamney-saamney ladein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ham aisa kabhi nahi kartey they. (yani pehli saf ke log dat kar ladtey they kamzori ka hargiz muzaahira nahi honey detey they) tum ne apne dushmanon ko bahut buri cheez ka aadi bana diya hai (tum jang ke mauqe par peechhey hat gaey ( wo hamla karne lagey. us hadis ko Hammad ne Sabit se aur unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat kya."
2846,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-khandaq ke din farmaya dushman ke lashkar ki khabar mere paas kon la sakta hai? ( dushman se murad yahan banu-Quraiza they) Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dobara phir puchha dushman ke lashkar ki khabrein kon la sakega ? us martaba bhi Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke main. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke har Nabi ke hawaarii ( sachey madadgaar ( hotey hain aur mere hawaarii ( Zuber ( hain.
2847,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba ko) bani Qureza ki taraf khabar laney ke liye) dawat di. sadqa (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ke ustaad) ne kaha ke mera khayal hai ye Khandaq ki jang ka waqia hai. to Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne is par labbaik kaha phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bulaya aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne labbaik kaha phir teesri baar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bulaya aur us martaba bhi Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne labbaik kaha, is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya har Nabi ke hawaarii hotey hain aur mere hawaarii Zubair-bin-Awaam hain."
2848,"jab ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke yahan se watan ke liye wapas lautey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ham se farmaya aik main tha aur doosrey mere saathii, (har Namaz ke waqt) azan pukaarnaa aur iqamat kehna aur tum donon mein jo bada ho wo Namaz padhaaey."
2849,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat tak ghodey ki peshani ke sath khair w barkat waabastaa rahegi (kyonke us se jihad mein kaam liya jata rahega).''
2850,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat tak ghodey ki peshani ke sath khair w barkat bandhi rahegi .'' Sulaiman ne Shoba ke waaste se bayan kya ke unse Urwa bin abi-Jad (Raziallahu anhu) ne is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) (jis mein bajaey ibne-Ja'd ke ibne-abii-Ja'd hai) Musaddad ne Hushaim se ki, unse Husain ne, unse Shabi ne aur unse Urwa-ibn-abii-Ja'd ne."
2851,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ghodey ki peshani mein barkat bandhi hui hai.''
2852,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''khair-w-barkat qiyamat tak ghodey ki peshani ke sath bandhi rahegi yani aakhirat mein sawab aur duniya mein maale-ghanimat milta rahega.''
2853,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jis shakhs ne Allah Taala par eman ke sath aur uske wada sawab ko jantey huey Allah ke rastey mein (jihad ke liye) ghoda paalaa to us ghodey ka khaanaa, peenaa aur uska peshab w leed sab qiyamat ke din uski taraazu mein hoga aur sab par usko sawab milega.''"
2854,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par) nikley. abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) apne chand sathiyon ke sath peechhey reh gaey they. unke doosrey tamam sathi to ehram ki haalat mein they lekin unhon-ne khud ehram nahi baandha tha. unke sathiyon ne aik gorkhar dekha. abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ke is par nazar padney se pahley un hazraat ki nazar agarche is par padi thi lekin unhon-ne usey chhod diya tha lekin abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) usey dekhtey hi apne ghodey par Sawar huey, unke ghodey ka naam Jaraada tha, iske baad unhon-ne sathiyon se kaha ke koi unka kodaa utha kar unhein dedey (jisey liye baghair wo Sawar ho gaey they) un logon ne us se inkar kya ( mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) honey ki wjah se) isliye unhon-ne khud hi ley liya aur gorkhar par hamla karke uski koonchein kaat diin unhon-ne khud bhi uska gosht khaya aur doosrey sathiyon ne bhi khaya phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. jab ye log Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ho liye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne puchha ke kya iska gosht tumharey paas bacha hua baqi hai? abu-Qatada ne kaha ke haan, uski aik raan hamarey sath baqi hai. chunanche Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi wo gosht khaayaa. ghodey ka naam Jaraada tha, (is se baab ka matlab Sabit hua) ."
2855,hamarey baagh main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aik ghoda rehta tha jiska naam Luhaif tha.
2856,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jis gadhey par Sawar they, main is par aap ke peechhey betha hua tha. us gadhey ka naam Afeer tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aey Muaz ! kya tumhen malum hai ke Allah Taala ka haq apne bandon par kya hai? aur bandon ka haq Allah Taala par kya hai?'' maine arz kya Allah aur uske rasool hi zyada jantey hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ka haq apne bandon par ye hai ke uski ibadat karein aur uske sath kisi ko Sharik na thehraein aur bandon ka haq Allah Taala par ye hai ke jo banda Allah ke sath kisi ko Sharik na thahraataa ho Allah usey azab na de.'' maine kaha ya Rasulullah! kya main uski logon ko bashaarat na de dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''logon ko uski bashaarat na do warna wo khali bharosa kar baithengey. (aur nek aamaal se ghaafil ho jaaeinge).''"
2857,"(eik raat ( Madina mein kuchh khatrah sa mehsus hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamara ( abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka jo aap ke azeez they) ghoda mangwaayaa, ghodey ka naam mandoob tha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' khatrah to ham ne koi nahi dekha albatta us ghodey ko ham ne samandar paya hai.''"
2858,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha '' nahoosat sirf teen chizon mein hoti hai. ghodey mein, aurat main aur ghar mein.''"
2859,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' nahoosat agar hoti to wo ghodey , aurat aur makan mein hotii.''"
2860,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ghodey ke Malik teen tarah ke log hotey hain. kuchh logon ke liye wo baaise-ajr-w-sawaab hain, kuchh ke liye wo sirf parda hain aur kuchh ke liye wabaale-jaan hain. jiske liye ghoda ajr w sawab ka zariaa hai ye wo shakhs hai jo Allah ke rastey mein jihad ki niyat se usey paaltaa hai phir jahan khub charii hoti hai ya (ye farmaya ke) kisi shaadaab jagah uski rassii ko khub lambi karke baandhtaa hai (taake charon taraf char sakey) to ghoda uski charii ki jagah se ya us shaadaab jagah se apni rassii mein bandhaa hua jo kuchh bhi khata peetaa hai Malik ko uski wjah se nekiyan miltii hain aur agar wo ghoda apni rassii tudaa kar aik chhalaang ya 2 chhalaang lagaey to uski leed aur uske qadmon ke nishaanon mein bhi Malik ke liye nekiyan hain aur agar wo ghoda nehar se guzrey aur is mein se pani pi ley to bhale hi Malik ne pani pilaaney ka irada na kya ho phir bhi us se usey nekiyan miltii hain, doosra shakhs wo hai jo ghodey ko fakhr, dukhaawey aur ahale-Islaam ki dushmanii mein baandhtaa hai to ye uske liye wabaale-jaan hai aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se gadhon ke mutaalliq puchha gaya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke mujh par us jaame aur munfarid aayat ke siwa unke mutaalliq aur kuchh nazil nahi hua ( فمن يعمل مثقال ذرة خيرا يره * ومن يعمل مثقال ذرة شرا يره‏ ( ''jo koi aik zarra barabar bhi neki karega iska badla paaeyga aur jo koi zarra barabar burai karega iska badla paaey ga.''"
2861,"mein Jabir-bin-Abdullah Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jo kuchh suna hai, unmein se mujh se bhi koi hadis bayan keejiye. unhon-ne bayan farmaya ke main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein tha. abu-Aqeel rawi ne kaha ke mujhey malum nahi (ye safar ( jihad ke liye tha ya Umra ke liye ( wapas hotey huey) jab (Madina Munawra ( dikhai dene laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya jo shakhs apne ghar jaldi jana chahey wo ja sakta hai. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir ham aagey badhey. main apne aik siyaahii maail surkh oont be-daagh par Sawar tha doosrey log mere peechhey reh gaey, main isi tarah chal raha tha ke oont ruk gaya (thak kar) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya Jaabir! apna oont thaam ley, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne kode se oont ko maaraa, oont kood kar chal nikla phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ye oont bechogey? maine kaha haan! jab Madina pahunchey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne ashaab ke sath masjide-Nabawi mein dakhil huey to main bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha aur ''balaat'' ke aik koney mein, maine oont ko baandh diya aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ye aap ka oont hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey aur oont ko ghumaaney lagey aur farmaya ke oont to hamara hi hai, iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chand auqiya sona mujhey dilwaayaa aur malum farmaya tum ko qeemat poori mil gaee. maine arz kya ji haan. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ab qeemat aur oont ( donon hi ( tumharey hain."
2862,Madina mein (eik raat ( kuchh khof aur ghabraahat hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ghoda maang liya. us ghodey ka naam '' mandoob '' tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) is par Sawar huey aur wapas aa kar farmaya ke khof ki to koi baat ham ne nahi dekhi albatta ye ghoda kya hai dariya hai!
2863,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (maale-ghaneemat se) ghodey ke 2 hissey lagaey they aur uske Malik ka aik hissa.
2864,"aik shakhs ne Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha kya Hunain ki ladai mein aap log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko chhod kar chaley gaey they? Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha haan lekin Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni jagah par Sabit qadam rahe. Hawazin ke log (jin se us ladai mein muqaabla tha) badey teerandaaz they, jab hamara unse saamnaa hua to shuru mein ham ne hamla karke unhein shikast de di, phir musalman maale-ghanimat par toot padey aur dushman ne teeron ki ham par barish shuru kar di phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni jagah se nahi hatey. maine dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne safaid khachchar par Sawar they, abu-Sufiyaan-bin-Haaris bin abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) uski lagaam thaamey huey they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye sher farma rahe they أنا النبي لا كذب أنا ابن عبد المطلب''main Nabi hun ismein jhoot ka koi dakhal nahi, main abdul-Muttalib ki aulad hoon.''"
2865,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jab apna pair rikaab mein daala aur ontni Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko lekar seedhi uth gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjid zul-Hulaifa ke paas labbaik kaha (ehraam baandhaa).
2866,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ghodey ki nangii peeth par jis par zeen nahi thi, Sawar ho kar sahaba se aagey nikal gaey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki gardan Mubarak mein talwaar latak rahi thi."
2867,"aik martaba (raat mein) ahal Madina ko dushman ka khatrah hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik ghodey ( mandoob ( par Sawar huey, ghoda sust raftaar tha ya ( rawi ne yun kaha ke) uski raftaar mein sustii thi, phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas huey to farmaya ke ham ne to tumharey us ghodey ko dariya paya (ye bada hi tez raftaar hai) chunanche iske baad koi ghoda us se aagey nahi nikal sakta tha."
2868,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne taiyaar kiye huey ghodon ki daud maqam hafiya se saniiyatul-wadaa' tak karaai thi aur jo ghodey taiyaar nahi kiye gaey they unki daud saniiyatul-wadaa' se masjid zuraiq tak karaai thi. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ghud daud mein Sharik honey walon mein main bhi tha. Abdullah ne bayan kya ke ham se Sufiyan ne bayan kya, kaha ke mujh se Ubaidullah ne bayan kya, unse Sufiyan Sory ne bayan kya ke hafiya se saniiyatul-wadaa' tak panch mail ka fasla hai aur saniiyatul-wadaa' se masjid bani zuraiq sirf aik mail ke faasley par hai."
2869,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un ghodon ki daud karaai thi jinhein taiyaar nahi kya gaya tha aur daud ki had saniiyatul-wadaa' se masjid bani zuraiq rakhi thi aur Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi usmein shirkat ki thi. abu-Adbullah ne kaha ke) أمدا ( ) hadis mein) had aur intihaa ke mana mein hai. ( Quran Majeed mein hai) ( فطال علیہم الامد ( yani '' phir un par lambi muddat guzar gaee ''jo usi mana mein hai.
2870,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un ghodon ki daud karaai jinhein taiyaar kya gaya tha. ye daud maqam hafiya se shuru karaai aur saniiyatul-wadaa' uski aakhiri had thi ( Abu-Ishaq rawi ne bayan kya ke) maine abu-Musa se puchha iska fasla kitna tha? to unhon-ne bataya ke chh ya saat (7) mail aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne un ghodon ki bhi daud karaai jinhein taiyaar nahi kya gaya tha. aisey ghodon ki daud saniiyatul-wadaa' se shuru hui aur had masjid bani zuraiq thi. maine puchha usmein kitna fasla tha? unhon-ne kaha ke taqriban aik meel. ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) bhi daud mein shirkat karne walon mein they.
2871,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ontni ka naam azbaa tha.
2872,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aik ontni thi jiska naam azbaa tha. koi ontni us se aagey nahi badhtii thi ya Humaid ne yun kaha wo peechhey reh janey ke qareeb na hoti phir aik dehati aik naujawaan aik qawii oont par Sawar ho kar aaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ontni se unka oont aagey nikal gaya. musalmanon par ye bada sakht guzra lekin jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko iska ilm hua to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Allah Taala bar-haq hai ke duniya mein jo cheez bhi buland hoti hai) kabhi kabhii ( usey wo giraataa bhi hai. Musa ne Hammad se uski riwayat tool ke sath ki hai, Hammad ne Sabit se, unhon-ne Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
2873,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (wafaat ke baad) siwa apne safaid khachchar ke, apne hathiyar aur us zameen ke jo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khairat kar di thi aur koi cheez nahi chhodi thi."
2874,unse aik shakhs ne puchha aey abu-Amaara! kya aap logon ne ( musalmanon ke lashkar ne) Hunain ki ladai mein peeth pher li thi? unhon-ne farmaya ke nahi Allah gawah hai Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne peeth nahi pherii thi albatta jald baaz log (maidaan se) bhag padey they (aur wo loot mein lag gaey they) qabila Hawazin ne un par teer barsaney shuru kar diye lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne safaid khachchar par Sawar they aur Abu-Sufiyan bin-Haaris uski lagaam thaamey huey they. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they أنا النبي لا كذب أنا ابن عبد المطلبmain Nabi hun jis mein jhoot ka koi dakhal nahi. mein abdul-Muttalib ki aulad hun.
2875,maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jihad ki ijazat chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tumhara jihad Haj hai. aur Abdullah-bin Waleed ne bayan kya ke ham se Sufiyan Sory ne bayan kya aur unse Muawiya ne yahi hadis naql ki.
2876,(is mein hai ke) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aap ki paak beeviyon ne jihad ki ijazat mangi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Haj bahut hi umda jihad hai.
2877,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) umme-Haraam binte-Milhaan ke yahan tashrif le gaey aur unke yahan takiya laga kar so gaey phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( uthey to ( muskuraa rahe they. umme-Haraam ne puchha ya Rasulullah ! aap kyon hans rahe they? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya ke meri ummat ke kuchh log Allah ke rastey mein (jihad ke liye) sabz samandar par Sawar ho rahe hain unki misal (duniyaa ya aakhirat mein) takht par baithey huey baadshaahon ki si hai. unhon-ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala se dua farma dijiye ke Allah mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki aey Allah ! unhein bhi un logon mein se kar de phir dobara Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) letey aur) uthey ( to muskuraa rahe they. unhon-ne us martaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se wahi sawal kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi pehli hi wjah bataaii. unhon-ne phir arz kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dua kar dijiye ke Allah Taala mujhey bhi unmein se kar de, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum sabse pahley lashkar mein Sharik hogi aur ye ke baad walon mein tumhari shirkat nahi hai. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir aap ne (umme-Haraam ne) Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath nikah kar liya aur binte-Qarz Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ke sath unhon-ne dariya ka safar kya. phir jab wapas huin aur apni sawari par chadhiin to usne unki gardan tod daalii. wo us sawari se gir gain aur (usi mein) unki maut hui."
2878,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) umme-Haraam binte-Milhaan ke yahan tashrif le gaey aur unke yahan takiya laga kar so gaey phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( uthey to ( muskuraa rahe they. umme-Haraam ne puchha ya Rasulullah ! aap kyon hans rahe they? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab diya ke meri ummat ke kuchh log Allah ke rastey mein (jihad ke liye) sabz samandar par Sawar ho rahe hain unki misal (duniyaa ya aakhirat mein) takht par baithey huey baadshaahon ki si hai. unhon-ne arz kya ya Rasulullah ! Allah Taala se dua farma dijiye ke Allah mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua ki aey Allah ! unhein bhi un logon mein se kar de phir dobara Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) letey aur) uthey ( to muskuraa rahe they. unhon-ne us martaba bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se wahi sawal kya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi pehli hi wjah bataaii. unhon-ne phir arz kya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) dua kar dijiye ke Allah Taala mujhey bhi unmein se kar de, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum sabse pahley lashkar mein Sharik hogi aur ye ke baad walon mein tumhari shirkat nahi hai. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir aap ne (umme-Haraam ne) Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath nikah kar liya aur binte-Qarz Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki biwi ke sath unhon-ne dariya ka safar kya. phir jab wapas huin aur apni sawari par chadhiin to usne unki gardan tod daalii. wo us sawari se gir gain aur (usi mein) unki maut huii."
2879,"un charon ne Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki ye hadis mujh se thodi thodi bayan ki. Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif ley jana chahtey (jihad ke liye) to apni beeviyon mein Qura daltey aur jiska naam nikal aata unhein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne sath ley jatey they. aik jang ke mauqe par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamarey darmyan Qura andazi ki to us martaba mera naam aaya aur main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath gaee, ye pardey ka hukm nazil honey ke baad ka waqia hai."
2880,"Uhud ki ladai ke mauqe par musalman Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas se juda ho gaey they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine Aaisha binte- abi-Bakr aur Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu)) Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ki walida ( ko dekha ke ye apne izaar sametey huey thin aur) tez chalney ki wjah se) pani ke mishkeezey chhalkaatii hui liye ja rahi thin aur abu-Ma'mar ke ilawa Ja'far-bin-mahraan ne bayan kya ke mishkeezey ko apni pusht par idhar se udhar jaldi jaldii liye phirtii thin aur qaum ko usmein se pani pilaatii thin, phir wapas aati thin aur mishkezon ko bhar kar ley jati thin aur qaum ko pani pilaatii thin, mein unke paon ki paazebein dekh raha tha."
2881,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Madina ki khawaateen mein kuchh chaadrein taqseem kin. aik nai chadar bach gaee to kuchh hazraat ne jo aap ke paas hi they kaha ya ameerul-momineen! ye chadar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki nawaasi ko de dijiye, jo aap ke ghar mein hain. unki murad (aap ki beewii) umme-kulsoom binte- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se thi lekin umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke umme-Saleet uski zyada mustahiq hain. ye umme-Saleet (Raziallahu anhu) un Ansari khawaateen mein se thin jinhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke aap Uhud ki ladai ke mauqe par hamarey liye mishkeezey (pani ke) utha kar laatii thin. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ( hadis mein) lafz ( تزفر (ka mana ye hai ke seetii thi."
2882,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (jang mein) Sharik hotey they, musalman faujiyon ko pani pilaatii thin zakhmiyon ki marham patti karti thin aur jo log Shahid ho jatey unhein Madina utha kar laateen thin."
2883,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jihad mein Sharik hotiin thin Mujahid musalmanon ko pani pilaatiin, unki khidmat kartin aur zakhmiyon aur shaheedon ko utha kar Madina ley jaatiin thin."
2884,abu-Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghutney mein teer laga to main unke paas pahuncha. unhon-ne farmaya ke us teer ko kheench kar nikal lo maine kheench liya to us se khoon bahney laga phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko us haadise ki itlaa di to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unke liye) dua farmaaii اللهم اغفر لعبيد أبي عامر aey Allah ! Ubaid abu-Aamir ki maghfirat farmaa.
2885,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eik raat ( bedaarii mein guzaarii, Madina pahunchne ke baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kaash! mere ashaab mein se koi nek mard aisa hota jo raat bhar hamara pahra detaa!'' abhi yahi baatein ho rahi thin ke ham ne hathiyar ki jhankaar suni. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ''ye kon sahib hain?'' ( aaney waley ne) kaha, main hun Sa'd-bin-abii-Waqaas, aap ka pahra dene ke liye hazir hua hun. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khush huey. unke liye dua farmai aur aap so gaey."
2886,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ashrafii ka banda , rupye ka banda, chadar ka banda, kambal ka banda halaak hua ke agar usey kuchh de diya jaey tab to khush ho jata hai aur agar nahi diya jaey to naraz ho jata hai.'' us hadis ko Israel aur Muhammad-bin jihaada ne abu-Haseen se direct bayan nahi kya."
2887,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ashrafii ka banda aur rupye ka banda aur kambal ka banda tabah hua, agar usko kuchh diya jaey tab to khush jab na diya jaey to ghussa ho jaey, aisa shakhs tabah aur sar-nigoon hua. usko kaantaa lagey to Allah karey phir na nikley. mubaarakbaad ka mustahiq hai wo banda jo Allah ke rastey mein (jang ke mauqe par) apne ghodey ki lagaam thaamey huey hai, uske sar ke baal paraaganda hain aur uske qadam gard-w-ghubaar se atey huey hain, agar usey chaukii-pahrey par laga diya jaey to wo apne us kaam mein poori tan-dahi se laga rahe aur agar lashkar ke peechhey (dekh-bhaal ke liye) laga diya jaey to usmein bhi poori tan-dahi aur farz shanaasii se laga rahe. (bhaley hi zindagi mein ghurbat ki wjah se uski koi ahmiyat bhi na ho ke) agar wo kisi se mulaqat ki ijazat chahey to usey ijazat bhi na miley aur agar kisi ki sifarish karey to uski sifarish bhi qabool na ki jaey. abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Israel aur Muhammad-bin-Juhaada ne abu-Haseen se ye riwayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se direct nahi bayan ki hai aur kaha ke Quran Majeed mein jo lafz ( تعسا‏ ( aaya hai maano yun kehna chahiye ke) فأتعسهم الله‏ .) ( Allah unhein giraaey halaak karey)."
2888,"main Jareer-bin-Abdullaah bijli (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath tha to wo meri khidmat kartey they halanke umr mein wo mujh se badey they, Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine har waqt Ansar ko aik aisa kaam kartey dekha (rasoolullaah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat) ke jab unmein se koi mujhey milta hai to main uski ta'zeem w ikraam karta hun."
2889,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath khaibar (jang ke mauqe par) gaya, mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat kya karta tha, phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas huey aur Uhud pahaad dikhai diya to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye wo pahaad hai jis se ham mohabbat kartey hain aur wo ham se mohabbat karta hai. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath se Madina ki taraf ishara karke farmaya, aey Allah ! main iske donon pathreeley maidaanon ke darmyan ke khittey ko hurmat wala qarar deta hun, jis tarah Ibrahim ne Makka ko hurmat wala Shahar qarar diya tha, aey Allaah! hamarey saa aur hamarey mudd mein barkat ata farmaa."
2890,"ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (eik safar mein) they. kuchh sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) rozey se they aur kuchh ne roza nahi rakha tha. mausam garmi ka tha, ham mein zyada behtar saaya jo koi karta, apna kambal taan letaa. khair jo log rozey se they wo koi kaam na kar sakey they aur jin hazraat ne roza nahi rakha tha to unhon-ne hi oonton ko uthaya (paanii pilaayaa) aur roza daaron ki khub khoob khidmat bhi ki. aur (doosrey tamaam) kaam kiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''aaj ajr w sawab ko roza na rakhney waley loot kar ley gaey.''"
2891,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''rozaana insan ke har aik jod par sadqa lazim hai aur agar koi shakhs kisi ki sawari mein madad karey ke usko sahara de kar uski sawari par Sawar kara de ya uska saman is par utha kar rakh de to ye bhi sadqa hai. achchha aur paak lafz bhi (zabaan se nikaalnaa) sadqa hai. har qadam jo Namaz ke liye uthtaa hai wo bhi sadqa hai aur (kisi musaafir ko) rasta bata dena bhi sadqa hai.''
2892,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Allah ke rastey mein dushman se mili hui sarhad par aik din ka pahra (duniya aur jo kuch usmein hai) se badh kar hai jannat mein kisi ke liye aik kode jitni jagah (duniya aur jo kuch usmein hai) se badh kar hai aur jo shakhs Allah ke rastey mein Sham ko chaley ya subah ko to wo ( duniya aur jo kuch usmein hai) se behtar hai.''
2893,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke apne bachchon mein se koi bachcha mere sath kar do jo khaibar ke ghazwey mein mere kaam kar diya karey, jabke main khaibar ka safar karun. abu-Talha apni sawari par apne peechhey bitha kar mujhey ( Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ko) le gaey, mein us waqt abhi ladka tha. baligh honey ke qareeb . jab bhi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kahin qiyam farmatey to main Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat karta. aksar main sunta ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye dua kartey. ( اللهم إني أعوذ بك من الهم والحزن والعجز والكسل والبخل والجبن وضلع الدين وغلبة الرجال ) ''aey Allaah! main teri panah mangta hun gham, aajizii, sustii, kanjoosii, buzdilii, qarz daari ke bojh aur zaalim ke apne uper ghalbe se, aakhir ham khaibar pahunchey aur jab Allah Taala ne khaibar ke qile' par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko fateh di to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney Safiya-bint-Huyi-bin akhtab (Raziallahu anhu) ke jamaal (zaahirii w baatinii) ka zikr kya gaya unka shauhar ( Yahudi ( ladai mein kaam aa gaya tha aur wo abhi dulhan hi thin (aur chunkey qabeele ke sardaar ki ladki thiin) isliye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (unka ikraam karne ke liye kaha) unhein apne liye pasand farma liya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unhein sath lekar wahan se chaley. jab ham sadaa-al-Sahbaa par pahunchey to wo haiz se paak huin, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse khilwat ki. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hees (khajoor, paneer aur ghi se taiyaar kya hua aik khaanaa) taiyaar kara kar aik chhotey se dastar-khaan par rakhwaayaa aur mujh se farmaya ke apne aas-paas ke logon ko dawat de-do aur yahi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka Sayeda Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath nikah ka walima tha. aakhir ham Madina ki taraf chaley, Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke maine dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ki wjah se apne peechhey (oont ke kohan ke ird-gird) apni chadar se parda kiye huey they (sawaarii par jab Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) sawar hotiin) to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne oont ke paas baith jatey aur apna ghutna khada rakhtey aur Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) apna paon Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ghutney par rakh kar Sawar ho jaatiin. is tarah ham chaltey rahe aur jab Madina Munawra ke qareeb pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Uhud pahaad ko dekha aur farmaya ye pahaad ham se mohabbat rakhta hai aur ham us se mohabbat rakhtey hain, iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina ki taraf nigaah uthai aur farmaya : aey Allaah! mein iske donon pathreeley maidaanon ke darmyan ke khittey ko hurmat wala qarar deta hun jis tarah Ibrahim ne Makka muazzama ko hurmat wala qarar diya tha aey Allaah! Madina ke logon ko unke mudd aur saa mein barkat diijiye!"
2894,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din unke ghar tashrif la kar qailula farmaya tha. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey to hans rahe they. unhon-ne puchha ya Rasulullah ! kis baat par aap hans rahe hain? farmaya mujhey apni ummat mein aik aisi qaum ko) khuwab mein dekh kar) khushi hui jo samandar main ( jang ke liye) is tarah ja rahe they jaisey badshah takht par baithey hun. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! Allah se dua kijiye ke mujhey bhi wo unmein se kar de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum bhi unmein se ho. iske baad phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey aur jab bedaar huey to phir hans rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us martaba bhi wahi baat bataaii. aisa 2 ya teen baar hua. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum sabse pahley lashkar ke sath hogi wo Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein thin aur wo unko (Islam ke sabse pahley behrii bedey ke saath) jang mein le gaey, waapsii mein sawar honey ke liye apni sawari se qareeb huin (sawaar hotey huey ya sawar honey ke baad) gir padiin jis se aap ki gardan toot gaee aur shahadat ki maut paaii."
2895,"nabii Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik din unke ghar tashrif la kar qailula farmaya tha. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey to hans rahe they. unhon-ne puchha ya Rasulullah ! kis baat par aap hans rahe hain? farmaya mujhey apni ummat mein aik aisi qaum ko) khuwab mein dekh kar) khushi hui jo samandar main ( jang ke liye) is tarah ja rahe they jaisey badshah takht par baithey hun. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah! Allah se dua kijiye ke mujhey bhi wo unmein se kar de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum bhi unmein se ho. iske baad phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) so gaey aur jab bedaar huey to phir hans rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us martaba bhi wahi baat bataaii. aisa 2 ya teen baar hua. maine kaha : aey Allah ke rasool! Allah Taala se dua kijiye ke mujhey bhi unmein se kar de. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum sabse pahley lashkar ke sath hogi wo Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ke nikah mein thin aur wo unko (Islam ke sabse pahley behrii bedey ke saath) jang mein le gaey, waapsii mein sawar honey ke liye apni sawari se qareeb huin (sawaar hotey huey ya sawar honey ke baad) gir padiin jis se aap ki gardan toot gaee aur shahadat ki maut paaii."
2896,Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ka khayal tha ke unhein doosrey bahut se sahaba par (apni maaldaarii aur bahaadurii ki wjah se) fazeelat hasil hai to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum log sirf apne kamzor ma'zoor logon ki duaon ke nateeje mein Allah ki taraf se madad pahunchaaey jatey ho aur un hi ki duaon se rizq diye jatey hain.
2897,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''eik zamana aisa aayega ke musalmanon ki fauj ki fauj jahan par hongi jin mein puchha jaeyga ke kya fauj mein koi aisey buzurg bhi hain jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sohbat uthai ho, kaha jaeyga ke yahan to unse fateh ki dua karaai jaeygi. phir aik aisa zamana aayega us waqt uski talash hogi ke koi aisey buzurg mil jayen jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ki sohbat uthai ho, (yani taaba'ii) aisey bhi buzurg mil jaeinge aur unse fateh ki dua karaai jaeygi iske baad aik aisa zamana aayega ke puchha jaeyga ke kya tum mein koi aisey buzurg hain jinhoney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba ke shagirdon ki sohbat uthai ho kaha jaeyga ke haan aur unse fateh ki dua karaai jaeygi. ''"
2898,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki (apne ashaab ke sath Uhuad ya khaibar ki ladai mein) mushrekeen se mudbhed hui aur jang chhid gaee, phir jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (us din ladai se farigh ho kar) apne padao ki taraf wapas huey aur mushrekeen apne padao ki taraf to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki fauj ke sath aik shakhs tha, ladai ladney mein unka ye haal tha ke mushrekeen ka koi aadmi bhi agar kisi taraf nazar aa jata to uska peechhaa karke wo shakhs apni talwaar se usey qatl kar deta. Sehal (Raziallahu anhu) ne iske mutaalliq kaha ke aaj jitni sargarmii ke sath falan shakhs lada hai, ham mein se koi bhi shakhs is tarah na lad saka. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke lekin wo shakhs dozakhi hai. musalmanon mein se aik shakhs ne (apne dil mein kaha achchha mein iska peechhaa karunga ( dekhun ( Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey kyon dozakhi farmaya hai) bayan kya ke wo uske saath-saath doosrey din ladai mein maujood raha, jab kabhi wo khada ho jata to ye bhi khada ho jata aur jab wo tez chalta to ye bhi iske sath tez chaltaa. bayan kya ke aakhir wo shakhs zakhmi ho gaya zakhm bada gehra tha. isliye us ne chaha ke maut jaldi aa jaey aur apni talwaar ka phal zameen par rakh kar uski dhaar ko seeney ke muqaabla mein kar liya aur talwaar par gir kar apni jaan de di. ab wo sahib Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur kehney lagey ke main gawahi deta hun ke aap Allah ke sachey rasool hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke kya baat huii? unhon-ne bayan kya ke wahi shakhs jiske mutaalliq aap ne farmaya tha ke wo dozakhi hai, sahaba kiram (Raziallahu anhu) par ye aap ka farman bada sakht guzra tha. maine unse kaha ke tum sab logon ki taraf se main iske mutaalliq tahqeeq karta hun. chunanche main iske peechhey ho liya. iske baad wo shakhs sakht zakhmi hua aur chaha ke jaldi maut aa jaey. isliye us ne apni talwaar ka phal zameen par rakh kar uski dhaar ko apne seeney ke muqabil kar liya aur is par gir kar khud jaan de di. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke aik aadmi zindagi bhar bazahir ahle-jannat ke se kaam karta hai halanke wo ahale-dozakh mein se hota hai aur aik aadmi bazahir ahale-dozakh ke kaam karta hai halanke wo ahle-jannat mein se hota hai."
2899,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka qabila banu-Aslam ke chand logon par guzar hua jo teer andazi ki mashq kar rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ismail (Alaihissalam) ke beto ! teer andazi karo ke tumharey buzurg dada Ismail (Alaihissalam) bhi teerandaaz they. haan ! teer andazi karo, mein bani falan (ibne-alwara' (Raziallahu anhu)) ki taraf hun. bayan kya, jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik fareeq ke sath ho gaey to (muqaabley mein hissey leney waale) doosrey aik fareeq ne hath rok liye. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kya baat pesh aaii, tum logon ne teer-andaazii band kyon kar dii? doosrey fareeq ne arz kya jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik fareeq ke sath ho gaey to bhala ham kis tarah muqaabla kar saktey hain. is par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya achchha teer andazi jari rakho main tum sab ke sath hun."
2900,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne badr ki ladai ke mauqe par jab ham Quraish ke muqable mein saf baandhey huey khadey ho gaey they aur wo hamarey muqable mein taiyaar they, farmaya ke agar (hamla kartey huey) Quraish tumharey qareeb aa jayen to tum log teer-andaazii shuru kar dena taake wo peechhey hatney par majbur hun."
2901,"Habsha ke kuchh log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney chhotey neze ka khel dikhla rahe they ke umr (Raziallahu anhu) aagey aur kankariyaan utha kar unhein unse maara . lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''Umar unhein khel dikhaaney do.'' Ali-bin madeenii ne ye bayan zyada kya ke ham se Abdur-Razzaq ne bayan kya, unhein Mamar ne khabar di ke masjid mein (ye sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) apne khel ka muzaahira kar rahe they)."
2902,abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) apni aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aad aik hi dhaal se kar rahe they aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) badey achchhey teerandaaz they. jab wo teer maartey to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sar utha kar dekhtey ke teer kahan ja kar gira hai.
2903,"jab Uhud ki ladai main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka khaud Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar par todaa gaya aur chehra khoon se san gaya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aagey ke daant Shahid ho gaey to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) dhaal mein bhar-bhar kar pani baar-baar la rahe they aur Fatima (Raziallahu anha) zakhm ko dho rahi thin. jab unhon-ne dekha ke khoon pani se aur zyada nikal raha hai to unhon-ne aik chatai jalaaii aur uski raakh ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zakhmon par laga diya, jisse khoon aana band ho gaya."
2904,banu-Nazeer ke baghaat wghaira un maalon mein se they jinko Allah Taala ne apne rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko baghair ladey de diya tha. musalmaanon ne unke hasil karne ke liye ghodey aur oont nahi daudaaey to ye maal khas taur se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hi ke they jin mein se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni paak beeviyon ko saalaana nafqa ke taur par bhi de detey they aur baqi hathiyar aur ghodon par kharch kartey they taake Allah ke rastey mein (jihad ke liye) har waqt taiyaarii rahe.
2905,Sad-bin-abi-Waqas (Raziallahu anhu) ke baad maine kisi ke mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se nahi suna ke aap ne khud ko un par sadqey kya ho. maine suna ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : ''teer barsaao ( Sad ( tum par mere maan-baap qurbaan hon.''
2906,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere yahan tashrif laey to 2 ladkiyan mere paas jang Buaas ke geet ga rahi thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bistar par let gaey aur chehra Mubarak dusri taraf kar liya iske baad Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) aagey aur aap ne mujhey daantaa ke ye shaitaanii gaanaa aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki maujoodgii mein! lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unki taraf mutwajjeh huey aur farmaya ke unhein gaaney do, phir jab Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) dusri taraf mutwajjeh ho gaey to maine un ladkiyon ko ishara kya aur wo chali gaiin."
2907,"eid ke din soodaan ke kuchh sahaba dhaal aur haraab ka khel dikhaa rahe they, ab ya maine khud Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hi farmaya ke tum bhi dekhnaa chahti ho? maine kaha ji haan. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey apne peechhey khada kar liya, mera chehra Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra par tha (is tarah mein peechhey pardey se khel ko b-khoobii dekh sakti thi) aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they : ''khoob banu-arfada!'' jab main thak gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''bas?'' maine kaha ji haan, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''to phir jaao.'' Ahmed ne bayan kya aur unse ibne-wahab ne (abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke aaney ke baad dusri taraf mutwajjeh ho janey ke liye lafz (amal) ke bajaey) (فلما غفل‏) naql kya hai. yani jab wo zara ghaafil ho gaey."
2908,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sabse zyada khoobsurat aur sabse zyada bahaadur they. aik raat Madina par (eik awaz sun kar) bada khof chhaa gaya tha, sab log us awaz ki taraf badhey lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sabse aagey they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hi waaqie ki tahqeeq ki. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik ghodey par Sawar they jiski pusht nangii thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki gardan se talwaar latak rahi thi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke daro mat. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham ne to ghodey ko samandar ki tarah tez paya hai ya ye farmaya ke ghoda jaisey samandar hai."
2909,"aik qaum (sahaaba (Raziallahu anhu)) ne bahut si futoohaat kiin aur unki talwaaron ki aaraaish soney chandi se nahi hui thi balke oont ki pusht ka chamda, seesaa aur loha unki talwaaron ke zewar they."
2910,"wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Najad ke aas-paas mein aik jang mein Sharik they. jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jihad se wapas huey to aap ke sath ye bhi wapas huey. rastey mein qailula ka waqt aik aisi wadi mein hua jis mein babool ke darakht kasrat se they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us wadi mein padao kya aur sahaba poori wadi main ( darakht ke saaey ke liye) phail gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi aik babool ke nichey qiyam farmaya aur apni talwaar darakht par latkaa di. ham sab so gaey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke pukarney ki awaz sunai di, dekha gaya to aik badwi Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usne ghafalat mein meri hi talwaar mujh par kheench li thi aur main soyaa hua tha, jab bedaar hua to nangii talwaar uske hath mein thi. usne kaha mujh se tumhen kon bachaaeyga? maine kaha ke Allaah! teen martaba (maine isi tarah kaha aur talwaar uske hath se chhoot kar gir gai) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dehati ko koi saza nahi di balke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baith gaey (phir wo khud mutassir ho kar Islam laayaa)."
2911,unse Uhud ki ladai main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zakhmi honey ke mutaalliq puchha gaya to unhon-ne batlaya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehra Mubarak par zakhm aaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aagey ke daant toot gaey they aur khud Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar Mubarak par toot gaee thi. (jis se sar par zakhm aaey they) Fatima (Raziallahu anha) khoon dho rahi thin aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) pani daal rahe they. jab Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne dekha ke khoon barabar badhtaa hi ja raha hai to unhon-ne aik chatai jalaaii aur uski raakh ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zakhmon par laga diya jis se khoon bahnaa band ho gaya.
2912,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (wafaat ke baad) apne hathiyar aik safaid khachchar aur aik zameen ka hissa jisey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) pahley hi sadqa kar chukey they ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi chhodi thi.
2913,"wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik ladai mein Sharik they. aik aisey jangal mein jahan babool ke darakht kasrat se they. qailula ka waqt ho gaya, tamam sahaba saaey ki talash mein (poorii wadi mein alag-alag darakhton ke neechey) phail gaey aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi aik darakht ke nichey qiyam farmaya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne talwaar (darakht ke taney se) latkaa di thi aur so gaey they. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bedaar huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik ajnabii maujood tha. us ajnabii ne kaha ke ab tumhen mujh se kon bachaaeyga? phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne awaz di aur jab sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us shakhs ne meri hi talwaar mujh par kheench li thi aur mujh se kehney laga tha ke ab tumhen mere hath se kon bacha sakega? maine kaha Allah (is par wo shakhs khud hi dehshat zada ho gaya) aur talwaar niyaam mein kar li, ab ye betha hua hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey koi saza nahi di thi."
2914,"aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they (suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par) Makka ke rastey mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne chand sathiyon ke sath jo ehram baandhey huey they, lashkar se peechhey reh gaey. khud Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne abhi ehram nahi baandha tha. phir unhon-ne aik gorkhar dekha aur apne ghodey par (shikaar karne ki niyat se) Sawar ho gaey, iske baad unhon-ne apne sathiyon se ( ehram baandhey huey they) kaha ke kodaa utha dein unhon-ne us se inkar kya, phir unhon-ne apna neza maanga uske deney se unhon-ne inkar kya, aakhir unhon-ne khud usey uthaya aur gorkhar par jhapat padey aur usey mar liya. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba mein se kuchh ne to us gorkhar ka gosht khaya aur kuchh ne uske khaney se (ehraam ke uzr ki bina par) inkar kya. phir jab ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey to iske mutaalliq masla poochha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ye to aik khaney ki cheez thi jo Allah ne tumhen ata ki. aur Zaid-bin-Aslam se riwayat hai ke unse Ata-bin-Yasar ne bayan kya aur unse abu-Qatada (Raziallahu anhu) ne gorkhar ke (shikaar se) mutaalliq abu-Nazar hi ki hadis ki tarah (albatta is riwayat mein ye zayed hai) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya ke iska kuchh bacha hua gosht abhi tumharey paas maujood hai?"
2915,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (badr ke din) dua farma rahe they, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik kheme mein tashrif farma they, ke aey Allaah! main terey ahad aur terey waadey ka waasta de kar faryaad karta hun. aey Allaah! agar to chahey to aaj ke baad teri ibadat na ki jaeygi. is par Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka hath pakad liya aur arz kya : bas kijiye aey Allah ke rasool! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne rab ke huzoor mein dua ki had kar di hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us waqt zirah pahney huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif laey to zaban par ye aayat thii سيهزم الجمع ويولون الدبر * بل الساعة موعدهم والساعة أدهى وأمر''jama'at ( mushrekeen ( jald hi shikast kha kar bhag jaeygi aur peeth dikhaana ikhtiyar karegi aur qiyamat ke din ka unse wada hai aur qiyamat ka din bada hi bhayanak aur talkh hoga.'' aur Wuhaib ne bayan kya, unse Khalid ne bayan kya ke badr ke din ka (ye waqia hai)."
2916,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki wafat hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki zirah aik Yahudi ke paas tees saa jo ke badley mein rahan rakhi hui thi aur Yala ne bayan kya ke ham se Aamash ne bayan kya ke lohey ki zirah ( thi) aur Mu-alla ne bayan kya, unse abdul-Wahid ne bayan kya, unse Aamash ne bayan kya ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne lohey ki aik zirah rahan rakhi thi."
2917,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kanjoos (jo zakat nahi detaa) aur zakat dene waley (daataa) ki misal 2 aadmiyon jaisi hai, donon lohey ke kurtey (zirah) pahney huey hain, donon ke hath gardan se bandhey huey hain zakat dene wala (daataa) jab bhi zakat ka irada karta hai to uska kurta itna kushaada ho jata hai ke zameen par chaltey mein ghisat'ta jata hai lekin jab kanjoos sadqe ka irada karta hai to uski zirah ka eik-eik halqa uske badan par tang ho jata hai aur is tarah sikud jata hai ke uske hath uski gardan se jud jatey hain.'' Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey suna ''phir kanjoos usey dheelaa karna chahta hai lekin wo dheelaa nahi hotaa.''"
2918,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) qazaey-hajat (zaroorat se farigh honey) ke liye tashrif ley gaey. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas huey to main pani lekar khidmat mein hazir hua, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) shaami jubba pahney huey they. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kulli ki aur naak mein pani daala aur apne chehre ko dhoya. iske baad (haath dhoney ke liye) aasteen chadhaaney ki koshish ki lekin aasteen tang thi isliye hathon ko nichey se nikala phir unhein dhoya aur sar ka masah kya aur donon mozon ka bhi masah kya."
2919,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf aur Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ko khaarish ke marz ki wjah se reshamii kurta pahnney ki ijazat de di thi, jawan donon ko laahiq ho gaee thi jo us marz mein faaydemand hai."
2920,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se juon ki shikayat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein reshamii kapdey ke istemal ki ijazat de di, phir maine jihad mein unhein reshamii kapda pahney huey dekha."
2921,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf aur Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) ko reshamii kapdey pahnney ki ijazat de di thi.
2922,"(Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne) rukhsat di thi ya (ye bayan kya ke) rukhsat di gaee thi, un donon hazraat ko khaarish ki wjah se jo unko laahiq ho gaee thi."
2923,"maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) shaaney ka gosht ( chhuri se) kaat kar kha rahe they, phir Namaz ke liye azan hui to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi lekin wuzu nahi kya. ham se abul-Yamaan ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko Shuaib ne khabar di aur unhein Zohri ne (is riwayat mein) ye zyadti bhi maujood hai ke (jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Namaz ke liye bulaey gaey to (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chhuri daal di."
2924,"wo Ubada-bin-Samit (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein hazir huey. aap ka qiyam saahile-Hims par apne hi aik makan mein tha aur aap ke sath (aap ki biwi ( umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) bhi thin. Umer ne bayan kya ke ham se umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke meri ummat ka sabse pahlaa lashkar jo dariyaaii safar karke jihad ke liye jaeyga, us ne (apne liye Allah Taala ki rehmat w maghfirat ( wajib kar li. umme-Haraam (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke maine kaha tha ya Rasulullah ! kya main bhi unke sath hongi ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke haan, tum bhi unke sath hogi. phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya sabse pahlaa lashkar meri ummat ka jo qaisar ( roomiyon ke badshah (ke Shahar ( Qustuntuniya ( par chadhai karega unki maghfirat hogi. maine kaha, main bhi unke sath hongi ya Rasulullah ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi."
2925,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(eik door aayega jab) tum yahudiyon se jang karogey. (aur wo shikast kha kar bhaagtey phirengey ( koi Yahudi agar patthar ke peechhey chhup jaeyga to wo patthar bhi bol uthega ke aey Allah ke bandey ! ye Yahudi mere peechhey chipa betha hai usey qatl kar daal.''
2926,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi jab tak Yahudi se tumhari jang na ho leygii aur wo patthar bhi us waqt ( Allah Taala ke hukm se) bol uthengey jiske peechhey Yahudi chipa hua hoga ke aey muslmaan! ye Yahudi meri aad lekar chipa hua hai isey qatl kar daalo.''
2927,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke qiyamat ki nishaniyon mein se hai ke tum aisi qaum se jang karogey jo baalon ki jootiyaan pahney hongey (ya unke baal bahut lambey hongey) aur qiyamat ki aik nishani ye hai ke un logon se ladogey jinke munh chaudey-chaudey hongey maano dhaalein hain chamda jamii hui (yani bahut motey munh waley hongey) .
2928,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim nahi hogi jab tak tum turkon se jang na kar logey, jinki aankhen chhoti hongii, chehrey surkh hongey, naak motii phailii hui hogi, unke chehrey aisey hongey jaisey tehband chamda lagi hui hoti hai aur qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim na hogi jab tak tum aik aisi qaum se jang na kar logey jinke jootey baal ke baney huey hongey.''"
2929,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qiyaamat us waqt tak qaaim nahi hogi jab tak tum aik aisi qaum se ladai na kar logey jinke jootey baalon ke hongey aur qiyamat us waqt tak qaaim nahi hogi jab tak tum aik aisi qaum se jang na kar logey jinke chehrey teh shuda dhaalon jaisey hongey.'' Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke usmein abu-Zinaad ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se ye zyada naql kya ke unki aankhen chhoti hongii, naak motii, chehrey aisey hongey jaisey teh-b-teh chamda lagi dhaal hoti hai."
2930,"abu-Amaara ! kya aap logon ne Hunain ki ladai mein faraar ikhtiyar kya tha? Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha nahi Allah ki qasam, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne pusht hargiz nahi pherii thi. albatta Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab mein jo naujawaan they be saro-saamaan jinke paas na zirah thi, na khaud aur koi hathiyar bhi nahi le gaey they, unhon-ne zaroor maidan chhod diya tha kyonke muqable mein Hawazin aur banu-nasar ke behtreen teerandaaz they ke kam hi unka koi teer khata jata. chunanche unhon-ne khub teer barsaey aur shayad hi koi nishana unka khata hua ho (is doran mein muslmaan) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aa kar jama ho gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne safaid khachchar par Sawar they aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chacherey bhai abu-Sufiyaan-bin-Haaris-ibn-abdul-Muttalib Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki sawari ki lagaam thaamey huey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sawari se utar kar Allah Taala se madad ki dua maangii. phir farmaya : أنا النبي لا كذب أنا ابن عبد المطلب''main Nabi hun usmein ghalat bayaanii ka koi shaayeba nahi, mein abdul-Muttalib ki aulad hoon.'' iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne ashaab ki) naey tareeqey par) saf bandi ki."
2931,jange-Ehzaab (khandaq (ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (mushrekeen ko) ye baddua di ke aey Allaah! unke gharon aur qabron ko aag se bhar de. unhon-ne ham ko salaatul-Wustaa (asr ki namaaz) nahi padhney di (ye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt farmaya) jab suraj ghurub ho chuka tha aur Asr ki Namaz qaza ho gaee thi.
2932,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (subah ki) dua'aey-qunoot mein (doosri rakaat ke rukoo ke baad) ye dua padhtey they للهم أنج سلمة بن هشام ، Mina padhi. اللهم أنج الوليد بن الوليد ، Mina padhi. اللهم أنج Ayash بن أبي ربيعة ، Mina padhi. اللهم أنج المستضعفين من المؤمنين ، Mina padhi. اللهم اشدد وطأتك على مضر ، Mina padhi. اللهم سنين كسني يوسف ''aey Allah Salma bin Hisham ko nijat de, Waleed-bin-Waleed ko nijat de, aey Allaah! Ayaash-bin-abii-Rabee'a ko nijat de, aey Allah ! tamam kamzor musalmanon ko nijat de. (jo Makka mein mushrekeen ki sakhtiyan jhel rahe hain) aey Allaah! Muzar par apna sakht azab nazil kar. aey Allah aisa qahat nazil kar jaisa Yusuf (Alaihissalam) ke zamane mein padaa thaa.''"
2933,"jange-Ehzaab ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dua ki thii اللهم منزل الكتاب سريع الحساب ، Mina padhi. اللهم اهزم الأحزاب ، Mina padhi. اللهم اهزمهم وزلزلهم ''aey Allaah! kitab ke nazil karne waley (qiyamat ke din) hisab badi tezi se leney waale, aey Allaah! mushrikon aur kuffaar ki jamaton ko (jo musalmanon ka isteesaal karne aai hain) shikast de. aey Allaah! unhein shikast de aur unhein jhanjhod kar rakh de.''"
2934,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Kaba ke saaey mein Namaz padh rahe they, abu-Jahal aur Quraish ke kuchh doosrey logon ne kaha ke oont ki ojhdii la kar kon un par daalega? Makka ke kinarey aik oont zabah hua tha (aur usi ki ojhdii laney ke waastey) un sab ne apne aadmi bhejey aur wo us oont ki ojhdii utha laey aur usey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke uper (namaz padhtey huey) daal diya. iske baad Fatima (Raziallahu anha) aaiin aur unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke uper se us gandagi ko hataayaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us waqt ye baddua ki اللهم عليك بقريش ، Mina padhi. اللهم عليك بقريش ، Mina padhi. اللهم عليك بقريش Mina padhi. . Mina لأبي جهل بن هشام ، Mina padhi. وعتبة بن ربيعة ، Mina padhi. وشيبة بن ربيعة ، Mina padhi. والوليد بن عتبة ، Mina padhi. وأبى بن خلف ، Mina padhi. وعقبة بن أبي معيط ''aey Allah ! Quraish ko pakad, aey Allah ! Quraish ko pakad , abu-Jahal bin Hisham , Utba-bin- Rabee , Sheba bin Rabee , Waleed bin Utba , Ubai-bin Khalaf aur Aqba bin abi mueet sab ko pakad ley.'' Abdullaah-bin-Mas'ood (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha chunanche maine un sab ko jange-badr mein badr ke kunein mein dekha ke sab ko qatl karke usmein daal diya gaya tha. Abu-Ishaq ne kaha ke main saatwen shakhs ka (jiske haq mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baddua ki thi naam) bhool gaya aur yoosuf-bin-abii-Is'haaq ne kaha ke unse Abu-Ishaq ne (Sufiyaan ki riwayat mein Ubai-bin-khalaf ki bajaey) Umayya-bin-Khalaf bayan kya aur Shoba ne kaha ke Umayya ya abi (shak ke sath hai) lekin sahi Umayya hai."
2935,kuchh Yahudi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaey aur kaha (Assaamu-alaik) (tum par maut aaey) maine un par laanat bhejii. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya baat huii?'' maine kaha kya unhon-ne abhi jo kaha tha aap ne nahi sunaa? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''kya aur tum ne nahi suna ke maine iska kya jawab diya (وعليكم) yani tum par bhi wahi aaey (yani maine koi bura lafz zaban se nahi nikala sirf unki baat un hi par lota di ).''
2936,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Rome (mojooda Itly) ke baadshaah) qaisar ko) khat ( likha jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye bhi likha tha ke agar tum ne (Islam ki dawat se) munh modaa to (apne gunah ke saath) un kaashtkaaron ka bhi gunah tum par padega (jin par tum hukmraanii kar rahe ho).
2937,Tufail-bin-Amr dosii (Raziallahu anhu) apne sathiyon ke sath Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke ya Rasulullah ! qabila dos ke log sarkashi par utar aaey hain aur Allah ka kalam sunney se inkar kartey hain. aap un par baddua kijiye ! kuchh sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke ab dos ke log barbad ho jaengey. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( اللهم اهد دوسا وائت بهم )''aey Allah ! dos ke logon ko hidayat de aur unhein (daayrae-Islaam mein) kheench laa.''
2938,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Rome ke badshah ko khat likhney ka irada kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha gaya ke wo log koi khat us waqt tak qabool nahi kartey jab tak is par muhr na ho, chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik chandi ki anguthi banwai. maano daste-mubaarak par uski safedi meri nazron ke samney hai. us anguthi par ''Muhammad rasoolullaah'' khuda hua tha."
2939,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna khat Kisraa ke paas bhejaa. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eilchii se) ye farmaya tha ke wo Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke khat ko Bahrain ke governer ko de diin, Bahrain ka governer usey Kisraa ke darbar mein pahuncha dega. jab Kisraa ne maktoob Mubarak padha to usey us ne phaad dala. mujhey yad hai ke Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne bayan kya tha ke phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par baddua ki thi ke wo bhi paara-paara ho jaey (chunaanche aisa hi hua)."
2940,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qaisar ko aik khat likha jis mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usey Islam ki dawat di thi. Dahiya Kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maktoob de kar bheja aur unhein hukm diya ke maktoob Basra ke governer ke hawale kar dein wo usey qaisar tak pahuncha dega. jab Faaris ki fauj (iske muqaabley mein) shikast kha kar peechhey hat gaee thi (aur iske mulk ke maqbooza ilaaqey wapas mil gaey they) to us inaam ke shukraane ke taur par jo Allah Taala ne (iska mulk usey wapas de kar) is par kya tha abhi qaisar teiswin se iiliyaa (baitul-maqdis) tak paidal chal kar aaya tha. jab uske paas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka naamaa Mubarak pahuncha aur uske samney padha gaya to usne kaha ke agar unki (Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki) qaum ka koi shakhs yahan ho to usey talash karke lao taake main us rasool ke mutaalliq us se kuchh sawalat karun.
2941,"Quraish ke aik qafley ke sath wo un dinon Sham (Syria) mein muqeem they. ye qaafila us daur mein yahan tijarat ki gharaz se aaya tha jis main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur kuffaare-Quraish mein aapasii suleh ho chuki thi. (Suleh Hudaibiya ( Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha ke qaisar ke aadmi ki ham se Sham (Syria) ke aik maqam par mulaqat hui aur wo mujhey aur mere sathiyon ko apne ( qaisar ke darbar mein baitul-maqdis ( lekar chala phir jab ham iiliyaa ( baitul-maqdis ( pahunchey to qaisar ke darbar mein hamein bulaya gaya. us waqt qaisar darbar mein betha hua tha. uske sar par taaj tha aur Rome (mojooda Itly) ke ameer uske aas-paas they, us ne apne tarjuman se kaha ke unse poochho ke jinhoney unke yahan nabwooat ka dawa kya hai nasb ke eitibaar se unse qareeb unmein se kon shakhs hai? Abu-Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke maine kaha, main nasb ke eitibaar se unke zyada qareeb hun. qaisar ne puchha tumhari aur unki qaraabat kya hai? maine kaha ( rishtey mein) wo mere chacha zaad bhai hotey hain, ittifaq tha ke us martaba qafley mein mere siwa bani abd munaaf ka aur aadmi maujood nahi tha. qaisar ne kaha ke us shakhs ( Abu-Sufiyan (Raziallahu anhu)) ko mujh se qareeb kar do aur jo log mere sath they uske hukm se mere peechhey qareeb mein khadey kar diye gaey. uske baad us ne apne tarjuman se kaha ke us shakhs (abu-Sufiyaan) ke sathiyon se keh do ke us se main un sahib ke barey mein poochhunga jo Nabi honey ke muddaii hain, agar ye unke barey mein koi jhoot baat kahey to tum fauran usko jhutlaa do. Abu-Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke Allah ki qism ! agar us din is baat ki sharm na hoti ke kahin mere sathi meri takzeeb na kar baithein to main un sawalat ke jawabaat mein zaroor jhoot bol jata jo usney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke barey mein kiye they, lekin mujhey to uska khatrah laga raha ke kahin mujhey jhutlaa na dein. isliye maine sachchai se kaam liya. iske baad us ne apne tarjuman se kaha us se poochho ke tum logon mein un sahib (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka nasb kaisa samjha jata hai? maine bataya ke ham mein unka nasb bahut umda samjha jata hai. us ne puchha achchha ye nabwooat ka dawa us se pahley bhi tumharey yahan kisi ne kya tha? maine kaha ke nahi. us ne puchha kya us da'we se pahley un par koi jhoot ka ilzam tha? maine kaha ke nahi, us ne puchha unke bap daadon mein koi badshah guzra hai? maine kaha nahi. us ne puchha to ab badey ameer log unki ittaba (pairvi) kartey hain ya kamzor aur kam haisiyat ke log ? maine kaha ke kamzor aur maamooli haisiyat ke log hi unke ( zyada tar manney waley hain) us ne puchha ke iske manney walon ki tadaad badhtii rehti hai ya ghat'tii ja rahi hai? maine kaha ji nahi tadaad barabar badhtii ja rahi hai. us ne puchha koi unke Deen se bezaar ho kar Islam laney ke baad phir bhi gaya hai kiya? maine kaha ke nahi, us ne puchha unhon-ne kabhi wada khilaafii bhi ki hai? maine kaha ke nahi lekin aaj kal hamara unse aik muaahida ho raha hai aur hamein unki taraf se muaahide ki khilaaf-warzii ka khatrah hai. Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha ke poori guftgu mein siwa iske aur koi aisa mauqa nahi mila jis mein main koi aisi baat mila sakun jis se Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki tauheen ho. aur apne sathiyon ki taraf se bhi jhutlaaney ka dar na ho. us ne phir puchha kya tum ne kabhi unse ladai ki hai ya unhon-ne tum se jang ki hai? maine kaha ke haan, us ne puchha tumhari ladai ka kya nateeja nikalta hai? maine kaha ladai mein hamesha kisi aik giroh ne fateh nahi hasil ki. kabhi wo hamein maghloob kar letey hain aur kabhi ham unhein, us ne puchha wo tumhen kin kaamon ka hukm detey hain? kaha hamein wo iska hukm detey hain ke ham sirf Allah ki ibadat karein aur iska kisi ko bhi Sharik na thehraein , hamein un buton ki ibadat se mana kartey hain jinki hamarey bap dada ibadat kya kartey they, Namaz , sadqa , paak bazi w marawwat, wafaa, ahad aur amanat ke ada karne ka hukm detey hain. jab main usey ye tamam baatein bata chuka to usne apne tarjuman se kaha, unse kaho ke maine tum se un (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke nasb ke mutaalliq malum kya to tum ne bataya ke wo tumharey yahan saahibe-nasb aur sharif samjhey jatey hain aur anbiya bhi yun hi apni qaum ke aalaa nasb mein paida kiye jatey hain. maine tum se ye puchha tha ke kya nabwooat ka dawa tumharey yahan us se pahley bhi kisi ne kya tha tum ne bataya ke hamarey yahan aisa dawa pahley kisi ne nahi kya tha, us se main ye samjha ke agar us se pahley tumharey yahan kisi ne nabwooat ka dawa kya hota to main ye bhi keh sakta tha ke ye sahib bhi usi da'we ki naql kar rahe hain jo us se pahley kya ja chuka hai. maine tum se malum kya ke kya tum ne dawa-e-nabwooat se pahley kabhi unki taraf jhoot mansub kya tha, tum ne bataya ke aisa kabhi nahi hua. us se main us nateejey par pahuncha ke ye mumkin nahi ke aik shakhs jo logon ke mutaalliq kabhi jhoot na bol saka ho wo Allah ke mutaalliq jhoot bol de. maine tum se malum kya ke unke bap daadon mein koi badshah tha, tum ne bataya ke nahi. maine us se ye faisla kya ke agar unke bap daadon mein koi badshah guzra hota to main ye bhi keh sakta tha ke) nabwooat ka dawa karke ( wo apne bap-dada ki saltanat hasil karna chahtey hain, maine tum se malum kya ke unki ittaba (pairvi) qaum ke badey log kartey hain ya kamzor aur be haisiyat log, tum ne bataya ke kamzor ghareeb qism ke log unki taabea'daarii kartey hain aur yahi giroh anbiya ki (har door mein) itaat karne wala raha hai. maine tum se puchha ke un taabea'daaron ki tadaad badhtii rehti hai ya ghat'tii bhi hai? tum ne bataya ke wo log barabar badh hi rahe hain, eman ka bhi yahi haal hai, yahan tak ke wo mukammal ho jaey, maine tum se malum kya ke kya koi shakhs unke Deen mein dakhil honey ke baad kabhi us se phir bhi gaya hai? tum ne kaha ke aisa kabhi nahi hua, eman ka bhi yahi haal hai jab wo dil ki gahraaiyon mein utar jaey to phir koi cheez us se momin ko hata nahi saktii. maine tum se malum kya ke kya unhon-ne wada khilaafii bhi ki hai? tum ne iska bhi jawab diya ke nahi, anbiya ki yahi shaan hai ke wo wada khilaafii kabhi nahi kartey. maine tum se malum kya ke kya tum ne kabhi unse ya unhon-ne tum se jang bhi ki hai? tum ne bataya ke aisa hua hai aur tumhari ladaaiyon ka nateeja hamesha kisi aik hi ke haq mein nahi gaya. balke kabhi tum maghloob huey ho aur kabhi wo. anbiya ke sath bhi aisa hi hota hai wo imtihaan mein daley jatey hain lekin anjam unhiin ka behtar hota hai. maine tum se malum kya ke wo tum ko kin kaamon ka hukm detey hain? tum ne bataya ke wo hamein iska hukm detey hain ke Allah ki ibadat karo aur uske sath kisi ko Sharik na thehrao aur tumhen tumharey un ma'boodon ki ibadat se mana kartey hain jinki tumharey bap dada ibadat kya kartey they. tumhen wo namaaz, sadqa, paak-baazii, wada wafaaii aur ada amanat ka hukm detey hain, usne kaha ke aik Nabi ki yahi sifat hai mere bhi ilm mein ye baat thi ke wo Nabi maboos hone-waale hain. lekin ye khayal na tha ke tum mein se wo maboos hongey, jo baatein tum ne bataein agar wo sahi hain to wo din bahut qareeb hai jab wo us jagah par hukmaraan hongey jahan us waqt mere donon qadam maujood hain, agar mujhey un tak pahunch sakney ki tawaqqoa' hoti to main unki khidmat mein hazir honey ki poori koshish karta aur agar main unki khidmat mein maujood hota to unke paon dhota . Abu-Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke iske baad qaisar ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka naamaa Mubarak talab kya aur wo uske samney padha gaya usmein likha hua tha ( tarjama ( shuru karta hun Allah ke naam se jo bada hi meharban bahut hi zyada raham karne wala hai. ye khat hai Muhammad Allah ke bandey aur uske rasool ki taraf se Rome (mojooda Itly) ke badshah Hiraql ki taraf, us shakhs par salamati ho jo hidayat qabool kar ley. ammaa baad (ammaa ba'd) main tumhen Islam ki dawat deta hun. Islam qabool karo, tumhen bhi salamati w amn hasil hogi aur Islam qabool karo Allah tumhen dohra ajr dega (eik tumharey apne Islam ka aur doosra tumhari qaum ke Islam ka jo tumhari wjah se Islam mein dakhil hogi) lekin agar tum ne us dawat se munh mod liya to tumhari riaya ka gunah bhi tum par hoga aur aey ahle-kitab! aik aisey kalime par aa kar ham se mil jao jo hamarey aur tumharey darmyan aik hi hai ye ke ham Allah ke siwa aur kisi ki ibadat na karein na iske sath kisi ko Sharik thehraein aur na ham mein se koi Allah ko chhod kar aapas mein aik doosrey ko parwardigar banaey ab bhi agar tum munh modtey ho to uska iqrar kar lo ke) Allah Taala ka waaqeii) farman bardaar ham hi hain. Abu-Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke jab Hiraql apni baat poori kar chuka to Rome ke sardaar uske ird-gird jama they, sab aik sath cheekhney lagey aur shor w ghul bahut badh gaya. mujhey kuchh pata nahi chala ke ye log kya keh rahe they. phir hamein hukm diya gaya aur ham wahan se nikal diye gaey. jab main apne sathiyon ke sath wahan se chala aaya aur unke sath tanhai hui to maine kaha ke ibne-abii-Kabsha (muraad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hai) ka mamla bahut aagey badh chuka hai, ''banu-al-Asfar'' (Roomiyon) ka badshah bhi us se darta hai, Abu-Sufiyan ne bayan kya ke Allah ki qasam! mujhey isi din se apni zillat ka yaqin ho gaya tha aur barabar is baat ka bhi yaqin raha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zaroor ghalib hongey, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ne mere dil mein bhi Islam dakhil kar diya. halanke (pahley ( mein Islam ko bura janta tha."
2942,"Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki ladai ke din farmaya tha ke Islami jhanda main aik aisey shakhs ke hath mein doonga jiske zariey Allah Taala fateh inayat farmaeyga. ab sab us intizar mein they ke dekhiye jhanda kisey milta hai, jab subah hui to sab sarkarda log isi ummeed mein rahe ke kash! unhein ko mil jaey lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya : Ali kahan hain? arz kya gaya ke wo aankhon ke dard mein mubtala hain, aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se unhein bulaya gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne munh ka luaab unki aankhon mein laga diya aur fauran hi wo achchhey ho gaey. jaisey pahley koi takleef hi na rahi ho. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ham un (yahoodiyon se) us waqt tak jang karengey jab tak ye hamarey jaisey ( musalman ( na ho jaaein. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : abhi thehro pahley unke maidan mein utar kar unhein tum Islam ki dawat de lo aur unke liye jo cheez zaroori hain unki khabar kar do ( phir wo na maanein to ladna ( Allah ki qism ! agar tumharey zariey aik shakhs ko bhi hidayat mil jaey to ye tumharey haq mein surkh oonton se behtar hai."
2943,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab kisi qaum par chadhai kartey to us waqt tak koi iqdaam na farmatey jab tak subah na ho jaatii, jab subah ho jati aur azan ki awaz sun letey to ruk jatey aur agar azan ki awaz sunai na deti to subah honey ke baad hamla kartey. chunanche khaibar mein bhi ham raat mein pahunchey they."
2944,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab hamarey sath mil kar jang kartey they.
2945,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) raat mein khaibar tashrif le gaey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aadat thi ke jab kisi qaum tak raat ke waqt pahunchtey to subah se pahley un par hamla nahi kartey they. jab subah hui to Yahudi apne phaawdey aur tokrey lekar bahar (kheton mein kaam karne ke liye) nikley. jab unhon-ne Islami lashkar ko dekha to cheekh padey Muhammad Allah ki qism Muhammad lashkar samet aa gaey. par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, Allah ki zaat sabse badi hai. ab khaibar to kharaab ho gaya ke jab ham kisi qaum ke maidan mein mujaahidaana utar aatey hain to (kufr se) daraaey huey logon ki subah manhoos ho jati hai."
2946,"mujhey hukm diya gaya hai ke main logon se us waqt tak jang karta rahoon yahan tak ke wo uska iqrar kar lein ke Allah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi, to jisne iqrar kar liya ke Allah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi to uski jaan aur maal ham se mehfooz hai, siwa us haq ke jiski bina par qaanoonan uski jaan w maal zad mein aaey aur uska hisab Allah ke zimme hai. uski riwayat umr aur ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ki hai."
2947,"mujhey Abdur-Rehman bin-abdullaah-bin-Ka'b-bin-Maalik ne khabar di aur unhein Abdullaah-bin-Ka'b (Raziallahu anhu) ne, Kab (Raziallahu anhu) (jab naa-beenaa ho gaey they) ke sath unke doosrey saahibzaadon mein yahi Abdullah unhein lekar rastey mein unke aagey-aagey chaltey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka usool ye tha ke jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi jang ka irada kartey to (maslihat ke liye) doosra maqam bayan kartey (taake dushman ko khabar na ho)."
2948,"aisa kam ittifaq hota ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi jihad ka irada karein aur wahi maqam bayan farma kar usko na chipaaein . jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-Tabook ko janey lagey to chunkey ye jang badi sakht garmi mein hona tha, lamba safar tha aur jangalon ko tay karna tha aur muqaabla bhi bahut badi fauj se tha, isliye Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne musalmanon se saaf-saaf farma diya tha taake dushman ke muqable ke liye poori taiyaarii kar lein chunanche ( jang ke liye) jahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jana tha (yani Tabook ( iska aap ne saaf elaan kar diya tha."
2949,Kab-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) kaha kartey they ke kam aisa hota ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi safar mein jumerat ke siwa aur kisi din niklein.
2950,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-Tabook ke liye jumerat ke din nikley they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jumerat ke din safar karna pasand farmatey they.
2951,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina mein Zohar char rakaat padhi phir Asr ki Namaz zul-Hulaifa mein 2 rakaat padhi aur maine suna ke sahaba Haj aur Umra donon ka labbaik aik sath pukar rahe they.
2952,"Madina se (hijjatul-wadaa ke liye) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath ham us waqt nikley jab Zi-Qada ke panch din baqi they. hafte ke din hamara maqsad Haj ke siwa aur kuchh bhi na tha. jab ham Makka se qareeb huey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm farmaya ke jiske sath qurbani ka janwar na ho jab wo Baitullah ke tawaaf aur Safa aur Marwa ki saee se farigh ho jaey to ehram khol de. ( phir Haj ke liye baad mein ehram baandhey) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha ke dasween Zil-Hijja ko hamarey yahan gaaey ka gosht aaya, maine puchha ke gosht kaisa hai? to bataya gaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni beeviyon ki taraf se jo gaaey qurbani ki hai ye usi ka gosht hai. Yahya ne bayan kya ke maine iske baad us hadis ka zikr Qasim-bin-Muhammad se kya to unhon-ne bataya ke qism Allah ki ! Umra binte-Abdur-Rehman ne tum se ye hadis theek theek bayan ki hai."
2953,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (fatah Makka ke liye Madina se) Ramazan mein nikley aur rozey se they. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maqam kudaid par pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iftaar kya. Sufiyan ne kaha ke Zohri ne bayan kya, unhein Abdullah ne khabar di aur unhein Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne phir yahi hadis bayan ki."
2954,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein aik fauj mein bheja aur hidayat farmai ke agar falan-falan 2 qureshi (Hiba-bin-Aswad aur Naafe'-bin-abd Umar) jinka aap ne naam liya tum ko mil jayen to unhein aag mein jalaa dena. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke jab ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se rukhsat honey ki ijazat ke liye hazir huey, us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tumhen pahley hidayat ki thi ke falan-falan qureshi agar tumhen mil jayen to unhein aag mein jalaa dena. lekin ye haqiqat hai ke aag ki saza dena Allah Taala ke siwa kisi ke liye sazawar nahi hai. isliye agar wo tumhen mil jayen to unhein qatl kar dena ( aag mein na jalaanaa ( ."
2955,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''(khaleefa waqt ke ehkaam) sunnaa aur unhein bajaa lana (har musalman ke liye) wajib hai, jab tak ke gunah ka hukm na diya jaey. agar gunah ka hukm diya jaey to phir na usey sunnaa chahiye aur na is par amal karna chaahiye.''"
2956,ham log bhaley hi duniya mein sabse peechhey aaey lekin (aakhirat mein) jannat mein sabse aagey hongey.''
2957,"jisne meri itaat ki us ne Allah ki itaat ki aur jisne meri nafarmani ki us ne Allah ki nafarmani ki aur jisne ameer ki itaat ki us ne meri itaat ki aur jisne ameer ki nafarmani ki, us ne meri nafarmani ki. imam ki misal dhaal jaisi hai ke iske peechhey reh kar uski aad mein (yani iske sath ho kar) jang ki jati hai. aur usi ke zariey (dushman ke hamle se) bacha jata hai, isliye agar imam tumhen Allah se dartey rehney ka hukm de aur insaf karey iska sawab usey milega, lekin agar be-insaafii karega to uska wabaal is par hoga."
2958,"(Suleh Hudaibiya ke baad) jab ham doosrey saal phir aaey, to ham mein se (jinhon ne suleh Hudaibiya ke mauqe par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi) 2 log bhi us darakht ki nishan dahii par muttafiq nahi ho sakey. jiske nichey ham ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki thi aur ye sirf Allah ki rehmat thi. Juweriya ne kaha, maine Naafe se poochha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se kis baat par bait ki thi, kya maut par li thi? farmaya ke nahi, balke sabr w istiqaamat par bait li thi."
2959,Harra ki ladai ke zamane mein aik sahib unke paas aaey aur kaha ke Abdullaah-bin-Hanzala logon se (Yazeed ke khilaaf) maut par bait ley rahe hain. to unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad ab main maut par kisi se bait nahi karunga .
2960,"(Hudaibiya ke mauqe par) maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bait ki. phir aik darakht ke saaey mein aa kar khada ho gaya. jab logon ka hujoom kam hua to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum kya, ibne-Akwa kya bait nahi karogey ? unhon-ne kaha ke maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! main to bait kar chuka hun. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, dobara aur bhi ! chunanche maine dobara bait ki) Yazeed bin abi Ubaidullah kehtey hain ke) maine Salma-bin-Akwa (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, abu-Muslim us din aap hazraat ne kis baat par bait ki thi? kaha ke maut par."
2961,"Ansar khandaq khodtey huey (Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par) kehtey they نحن الذين بايعوا محمدا على الجهاد ما حيينا أبدا''ham wo log hain jinhoney Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jihad par bait ki hai hamesha ke liye, jab tak hamarey jism mein jaan hai.''"
2962,"main apne bhai ke sath (fatah Makka ke baad) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke ham se hijrat par bait ley lijiye . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hijrat to (Makka ke fateh honey ke ba'd, wahan se) hijrat karke aaney walon par khatm ho gaee. maine arz kya, phir aap ham se kis baat par bait lengey ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Islam aur jihad par."
2963,"main apne bhai ke sath (fatah Makka ke baad) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ke ham se hijrat par bait ley lijiye . Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke hijrat to (Makka ke fateh honey ke ba'd, wahan se) hijrat karke aaney walon par khatm ho gaee. maine arz kya, phir aap ham se kis baat par bait lengey ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Islam aur jihad par."
2964,"mere paas aik shakhs aaya, aur aisi baat poochhi ke meri kuchh samajh mein na aaya ke iska jawab kya dun. us ne poochha, mujhey ye masla bataiye ke aik shakhs bahut hi khush aur hathiyar band ho kar hamarey ameeron ke sath jihad ke liye jata hai. phir wo ameer hamein aisi chizon ka mukallaf qarar detey hain ke ham unki taqat nahi rakhtey. maine kaha, Allah ki qism ! meri kuchh samajh mein nahi aata ke tumhari baat ka jawab kya dun, albatta jab ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hayaat mubaraka mein) they, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko kisi bhi maamle mein sirf aik martaba hukm ki zarurat pesh aati thi aur ham fauran hi usey bajaa latey they, ye yad rakhney ki baat hai ke tum logon mein us waqt tak khair rahegi jab tak tum Allah se dartey rahogey, aur agar tumharey dil mein kisi maamle mein shuba paida ho jaey (ke kya chahiye ya nahi ( to kisi aalim se iske mutaalliq poochh lo taake itmeenaan ho jaey, wo daur bhi aaney wala hai ke koi aisa aadmi bhi (jo sahi saheeh masley bata de) tumhen nahi milega. us zaat ki qism jiske siwa koi maabood nahi ! jitni duniya baqi reh gaee hai wo wadi ke us pani ki tarah hai jiska saaf aur achchha hissey to piyaa ja chuka hai aur gadlaa hissey baqi reh gaya hai."
2965,Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ne unhein khat likha aur maine usey padha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne kuchh dinon mein jin mein aap jang kartey they Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) intizar kartey yahan tak ke suraj dhal jata ( phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ladai shuru kartey ( .
2966,"iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ko khitab kartey huey farmaya : ''logo! dushman ke sath jang ki khahish aur tamanna dil mein na rakha karo, balke Allah Taala se amn w aafiyat ki dua kya karo, albatta jab dushman se mudbhed ho hi jaey to phir sabr w istiqaamat ka saboot do, yad rakho ke jannat talwaaron ke saaey taley hai, iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun dua ki اللهم منزل الكتاب ومجري السحاب وهازم الأحزاب ، Mina padhi. اهزمهم وانصرنا عليهم''aey Allaah! kitab ke nazil karne waale, badal bhejney waale, ehzaab ( dushman ke daston ( ko shikast dene waale, unhein shikast de aur unke muqaabley mein hamari madad kar.''"
2967,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jang ( jange-Tabook ( mein Sharik tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) peechhey se aa kar mere paas tashrif laey. main apne pani laadney waley aik oont par Sawar tha. chunkey wo thak chuka tha, isliye ahista-ahista chal raha tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum farmaya ke Jaabir ! tumharey oont ko kya ho gaya hai? maine arz kya ke thak gaya hai. Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) peechhey gaey aur usey daantaa aur uske liye dua ki. phir to wo barabar doosrey oonton ke aagey-aagey chalta raha. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, apne oont ke mutaalliq kya khayal hai? maine kaha ke ab achchha hai. aap ki barkat se aisa ho gaya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir kya usey bechogey? unhon-ne bayan kya ke main sharminda ho gaya, kyonke hamarey paas pani laney ko iske siwa aur koi oont nahi raha tha. magar maine arz kya, ji haan ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya phir bech de. chunanche maine wo oont Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bech diya aur ye tay paya ke Madina tak mein usi par Sawar ho kar jaaunga. bayan kya ke maine arz kya, ya Rasulullah! meri shadi abhi nai hui hai. maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ( aagey badh kar apne ghar janey ki) ijazat chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat inayat farma di. isliye main sabse pahley Madina pahunch aaya. jab maamun se mulaqat hui to unhon-ne mujh se oont ke mutaalliq poochha. jo maamle mein kar chuka tha uski unhein itlaa di. to unhon-ne mujhey bura-bhala kaha, (eik oont tha terey paas wo bhi bech daala ab pani kis par laaeyga) jab maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat chahi thi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se malum farmaya tha ke kunwari se shadi ki hai ya bewa se? maine arz kya tha bewa se is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha ke kunwaarii se kyon na ki, wo bhi tumharey sath kheltii aur tum bhi uske sath kheltey. (kyonke Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) bhi abhi kunwaarey they) maine kaha ya Rasulullah ! mere bap ki wafat ho gaee hai ya (ye kaha ke) wo (Uhud) mein Shahid ho chukey hain aur meri chhoti chhotii bahnein hain. isliye mujhey achchha nahi malum hua ke unhiin jaisi kisi ladki ko biyaah ke laaun, jo na unhein adab sikhaa sakey na unki nigrani kar sakey. isliye maine bewa se shadi ki taake wo unki nigrani karey aur unhein adab sikhaaey. unhon-ne bayan kya, phir jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Madina pahunchey to subah ke waqt main usi oont par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey us oont ki qeemat ata farmai aur phir wo oont bhi wapas kar diya. Mughira rawi (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ne kaha ke hamarey nazdeek saude mein ye shart lagaanaa achchha hai kuchh bura nahi."
2968,Madina mein aik baar kuchh dahshat phail gaee to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik ghodey par Sawar ho kar) halaat malum karne ke liye sabse aagey they) phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ham ne to koi baat nahi dekhi . albatta us ghodey ko ham ne daudney mein dariya ki rawaanii jaisa tez paya hai (baab aur hadis mein mutaabiqat zahir hai).
2969,"(Madina mein) logon mein dahshat phail gaee thi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik ghodey par jo bahut sust tha, sawar huey aur tanha eid lagaatey huey aagey badhey . sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aap ke peechhey Sawar ho kar nikley. iske baad waapsii par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke khaufzada honey ki koi baat nahi hai, albatta ye ghoda dariya hai. us din ke baad phir wo ghoda ( daud wghaira ke mauqe par) kabhi peechhey nahi raha."
2970,umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya maine Allah ke rastey mein (jihad ke liye) apna aik ghoda aik shakhs ko sawari ke liye de diya tha. phir maine dekha ke (baazaar mein) wahi ghoda bik ( bik ( raha hai. maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha ke kya main usey khareed sakta hoon? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke us ghodey ko tum na khareedo aur apna sadqa ( chahe khareed kar hi ho ( wapas na lo.
2971,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne Allah ke rastey mein apna aik ghoda sawari ke liye de diya tha. phir unhon-ne dekha ke wahi ghoda bik ( bik ( raha hai. apne ghodey ko unhon-ne khareednaa chaha aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se iske mutaalliq poochha, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke tum usey na khareedo aur is tarah apne sadqa ko wapas na lo."
2972,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar meri ummat par ye Amr mushkil na guzarta to main kisi sariya (yani mujaahideen ka aik chhota sa dasta jiski tadaad zyada se zyada chalis (40) ho) ki shirkat bhi na chhodtaa. lekin mere paas sawari ke itney oont nahi hain ke main unko sawar karke sath ley chalun aur ye mujh par bahut mushkil hai ke mere sathi mujh se peechhey reh jaaein. meri to ye khushi hai ke Allah ke rastey mein main jihad karun aur Shahid kya jaun. phir zinda kya jaun, phir Shahid kya jaun aur phir zinda kya jaaun.''"
2973,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jange-Tabook mein Sharik tha aur aik jawan oont maine sawari ke liye diya tha, mere khayal mein mera ye amal, tamam doosrey aamaal ke muqaabley mein sabse zyada qaabile-bharosa tha. (ke Allah Taala ke yahan maqbool hoga) maine aik mazdoor bhi apne sath ley liya tha. phir wo mazdoor aik shakhs (khud Yala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu)) se lad padaa aur unmein se aik ne doosrey ke hath mein daant se kaat liya. doosrey ne jhat jo apna hath uske munh se kheenchaa to uske aagey ka daant toot gaya. wo shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein faryaadii hua lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hath kheenchney waley par koi jurmaanaa nahi lagaya balke farmaya ke kya tumharey munh mein wo apna hath yun hi rehney deta taake tum usey chabaa jao jaisey oont chabaataa hai."
2974,"Qais-bin-Sad Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ne, jo jihad main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke alambardaar they, jab Haj ka irada kya to ( ehram baandhney se pahley) kanghi ki."
2975,Khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath nahi aaey they. unki aankhon mein takleef thi. phir unhon-ne kaha ke kya main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jihad mein Sharik na hoonga? chunanche wo nikley aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ja miley. us raat ki Sham ko jiski subah ko khaibar fateh hua hai Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main Islami jhanda us shakhs ko doonga ya (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke) kal Islami jhanda us shakhs ke hath mein hoga jisey Allah aur uske rasool apna mahboob rakhtey hain. ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye farmaya ke jo Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat rakhta hai. aur Allah us shakhs ke hath par fateh farmaeyga. phir Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aa gaey. halanke unke aaney ki hamein koi ummeed na thi. (kyonke wo aankhen dukhney ki bimari mein mubtala they) logon ne kaha ke ye Ali (Raziallahu anhu) bhi aagey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jhanda unhein ko diya aur Allah ne unhein ke hath par fateh farmai.
2976,"maine suna ke Abbas (rz), Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) se keh rahe they ke kya yahan par Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aapko jhanda nasab karne ka hukm farmaya tha?"
2977,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, mujhey jaame' kalam (jiski ibaarat mukhtasar aur faseeh w baleegh ho aur mana bahut wasee hon) de kar bheja gaya hai aur raub ke zariey meri madad ki gaee hai. main soyaa hua tha ke zameen ke khazaanon ki kunjiyaan mere paas laai gain aur mere hath par rakh di gaiin. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) to (apne rab ke paas) ja chukey aur (jin khazaanon ki wo kunjiyaan thiin) unhein ab tum nikal rahe ho."
2978,(aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka naamaa Mubarak jab Rome ke badshah Hiraql ko mila to) us ne apna aadmi unhein talash karne ke liye bhejaa. ye log us waqt iiliyaa mein thahrey huey they. aakhir (taweel guftgu ke baad) us ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka naamaa Mubarak mangwaayaa. jab wo padha ja chuka to uske darbar mein hangaama barpa ho gaya (chaaron taraf se) awaz buland honey lagi aur hamein bahar nikal diya gaya. jab ham bahar kar diye gaey to maine apne sathiyon se kaha ke ibne-abii-Kabsha ( murad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se hai) ka mamla to ab bahut aagey badh chuka hai. ye mulk bani Asfar ( qaisar Rome (mojooda Itly) ( bhi unse darney laga hai.
2979,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Madina ki hijrat ka irada kya to maine (waalid maajid saiyedna ( Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke ghar aap ke liye safar ka naashta taiyaar kya tha. unhon-ne bayan kya ke jab aap ke naashtey aur pani ko baandhney ke liye koi cheez nahi milii, to maine Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke mere kamar band ke alaawaa aur koi cheez usey baandhney ke liye nahi hai. to unhon-ne farmaya ke phir usi ke 2 tukdey kar lo. aik se naashta baandh dena aur doosrey se paanii, chunanche us ne aisa hi kya, aur isi wjah se mera naam ''zaatun-naqaatain'' ( 2 kamar bandon wali) pad gaya."
2980,"ham log Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamaney mein qurbani ka gosht bataur khane-pine ka saman Madina ley jaya kartey they (ye ley jana bataur khane-pine ka saman hua karta tha, us se aap ka matlab Sabit hua) ."
2981,khaibar ki jang ke mauqe par wo Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath gaey they. jab lashkar maqam Sehbaa par pahuncha jo khaibar ka nichlaa ilaqa hai to logon ne Asr ki Namaz padhi aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khana mangwaayaa. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas sattu ke siwa aur koi cheez nahi laai gaee aur ham ne wahi sattu khaya aur piyaa. iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khadey huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kulli ki. ham ne bhi kulli ki aur Namaz padhi.
2982,"jab logon ke paas zaade-raah khatm honey laga to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein log apne oont zabah karne ki ijazat leney hazir huey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ijazat de di. itney mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) se unki mulaqat hui. us ijazat ki itlaa unhein bhi un logon ne di. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne sun kar kaha, un oonton ke baad phir tumharey paas baqi kya reh jaeyga (kyonke unhiin par Sawar ho kar itni door daraaz ki masafat bhi to tay karni thi) iske baad umr (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! log agar apne oont bhi zabah kar dengey. to phir iske baad unke paas baqi kya reh jaeyga ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : phir logon mein elaan kar do ke) oonton ko zabah karne ke bajaey) apna bacha khuchaa khane-pine ka saman lekar yahan aa jaaein. (sab logon ne jo kuchh bhi unke paas khaney ki cheez baqi bach gaee thi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney la kar rakh di (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dua farmai aur is mein barkat hui. phir sab ko unke bartanon ke sath aap ne bulaya. sab ne bhar-bhar kar usmein se liya aur jab sab log farigh ho gaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main gawahi deta hun ke Allah Taala ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi aur main Allah ka rasool hun."
2983,"ham (eik jang par) nikley. hamari tadaad teen so thi, ham apna raashan apne kandhon par uthaey huey they. aakhir hamara khane-pine ka saman jab ( taqriban ( khatm ho gaya, to aik shakhs ko rozaana sirf aik khajoor khaney ko milney lagi aik shagird ne poochha, aey abu-Adbullah ! ( Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu)) aik khajoor se bhala aik aadmi ka kya banta hoga? unhon-ne farmaya ke uski qadr hamein us waqt malum hui jab aik khajoor bhi baqi nahi reh gaee thi. iske baad ham dariya par aaey to aik aisi machhli mili jisey dariya ne bahar phenk diya tha aur ham atthaara din tak khub ji bhar kar usi ko khaatey rahe."
2984,"unhon-ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! aap ke ashaab Haj aur Umra donon karke wapas ja rahe hain aur main sirf Haj kar paai hun. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir jao (Umra kar aao) Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu)) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ke bhai ( tumhen apni sawari ke peechhey bitha lengey. chunanche aap ne Abdur-Rehman (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya ke taneem se (ehraam baandh kar) Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko Umra kara laaein. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us arsa main Makka ke oopri ilaqe par unka intizar kya. yahan tak ke wo aa gaiin."
2985,mujhey Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hukm diya tha ke apni sawari par apne peechhey Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ko bitha kar ley jaun aur taneem se ( ehram baandh kar) unhein Umra kara laaun.
2986,mein abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ki sawari par unke peechhey betha hua tha. tamam sahaba Haj aur Umra donon hi ke liye aik sath labbaik keh rahe they.
2987,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik gadhey par uski paalaan rakh kar sawar huey. jis par aik chadar bichhi hui thi aur Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko aap ne apne peechhey bitha rakha tha.
2988,"fateh Makka ke mauqe par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Makka ke oopri ilaaqey se apni sawari par tashrif laey. Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni sawari par peechhey bitha diya tha aur aap ke sath Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. aur Usmaan-bin-Tal'ha (Raziallahu anhu) bhi jinke paas Kaba ki kunjiyaan thin. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne masjide-Haraam main apni sawari bitha di aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha ke Baitullah ki kunjii laaein. unhon-ne Kaba ka darwaza khol diya aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) andar dakhil ho gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Usaama, Bilal aur Usman (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kafi der tak andar thahrey rahe aur jab bahar tashrif laey to sahaba ne (andar janey ke liye) aik doosrey se aagey honey ki koshish ki sabse pahley andar dakhil hone-waale Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) they. unhon-ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko darwazey ke peechhey khada paya aur unse puchha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz kahan padhi hai? unhon-ne us jagah ki taraf ishara kya jahan Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Namaz padhi thi. Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke mujhey ye poochhna yad nahi raha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kitni rakatein padhi thin."
2989,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''insaan ke har aik jod par sadqa lazim hota hai. har din jis mein suraj tuloo hota hai. phir agar wo insanon ke darmyan insaf karey to ye bhi aik sadqa hai aur kisi ko sawari ke mamley mein agar madad pahunchaaey, is tarah par ke usey is par Sawar kiraaey ya uska saman utha kar rakh de to ye bhi aik sadqa hai aur achi baat munh se nikaalnaa bhi aik sadqa hai aur har qadam jo Namaz ke liye uthtaa hai wo bhi sadqa hai aur agar koi rastey se kisi takleef dene wali cheez ko hata de to wo bhi aik sadqa hai.''"
2990,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne dushman ke ilaaqey mein Quran Majeed lekar janey se mana farmaya tha.
2991,"subah hui to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khaibar mein dakhil they. itney mein wahan ke rehney waley ( Yahudi ( phaawdey apni gardanon par liye huey nikley. jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko (lashakr ke sath Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko) dekha to chilla uthey ke ye Muhammad lashkar ke sath ( aagey ( Muhammad lashkar ke sath , Muhammad lashkar ke sath ! (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) chunanche wo sab bhag kar qile' mein panah guzeen ho gaey. us waqt Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne hath uthaey aur na'rae-takbeer buland farmaya, sath hi irshad hua ke khaibar to tabah ho chukaa. ke jab kisi qaum ke aangan mein ham utar aatey hain to daraaey huey logon ki subah buri ho jati hai. aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ham ko gadhey mil gaey, aur ham ne unhein zabah karke pakaanaa shuru kar diya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke manaadii ne ye pukara ke Allah aur uske rasool tumhen gadhey ke gosht se mana kartey hain. chunanche haandiyon mein jo kuchh tha sab ulat diya gaya. is riwayat ki mutabiat (pairavi) Ali ne Sufiyan se ki hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne donon hath uthaey they."
2992,"ham aik safar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. jab ham kisi wadi mein utartey to ( لا إله إلا الله (aur ( Allahu-akbar ( kehtey aur hamari awaz buland ho jati isliye Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey logo ! apni jaanon par raham khaao , kyonke tum kisi behrey ya ghayab Allah ko nahi pukar rahe ho. wo to tumharey sath hi hai. beshak wo sunney wala aur tum se bahut qareeb hai. barkaton wala hai. uska naam aur uski azmat bahut hi badi hai.''"
2993,"jab ham (kisi bulandi par) chadhtey , to ( Allahu-akbar ( kehtey aur jab ( kisi nasheb mein) utartey to (subhanallah) kehtey they."
2994,jab ham bulandi par chadhtey to ( Allahu-akbar ( kehtey aur nichey ki taraf utartey to (subhanallah) kehtey they.
2995,"jab Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Haj ya Umra se wapas hotey jahan tak mein samajhta hun yun kaha jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jihad se laut'tey, to jab bhi aap kisi bulandi par chadhtey ya (nasheb se) kankreeley maidan mein aatey to teen martaba ( Allahu-akbar ( kehtey. phir farmaatey لا إله إلا الله ، Mina وحده لا شريك له ، Mina له الملك ، Mina وله الحمد ، Mina وهو على كل شىء قدير ، Mina آيبون تائبون عابدون ساجدون لربنا حامدون ، Mina صدق الله وعده ، Mina ونصر عبده ، Mina وهزم الأحزاب وحده‏''Allaah ke siwa aur koi maabood nahi wo aik hai. uska koi Sharik nahi. mulk uska hai aur tamam ta'reefein usi ke liye hain aur wo har kaam par qudrat rakhta hai. ham wapas ho rahe hain tauba kartey huey, ibadat kartey huey. apne rab ki bargah mein sajda rez hotey aur uski hamd padhtey huey, Allah ne apna wada sach kar dikhaya aur apne bandey ki madad ki aur tanha (kuffaar ki) tamam jamaton ko shikast de dii.'' Saleh ne kaha ke maine Saalim-bin-Abdullaah se puchha kya Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ne lafz ( آيبون (ke baad (inshaAllah) nahi kaha tha to unhon-ne bataya ke nahi."
2996,"maine abu-Barda bin abi Musa se suna, wo aur Yazeed-bin-abii-Kabsha aik safar mein sath they aur Yazeed safar ki haalat mein bhi roza rakha kartey they. abu-Barda ne kaha ke maine (apne waalid) abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) se bahut baar suna. wo kaha kartey they ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab banda bimar hota hai ya safar karta hai to uske liye un tamam ibaadaat ka sawab likha jata hai jinhein iqamat ya sihat ke waqt ye kya karta tha."
2997,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (eik kaam ke liye) Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par sahaba ko pukara , to Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne uske liye kaha ke main hazir hun. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba ko pukara , aur us martaba bhi Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne ko pesh kya, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir pukara aur phir Zuber (Raziallahu anhu) ne apne aapko pesh kya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aakhir farmaya ke har Nabi ke hawaarii hotey hain aur mere hawaarii Zuber hain. Sufiyan ne kaha ke hawaarii ke mana muaawin , madadgaar ke hain (ya wafaadaar mahrame-raaz ko hawaarii kaha gaya hai)."
2998,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' jitna main janta hun, agar logon ko bhi akeley safar (ki buraaiyon (ke mutaalliq itna ilm hota to koi sawar raat mein akelaa safar na kartaa.''"
2999,"Usama-bin-Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) se Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke Hijjatul-wada ke safar ki raftaar ke mutaalliq puchha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kis kis chaal par chaltey , Yahya ne kaha Urwa ne ye bhi kaha tha (ke mein sun raha tha) lekin main iska kehna bhool gaya. gharaz Usama (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) zara tez chaltey jab khuli jagah patey to sawari ko douda detey. ( nas ( oont ki chaal jo (عنق‏) se tez hoti hai."
3000,"main Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Makka ke rastey mein tha, itney mein unko Safiya binte- abi Ubaid (Raziallahu anhu) (unki biwi (ke mutaalliq sakht bimari ki khabar mili . chunanche aap ne tez chalnaa shuru kar diya aur jab ( suraj ghurub honey ke baad) shafaq doob gaee to aap sawari se utrey aur maghrib aur isha ki Namaz mila kar padhi, phir kaha ke maine Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha ke jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tezi ke sath safar karna chahtey to maghrib mein taakheer karke donon namazein ( maghrib aur isha ( aik sath ada farmatey."
3001,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''safar kya hai maano azab ka aik tukda hai, aadmi ki neend, khaaney-peeney sab mein rukawat paida karta hai. isliye jab musaafir apna kaam pura kar ley to usey jaldi ghar wapas aa jana chaahiye.''"
3002,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik ghoda Allah ke rastey mein sawari ke liye de diya tha, phir unhon-ne dekha ke wahi ghoda bik raha hai. unhon-ne chaha ke usey khareed lein. lekin jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat chahi to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab tum usey na khareedo, aur apne sadqa ko wapas na phero."
3003,"maine Allah ke rastey mein aik ghoda sawari ke liye diya, aur jisey diya tha wo usey bechney laga. ya (aap ne ye farmaya tha ke) us ne usey bilkul kamzor kar diya tha. isliye mera irada hua ke main usey wapas khareed loon , mujhey ye khayal tha ke wo shakhs sastey daamon par usey bech dega. maine iske mutaalliq Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jab puchha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar wo ghoda tumhen aik dirham mein mil jaey phir bhi usey na khareednaa. kyonke apne hi sadqa ko wapas leney wala us kuttey ki tarah hai jo apni qai ko khud hi chaatta hai."
3004,"maine Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, aap bayan kartey they ke aik sahabi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se jihad mein shirkat ki ijazat chahi . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse malum farmaya ''kya tumharey maan-baap zinda hain? '' unhon-ne kaha ke ji haan ! Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''phir unhiin mein jihad karo. (yani unko khush rakhney ki koshish karo).''"
3005,wo aik safar main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. Abdullah ( Abdullah-bin abi-Bakr bin Hazam rawi hadis) ne kaha ke mera khayal hai Abu-Basheer ne kaha ke log apni khuwab gaahon mein they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna aik qaasid ( Zaid-bin-Haarisa (Raziallahu anhu)) ye elaan karne ke liye bheja ke jis shakhs ke oont ki gardan mein taant ka gandaa ho ya yun farmaya ke gandaa (haar) ho wo usey kaat daley.
3006,"unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke koi mard kisi ( ghair mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) ( aurat ke sath tanhai mein na baithey aur koi aurat us waqt tak safar na karey jab tak uske sath koi uska mohrim (ehraam walaa shakhs) na ho. itney mein aik sahabi khadey huey aur arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! maine falan jihad mein apna naam likhwaa diya hai aur idhar meri biwi Haj ke liye ja rahi hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir to bhi ja aur apni biwi ke sath Haj kar."
3007,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey , Zuber aur Miqdaad-bin-Aswad (Raziallahu anhu) ko aik muhim par bheja aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jab tum log rauza khaakh (jo Madina se baara mail ke fasla par aik jagah ka naam hai) par pahunch jao to wahan aik badhiyaa aurat tumhen oont par Sawar milegii aur uske paas aik khat hoga, tum log us se wo khat ley lenaa. ham rawaana huey aur hamarey ghodey hamein tezi ke sath liye ja rahe they. aakhir ham rauza khaakh par pahunch gaey aur wahan waqei aik boodhi aurat maujood thi jo oont par Sawar thi. ham ne us se kaha ke khat nikaal. usne kaha ke mere paas to koi khat nahi. lekin jab ham ne usey dhamki di ke agar tu ney khat na nikala to tumharey kapdey ham khud utaar dengey. is par us ne apni gundhii hui choti ke andar se khat nikal kar diya, aur ham usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein lekar hazir huey, uska mazmoon ye tha, Haatib bin abi Balta' ki taraf se mushrekeen Makka ke chand aadmiyon ki taraf, usmein unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke kuchh bhedon ki khabar di thi. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Haatib ! ye kya waqia hai? unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! mere barey mein jaldbaazii se kaam na lijiye. meri haisiyat (Makka mein) ye thi ke Quraish ke sath maine rehna sahnaa ikhtiyar kar liya tha, unse rishta naata mera kuchh bhi na tha. aap ke sath jo doosrey muhajireen hain unki to Makka mein sab ki rishtedaarii hai aur Makka waley usi wjah se unke azeezon ki aur unke maalon ki hifazat w himaayat karengey magar Makka walon ke sath mera koi nasbi (rishtey ka ( talluq nahi hai, isliye maine sochaa ke un par koi ehsan kar dun jis se asar lekar wo mere bhi azeezon ki Makka mein hifazat karein. maine ye kaam kufr ya irtidaad (Islam se phir jaaney) ki wjah se hargiz nahi kya hai aur na Islam ke baad kufr se khush ho kar. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sun kar farmaya ke Haatib ne sach kaha hai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! ijazat dijiye mein us munafiq ka sar uda dun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' nahi, ye badr ki ladai main ( musalmanon ke sath mil kar) ladey hain aur tumhen malum nahi, Allah Taala mujaahideen badr ke ahwaal ( maut tak ke) pahley hi se janta tha, aur wo khud hi farma chuka hai ke tum jo chaho karo main tumhen maaf kar chuka hoon.'' Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha ke hadis ki ye sanad bhi kitni umda hai."
3008,"badr ki ladai se qaidi ( mushrekeen Makka ( laey gaey. jin mein Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they. unke badan par koi kapda nahi tha. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke liye qamees talash karwai . (wo lambey qad ke they) isliye Abdullah-bin-Ubai ( munafiq ( ki qamees hi unke badan par aa saki aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein wo qamees pehna di. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( Abdullah-bin-Ubai ki maut ke baad) apni qamees utaar kar usey pahnaaii thi. ibne-Uena ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par jo uska ehsan tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne chaha ke usey ada kar dein."
3009,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne khaibar ki ladai ke din farmaya '' kal mein aisey shakhs ke hath mein Islami jhanda doonga jiske hath par Islami fateh hasil hogi, jo Allah aur uske rasool se mohabbat rakhta hai aur jis se Allah aur uska rasool bhi mohabbat rakhtey hain.'' raat bhar sab sahaba ke zahan mein yahi khayal raha ke dekhiye ke kisey jhanda milta hai. jab subah hui to har shakhs ummeedwaar tha, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya '' Ali kahan hain? '' arz kya gaya ke unki aankhon mein dard ho gaya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apna Mubarak thook unki aankhon mein laga diya aur us se unhein sihat ho gaee, kisi qism ki bhi takleef baqi na rahi. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ko jhanda ata farmaya, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke kya main un logon se us waqt tak na ladun jab tak ye hamarey hi jaisey yani musalman na ho jaaein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein hidayat farmai ke yun hi chala jaa. jab unki sarhad mein utrey to unhein Islam ki dawat dena aur unhein batana ke (Islam ke hawale sey) un par kon kaun se kaam zaroori hain. Allah ki qism ! agar tumharey zariey Allah aik shakhs ko bhi musalman kar de to ye tumharey liye surkh oonton se behtar hai."
3010,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' aisey logon par Allah ko tajjub hoga, jo jannat mein bediyon samet dakhil hongey (yani musalmanon ne kaafiron ko pakad kar bediyon mein qaid kar diya phir wo musalman ho gaey to Allah Taala unko Islam ki wjah se jannat mein dakhil kar dega to Allah Taala aisey logon par tajjub karengey ke ye log apne kufr ki wjah se pairon mein zanjeer bandhey huey aur Islam la kar jannat mein dakhil ho gaey.)"
3011,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''teen tarah ke aadmi aisey hain jinhein 2 guna sawab milta hai. awwal wo shakhs jiski londi ho, wo usey taleem de aur taleem dene mein achchha tariqa ikhtiyar karey, usey adab sikhaaey aur is mein achchhey tareeqey se kaam ley , phir usey aazad karke us se shadi kar ley to usey dohra ajr milega. doosra wo momin jo ahle-kitab mein se ho ke pahley (apne Nabi par eman laya tha) phir Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) par bhi eman laya to usey bhi dohra ajr milega , tesraa wo ghulam jo Allah Taala ke huquq ki bhi adaaeygi karta hai aur apne aaqa ke sath bhi bhalai karta hai.'' iske baad Shabi ( rawi hadis) ne kaha ke maine tumhen ye hadis bila kisi mehnat w mashaqqat ke de di hai. aik zamana wo bhi tha jab us se bhi kam hadis ke liye Madina Munawra tak ka safar karna padta tha."
3012,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) maqam Abwaa ya maqam Wadaan mein mere paas se guzrey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya ke mushrekeen ke jis qabeeley par shab khoon maara jaeyga kya unki aurton aur bachchon ko bhi qatl karna durust hoga? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo bhi unhiin mein se hain aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna ke aap farma rahe they Allah aur uske rasool ke siwa aur kisi ki charaagaah nahi hai.
3013,"Amr ham se hadis bayan kartey they. unse ibne-Shahaab, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, ( Sufiyan ne) bayan kya ke phir ham ne hadis khud Zohri ( ibne-Shahab ( se suni. unhon-ne bayan kya ke mujhey Ubaidullah ne khabar di, unhein Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne aur unhein Sa'b (Raziallahu anhu) ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' ( mushrekeen ki aurton aur bachchon ke mutaalliq ke) wo bhi unhiin mein se hain.'' (Zohri ke waaste se) jis tarah Amr ne bayan kya tha ke) هم من آبائهم ( wo bhi unhiin ke baap-daadon ki nasl hain. Zohri ne khud ham se un alfaz ke sath bayan nahi kya yani ( هم من آبائهم ( nahi kaha balke ( هم منهم ( kaha,"
3014,"ham se Ahmed bin Yunus ne bayan kya, kaha ham ko Leis ne khabar di, unhein Naafe ne aur unhein Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne khabar di ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ek jang mein ek aurat qatl hui paai gaee to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton au bachchon ke qatl ko manaa farmaayaa."
3015,aik aurat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zamane mein kisi ghazwey mein maqtool paai gaee to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aurton aur bachchon ke qatl se mana farmaya (to unhon-ne iska iqrar kya ( .
3016,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein aik muhim par rawaana farmaya aur ye hidayat farmai ke agar tumhen falan aur falan mil jayen to unhein aag mein jalaa denaa, phir jab ham ne rawaangii ka irada kya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine tumhen hukm diya tha ke falan aur falan ko jalaa dena. lekin aag aik aisi cheez hai jiski saza sirf Allah Taala hi de sakta hai. isliye agar wo tumhen milein to unhein qatl karna (aag mein na jalaanaa)."
3017,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik qaum ko (jo Abdullah-bin sabaa ki muttabea' thi aur Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko apna rab kehti thi) jalaa diya tha. jab ye khabar Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko mili to aap ne kaha ke agar main hota to kabhi unhein na jalaataa kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai ke Allah ke azab ki saza kisi ko na do, albatta main unhein qatl zaroor karta kyonke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya hai jo shakhs apna Deen tabdeel kar de usey qatl kar do."
3018,"qabila ukul ke aath (8) aadmiyon ki jamat Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein (Islam qabool karne ko) hazir hui lekin Madina ki aab w hua unhein muwafiq nahi aaii, unhon-ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah! hamarey liye (oont ke) doodh ka intizam kar dijiye. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke main tumharey liye doodh nahi de sakta, tum (sadqa ke) oonton mein chaley jao. unka doodh aur peshab piyo, taake tumhari sihat theek ho jaey. wo log wahan se chaley gaey aur unka doodh aur peshab pi kar tandurust ho gaey to charwaahey ko qatl kar diya, aur oonton ko apne sath lekar bhag nikley aur Islam laney ke baad kufr kya, aik shakhs ne uski khabar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko di, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unki talash ke liye sawar daudaaey, do-pahar se pahley hi wo pakad kar laey gaey. unke hath paon kaat diye gaey. phir aap ke hukm se unki aankhon mein salaaii garm karke pher di gaee aur unhein Harra (Madina ki pathreelii zameen) mein daal diya gaya. wo pani maangtey they lekin unhein nahi diya gaya. yahan tak ke wo sab mar gaey. (aisaa hi unhon-ne oonton ke charaney walon ke sath kya tha, jiska badla unhein diya gaya) abu-Qilaba ne kaha ke unhon-ne qatl kya tha, chori ki thi, Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath jang ki thi aur zameen mein fasaad barpa karne ki koshish ki thi."
3019,"maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna hai, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke aik chewntii ne aik Nabi (uzair ya Musa (Alaihissalam) ( ko kaat liya tha. to unke hukm se chewntiyon se sarey ghar jalaa diye gaey. is par Allah Taala ne unke paas wahi bheji ke agar tumhen aik chewntii ne kaat liya tha to tum ne aik aisi makhlooq ko jalaa kar khaak kar diya jo Allah ki tasbeeh bayan karti thi."
3020,"mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''zul-khalasa ko) barbad karke ( mujhey raahat kyon nahi de detey. ye zul-khalasa qabila Khasam ka aik but khaana tha aur usey ( كعبة اليمانية ( kehtey they. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir main qabila Ahmas ke aik so pachaas sawaaron ko lekar chalaa. ye sab hazraat badey achchhey ghud sawar they. lekin main ghodey ki sawari achi tarah nahi kar paata tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere seeney par (apne hath se) maaraa, maine ungliyon ka nishan apne seeney par dekha. farmaya : aey Allah ! ghodey ki pusht par usey sabaat ata farma, aur usey dusron ko hidayat ki raah dikhaaney wala aur khud hidayat yaafta bana , iske baad Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) rawaana huey, aur zul-khalasa ki Imaarat ko gira kar usmein aag laga di. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski khabar bhijwaai . Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ke qaasid ( abu irtaat Husain-bin-Rabee'a) ne khidmat nabwi mein hazir ho kar arz kya us zaat ki qasam! jisne aapko haq ke sath maboos kya hai. main us waqt tak aap ki khidmat mein hazir nahi hua, jab tak ham ne zul-khalasa ko aik khali pet waley oont ki tarah nahi bana diya, ya (unhon-ne kaha) khaarish waley oont ki tarah (muraad weeraanii se hai) Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Ahmas ke sawaaron aur qabeelon ke tamam logon ke liye panch martaba barkaton ki dua farmai."
3021,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( yahood ( banu-nazeer ke khajoor ke baghaat jalwaa diye they.
3022,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke chand aadmiyon ko abu-Raafe ( Yahudi ( ko qatl karne ke liye bhejaa, unmein se aik sahib ( Abdullah-bin Ateek (Raziallahu anhu)) aagey chal kar us qile' ke andar dakhil ho gaey. unhon-ne bayan kya ke andar janey ke baad main us makan mein ghus gaya, jahan unke janwar bandhaa kartey they. bayan kya ke unhon-ne qile' ka darwaza band kar liya, lekin ittifaq ke unka aik gadhaa unke maweshiyon mein se gum tha. isliye usey talash karne ke liye bahar nikley. (is khayal se ke kahin pakda na jaun ( nikalney walon ke sath mein bhi bahar aa gaya, taake un par ye zahir kar dun ke main bhi talash karne walon mein se hun, aakhir gadhaa unhein mil gaya, aur wo phir andar aa gaey. mein bhi unke sath andar aa gaya aur unhon-ne qile' ka darwaza band kar liya, raat ka waqt tha, kanjiyon ka guchchaa unhon-ne aik aisey taaq mein rakhaa, jisey maine dekh liya tha. jab wo sab so gaey to maine chaabiyon ka guchchaa uthaya aur darwaza khol kar abu-Raafe ke paas pahuncha. maine usey awaz di, abu-Raafea'! us ne jawab diya aur main fauran uski awaz ki taraf badha aur is par waar kar baithaa. wo cheekhney laga to main bahar chala aaya. uske paas se wapas aa kar main phir uske kamre mein dakhil hua, maano main uski madad ko pahuncha tha. maine phir awaz di abu-Raafe ! us martaba maine apni awaz badal li thi, usne kaha ke kya kar raha hai, teri maan barbad ho. maine poochha, kya baat pesh aai ? wo kehney laga, na malum kon shakhs mere kamrey mein aa gaya, aur mujh par hamla kar betha hai, unhon-ne kaha ke ab ki baar maine apni talwaar iske pet par rakh kar itni zor se dabaai ke uski haddiyon mein utar gaee, jab main uske kamre se nikla to bahut dahshat mein tha. phir qile' ki aik seedhi par main aaya taake us se nichey utar jaun magar main is par se gir gaya, aur mere paon mein moch aa gaee, phir jab main apne sathiyon ke paas aaya to maine unse kaha ke main to us waqt tak yahan se nahi jaaunga jab tak uski maut ka elaan khud na sun loon. chunanche main wahin thahar gaya aur maine roney wali aurton se abu-Raafe hijaaz ke sodagar ki maut ka elaan buland awaz se suna. unhon-ne kaha ke phir main wahan se uthaa, aur mujhey us waqt kuchh bhi dard malum nahi hua, phir ham Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski bashaarat di."
3023,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ke chand aadmiyon ko abu-Raafe ke paas ( usey qatl karne ke liye) bheja tha. chunanche raat mein Abdullaah-bin-Ateek (Raziallahu anhu) uske qile' mein dakhil huey aur usey sotey huey qatl kya.
3024,"jab wo khawaarij se ladney ke liye rawaana huey to unhein Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ka khat mila. maine usey padha to usmein unhon-ne likha tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik ladai ke mauqe par intizar kya, phir jab suraj dhal gaya."
3025,"to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne logon ko khitab kartey huey farmaya ''aey logo ! dushman se ladai bhidaaii ki tamanna na karo, balke Allah se salamati maango. haan! jab jang chhid jaey to phir sabr kiye raho aur dat kar muqaabla karo aur jaan lo ke jannat talwaaron ke saaey mein hai.'' phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne yun dua ki (اللهم منزل الكتاب ومجري السحاب وهازم الأحزاب اهزمهم وانصرنا عليهم) ''aey Allah ! kitab ( Quran (ke nazil farmaney waale, aey badalon ke chalaney waley ! aey ehzaab (yani kaafiron ki jamaton ko Khandaq ki jang ke mauqe par) shikast dene waley ! hamarey dushman ko shikast de aur unke muqaabley mein hamari madad kar.'' aur Musa-bin-Aqba ne kaha ke mujh se Salim abu-Nazar ne bayan kya ke main Umar-bin Ubaidullah ka munshi tha. unke paas Abdullaah-bin-abi-Aufii (Raziallahu anhu) ka khat aaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha '' dushman se ladai ladney ki tamanna na karo.''"
3026,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' dushman se ladney bhidney ki tamanna na karo, haan ! agar jang shuru ho jaey to phir sabr se kaam lo. ''"
3027,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Kisraa ( Iraan ka badshah ( barbad w halaak ho gaya, ab iske baad koi Kisraa nahi aayega aur qaisar ( Rome (mojooda Itly) ka badshah ( bhi halaak w barbad ho gaya, aur uske baad) Sham (Syria) mein) koi qaisar baqi nahi reh jaeyga aur unke khazaaney Allah ke rastey mein taqseem hongey.''"
3028,aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ladai ko makar aur faraib farmaya.
3029,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''ladaaii kya hai? aik chaal hai.''
3030,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tha '' jang to aik chaalbaazii ka naam hai.''
3031,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Kab-bin-Ashraf ka kaam kon tamam karega? wo Allah aur uske rasool ko bahut takleefein pahuncha chuka hai.'' Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! kya aap mujhey ijazat bakhsh dengey ke main usey qatl kar aaoon ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' haan. '' rawi ne bayan kya ke phir Muhammad-bin-Muslima Kab Yahudi ke paas aaey aur us se kehney lagey ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne to hamein thakaa diya, aur ham se aap zakat maangtey hain. Kab ne kaha ke qism Allah ki ! abhi kya hai abhi aur museebat mein padogey Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) is par kehney lagey ke baat ye hai ke ham ne unki pairwi kar li hai. isliye us waqt tak iska sath chhodnaa ham munasib bhi nahi samajhtey jab tak unki dawat ka koi anjam hamarey samney na aa jaey. gharaz Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) us se isi tarah baatein kartey rahe. aakhir mauqa pa kar usey qatl kar diya."
3032,Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' Kab-bin-Ashraf ke liye kon himmat karta hai? '' Muhammad-bin-Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha kya main usey qatl kar dun? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' haan ! '' unhon-ne arz kya ke phir aap mujhey ijazat dein (ke mein jo chaahoon jhoot sach kahun (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''meri taraf se uski ijazat hai.''
3033,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ibne-Sayyaad ( Yahudi bachchey ( ki taraf ja rahe they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) bhi they ( ibne-Sayyaad ke ajeeb w ghareeb ahwaal ke mutaalliq Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud tahqeeq karna chahtey they) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko itlaa di gaee thi ke ibne-Sayyaad us waqt khajooron ki aad mein maujood hai. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan pahunchey to shakhon ki aad mein chalney lagey. (taake wo aapko dekh na sakey ( ibne-Sayyaad us waqt aik chadar odhey huey chupkey chupkey kuchh gungunaa raha tha, uski maan ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh liya aur pukar uthi ke aey ibne-Sayyaad! ye Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aa pahunchey, wo chaunk uthaa, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke agar ye uski khabar na karti to wo kholtaa (yani uski baton se iska haal khul jaataa) ."
3034,"maine dekha ke jange-Ehzaab main ( khandaq khodtey huey) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) khud mitti utha rahe they. yahan tak ke Sina Mubarak ke baal mitti se at gaey they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke (jism par) baal bahut ghaney they. us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye sher padh rahe they ''aey Allah ! agar teri hidayat na hoti to ham kabhi seedha rasta na patey , na sadqa kar saktey aur na Namaz padhtey. ab tu, ya Allah ! hamarey dilon ko sukoon aur itminan ata farma, aur agar (dushmanon se mudbhed ho jaey to hamein Sabit qadam rakh, dushmanon ne hamarey uper zyadti ki hai. jab bhi wo ham ko fitna fasaad mein mubtala karna chahtey hain to ham inkar kartey hain.'' aap ye sher buland awaz se padh rahe they."
3035,"jab se main Islam laayaa, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (parde ke saath) mujhey (apne ghar mein dakhil honey se) kabhi nahi rokaa aur jab bhi aap mujh ko dekhtey, khushi se aap muskuraaney lagtey."
3036,"aik baar maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein shikayat ki ke main ghodey ki peeth par achi tarah nahi jam paata hun, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere seeney par apna daste-mubaarak maaraa, aur dua ki) اللهم ثبته واجعله هاديا مهديا ( ''aey Allaah! usey ghodey par jama de aur dusron ko seedha rasta bataaney wala bana de aur khud usey bhi seedhey rastey par qaaim rakh.''"
3037,Sahal-bin-Sad Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se shagirdon ne puchha ke) jange-Uhud mein) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke zakhmon ka ilaaj kis dawaa se kya gaya tha? Sehal ne is par kaha ke ab sahaba mein koi shakhs bhi aisa zinda maujood nahi hai jo iske barey mein mujh se zyada janta ho. Ali (Raziallahu anhu) apni dhaal mein pani bhar-bhar kar la rahe they aur Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke chehrey se khoon ko dho rahi thin aur aik boriyaa jalaayaa gaya tha aur aap ke zakhmon mein usi ki raakh ko bhar diya gaya tha.
3038,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) aur abu-Musa ko Yaman bhejaa, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us mauqe par ye hidayat farmai thi ke (logon ke liye) aasani paida karnaa, unhein sakhtiyon mein mubtala na karnaa, unko khush rakhna, nafrat na dilaanaa, aur tum donon aapas mein ittifaq rakhna, ikhtilaf na paida karna."
3039,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-Uhud ke mauqe par (teer andaazon ke) pachaas aadmiyon ka afsar Abdullaah-bin-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein takeed kar di thi ke agar tum ye bhi dekh lo ke parindey ham par toot padey hain. phir bhi apni jagah se mat hatna , jab tak main tum logon ko kelha na bhejoon. isi tarah agar tum ye dekho ke kuffaar ko ham ne shikast de di hai aur unhein paamaal kar diya hai phir bhi yahan se na talnaa , jab main tumhen khud bila na bhejoon . phir Islami lashkar ne kuffaar ko shikast de di. Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, ke Allah ki qism ! maine mushrik aurton ko dekha ke tezi ke sath bhag rahi thin. unke paazeb aur pindliyaan dikhai de rahi thin aur wo apne kapdon ko uthaey huey thin. Abdullaah-bin-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) ke sathiyon ne kaha, ke ghaneemat looto, aey qaum ! ghaneemat tumharey samney hai. tumharey sathi ghalib aagey hain. ab dar kis baat ka hai. is par Abdullaah-bin-Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke kya jo hidayat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ki thi, tum usey bhool gaey? lekin wo log usi par adey rahe ke doosrey ashaab ke sath ghaneemat jama karne mein Sharik rahengey. jab ye log ( aksariyat ( apni jagah chhod kar chaley aaey to unke munh kaafiron ne pher diye, aur) musalmanon ko) shikast zada pa kar bhaagtey huey aaey, yahi wo ghadi thi (jiska zikr sura aale-Imraan mein hai ke) '' jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tum ko peechhey khadey huey bula rahe they''. us se yahi murad hai. us waqt Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath baara sahaba ke siwa aur koi bhi baqi na reh gaya tha. aakhir hamarey 70 aadmi Shahid ho gaey. badr ki ladai mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba ke sath mushrekeen ke aik so chalis (40) aadmiyon ka nuqsan kya tha, 70 unmein se qaidi they aur 70 maqtool , (jab jang khatm ho gaee to aik pahaad par khadey ho kar) Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha kya Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni qaum ke sath maujood hain? teen martaba unhon-ne yahi poochha. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jawab deney se mana farma diya tha. phir unhon-ne poochha, kya ibne-abi-Qahaafa (abu-Bakar (rz)) apni qaum mein maujood hain? ye sawal bhi teen martaba kya, phir puchha ibne-khattaab (Umar (Raziallahu anhu)) apni qaum mein maujood hain? ye bhi teen martaba poochha, phir apne sathiyon ki taraf mud kar kehney lagey ke ye teenon qatl ho chukey hain is par umr (Raziallahu anhu) se na raha gaya aur aap bol padey ke aey Allah ke dushman ! Allah gawah hai ke to jhoot bol raha hai jinke tu ney abhi naam liye they wo sab zinda hain aur abhi tera bura din aaney wala hai. Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha achchha! aaj ka din badr ka badla hai. aur ladai bhi aik dol ki tarah hai) kabhi idhar kabhi idhar ( tum logon ko apni qaum ke kuchh log musla kiye huey milengey. maine is tarah ka koi hukm (apne aadmiyon ko) nahi diya tha, lekin mujhey unka ye amal bura bhi nahi malum hua. iske baad wo fakhriya rajz padhney laga, hubal ( but ka naam ( buland rahe. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tum log iska jawab kyon nahi detey. sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha ham iske jawab mein kya kahein ya rasoolullaah? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya kaho ke Allah sabse buland aur sabse bada buzurg hai. Abu-Sufiyan ne kaha hamara madadgar uzzaa ( but ( hai aur tumhara koi bhi nahi, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, jawab kyon nahi detey, sahaba ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! iska jawab kya diya jaaey? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, kaho ke Allah hamara haami hai aur tumhara haami koi nahi."
3040,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sabse zyada haseen, sabse zyada data aur sabse zyada bahaadur they. unhon-ne kaha ke aik martaba raat ke waqt Madina waaley ghabraa gaey they, kyonke aik awaz sunai di thi. phir abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ke aik ghodey par jiski peeth nangii thi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) haqeeqate-haal malum karne ke liye tanha Madina k aas-paas mein sabse aagey tashrif ley gaey. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wapas aa kar sahaba (Raziallahu anhu) se miley to talwaar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki gardan mein latak rahi thi aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) farma rahe they ke ghabraaney ki koi baat nahi, ghabraaney ki koi baat nahi. iske baad Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke maine to usey dariya ki tarah paya. (tez daudney mein) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka ishara ghodey ki taraf tha."
3041,"main Madina Munawra se Ghaaba ( Sham (Syria) ke rastey mein aik maqam ( ja raha tha, Ghaaba ki pahaadii par abhi main pahuncha tha ke Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ghulam ( Ribah ( mujhey mila. maine kaha, kya baat pesh aai ? kehney laga ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki dudhail oontniyan ( doodh dene waaliyaan ( chheen li gain hain. maine puchha kis ne chheenaa hai? bataya ke qabila Ghatfan aur qabila Fazara ke logon ne. phir maine teen martaba bahut zor se cheekh kar ''yaa sabaahaa, ya sabaahaa'' kaha, itni zor se ke Madina ke charon taraf meri awaz pahunch gaee. iske baad main bahut tezi ke sath aagey badhaa, aur daakuon ko ja liya, oontniyan unke sath thin, maine un par teer barsaanaa shuru kar diya, aur kehney laga, main Akwaa ka betaa Salma hun aur aaj ka din kameenon ki halaakat ka din hai. aakhir oontniyan maine unse chhudaa lein, abhi wo log pani na peeney paaey they aur unhein haank kar wapas la raha tha ke itney main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bhi mujh ko mil gaey. maine arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! daaku piyaasey hain aur maine maarey teeron ke pani bhi nahi peeney diya. isliye unke peechhey kuchh logon ko bhej dein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, aey ibne-Akwa! to in par ghalib ho chuka ab janey de, darguzar kar wo to apni qaum mein pahunch gaey jahan unki mehmani ho rahi hai."
3042,"unhon-ne Bara-bin-Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha tha, aey abu-Amaara ! kya aap log Hunain ki jang mein waqei faraar ho gaey they? Abu-Ishaq ne kaha, main sun raha tha, Bara (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye jawab diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us din apni jagah se bilkul nahi hatey they. Abu-Sufiyan bin-Haaris bin abdul-Muttalib aap ke khachchar ki lagaam thaamey huey they, jis waqt mushrekeen ne aapko charon taraf se gher liya to aap sawari se utrey aur) tanha maidan mein aa kar) farmaney lagey mein Allah ka Nabi hon, ismein bilkul jhoot nahi. mein abdul-Muttalib ka betaa hun. Bara ne kaha ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada bahaadur us din koi bhi nahi tha."
3043,"Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya jab banu-Quraiza Sad-bin-Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) ki saalisii ki shart par hathiyar daal kar qil'a se utar aaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein ( Sad (Raziallahu anhu) ko) bulaya. aap wahin qareeb hi aik jagah thahrey huey they (kyonke zakhmi they) Sad (Raziallahu anhu) gadhey par Sawar ho kar aaey, jab wo aap ke qareeb pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, apne sardaar ki taraf khadey ho jao (aur unko sawari se utaaro ( aakhir aap utar kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb aa kar baith gaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un logon ( banu-Quraiza ke Yahudi ( ne aap ki saalisii ki shart par hathiyar daal diye hain. (is liye aap unka faisla kar dein ( unhon-ne kaha ke phir mera faisla ye hai ke unmein jitney aadmi ladney waley hain, unhein qatl kar diya jaey, aur unki aurton aur bachchon ko ghulam bana liya jaey. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tu ney Allah Taala ke hukm ke mutabiq faisla kya hai."
3044,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) fateh Makka ke din jab Shahar mein dakhil huey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sar Mubarak par khaud tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab usey utaar rahe they, to aik shakhs (abu-Barza Aslamii) ne aa kar aapko khabar di ke ibne- khatal (Islam ka badtareen dushman) Kaba ke pardey se latkaa hua hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya usey wahin qatl kar do."
3045,"Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne das sahaba ki aik jamat kuffaar ki jaasoosii ke liye bhejii, us jamat ka ameer Aasim bin umr bin-Khattab ke naana Aasim-bin-Saabit Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) ko banaya aur jamat rawaana ho gaee. jab ye log maqam Hadaa par pahunchey jo Asfan aur Makka ke darmyan mein hai to qabila huzail ki aik shaakh banu-Lahiyaan ko kisi ne khabar de di aur us qabeele ke 200 teerandaazon ki jamat unki talash mein niklii, ye sab sahaba ke nishanat qadam se andaza lagaatey huey chaltey chaltey aakhir aik aisi jagah par pahunch gaey jahan sahaba ne baith kar khajoorein khaaii thin, jo wo Madina Munawra se apne sath lekar chaley they. peechhaa karne walon ne kaha ke ye ( guthliyaan ( to yasrib (Madina ( ki) khajooron ki) hain aur phir qadam ke nishaanon se andaza kartey huey aagey badhney lagey. aakhir Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke sathiyon ne jab unhein dekha to un sab ne aik pahaad ki choti par panah li, mushrekeen ne unse kaha ke hathiyar daal kar nichey utar aao, tum se hamara ahad w paiman hai. ham kisi shakhs ko bhi qatl nahi karengey. Aasim-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) muhim ke ameer ne kaha ke main to aaj kisi sura mein bhi aik kaafir ki panah mein nahi utroonga. aey Allah ! hamari haalat se apne Nabi ko muttla kar de. is par un kaafiron ne teer barsaney shuru kar diye aur Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) aur saat (7) doosrey sahaba ko Shahid kar dala. baqi teen sahabi unke ahad w paiman par utar aaey, ye Khubaib Ansari (rz), Ibne-Dasna (Raziallahu anhu) aur aik teesrey sahabi ( Abdullah-bin Tariq balwii (Raziallahu anhu)) they. jab ye sahabi unke qaabu mein aagey to unhon-ne apni kamaanon ke taant utaar kar unko unse baandh liya, Abdullaah-bin-Taariq (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Allah ki qism ! ye tumhari pehli ghaddaar hai. main tumharey sath hargiz na jaunga, balke main to unhiin ka uswa ikhtiyar karunga, unki murad shohdaa se thi. magar mushrekeen unhein khinchney lagey aur zabardastii apne sath ley jana chaha jab wo kisi tarah na gaey to unko bhi Shahid kar diya. ab ye Khubaib aur ibne-Dasna (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar chaley aur unko Makka mein ley ja kar bech diya. ye jange-badr ke baad ka waqia hai. Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ko Haaris-bin-Aamir-bin-Naufal-bin-abd-Munaaf ke ladkon ne khareed liya, Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne hi badr ki ladai mein Haaris-bin-Aamir ko qatl kya tha. aap unke yahan kuchh dinon tak qaidi bin kar rahe, (Zohri ne bayan kya (ke mujhey Ubaidullah bin ayaaz ne khabar di aur unhein Haris ki beti ( Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ( ne khabar di ke jab ( unko qatl karne ke liye) log aaey to Zenab se unhon-ne naaf ke nichey ke baal moondney ke liye ustara maangaa. unhon-ne ustara de diya, ( Zenab ne bayan kya ( phir unhon-ne mere aik bachchey ko apne paas bula liya, jab wo unke paas gaya to main ghaafil thi, Zenab ne bayan kya ke phir jab maine apne bachchey ko unki raan par betha hua dekha aur ustara unke hath mein tha, to main us buri tarah ghabraa gaee ke Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) bhi mere chehrey se samajh gaey unhon-ne kaha, tumhen iska khof hoga ke main usey qatl kar daalunga, yaqin karo main kabhi aisa nahi kar sakta. Allah ki qism ! koi qaidi maine Khubaib se behtar kabhi nahi dekha. Allah ki qism ! maine aik din dekha ke angoor ka khosha unke hath mein hai aur wo usmein se kha rahe hain. halanke wo lohey ki zanjeeron mein jakdey huey they aur Makka mein phalon ka mausam bhi nahi tha. kaha karti thin ke wo to Allah Taala ki rozii thi jo Allah ne Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ko bheji thi. phir jab mushrekeen unhein haram se bahar laaey, taake haram ke hudood se nikal kar unhein Shahid kar dein to Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne unse kaha ke mujhey sirf 2 rakaat Namaz padh leney do. unhon-ne unko ijazat de di. phir Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) ne 2 rakaat Namaz padhi aur farmaya, agar tum ye khayal na karne lagtey ke main ( qatl se) ghabraa raha hun to main un rakaton ko aur lamba karta. aey Allah ! in zaalimon se eik-eik ko khatm kar de, ( phir ye ashaar padhey ( '' jabke mein musalman honey ki haalat mein qatl kya ja raha hun, to mujhey kisi qism ki bhi parwah nahi hai. chahe Allah ke rastey mein mujhey kisi pahlu par bhi pachhaadaa jaey, ye sirf Allah Taala ki raza hasil karne ke liye hai aur agar wo chahey to us jism ke tukdon mein bhi barkat de sakta hai jiski buti botii kar di gaee ho. aakhir Haris ke betey (Aqba) ne unko Shahid kar diya. Khubaib (Raziallahu anhu) se hi har us musalman ke liye jisey qaid karke qatl kya jaey ( qatl se pahley) 2 rakatein mashroo hui hain. idhar haadise ke shuru hi mein Aasim-bin-Saabit (Raziallahu anhu) (muhim ke ameer) ki dua Allah Taala ne qabool kar li thi ke aey Allaah! hamari haalat ki khabar apne Nabi ko dedey) aur Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apne sahaba ko wo sab halaat bata diye they jin se ye muhim do-chaar hui thi. kuffaare-Quraish ke kuchh logon ko jab malum hua ke Aasim Shahid kar diye gaey to unhon-ne ne unki laash ke liye apne aadmi bhejey taake unke jism ka koi aisa hissey kaat laaein jis se unki shanaakht ho sakti ho. Aasim (Raziallahu anhu) ne badr ki jang mein kuffaare-Quraish ke aik sardaar (aqba bin abi mueet) ko qatl kya tha. lekin Allah Taala ne bhidon ka aik chhatta Aasim ki laash par qaaim kar diya unhon-ne Quraish ke aadmiyon se Aasim ki laash ko bacha liya aur wo unke badan ka koi tukda na kaat sakey."
3046,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''qaidii ko chhudaayaa karo, bhookey ko khilaaya karo, bimar ki iyaadat karo.''"
3047,"maine Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se poochha, aap hazraat ( ahal bait (ke paas kitabullah ke siwa aur bhi koi wahi hai? aap ne iska jawab diya. us zaat ki qism ! jisne daney ko) zameen ( cheer kar) nikala (aur jisne Rooh ko paida kya, mujhey to koi aisi wahi malum nahi (jo Quran mein na ho ( albatta samajh aik dusri cheez hai, jo Allah kisi bandey ko Quran mein ata farmaai ( Quran se tarah tarah ke mataalib nikaley (ya jo us waraq mein hai. maine poochha, us waraq mein kya likha hai? unhon-ne batlaya ke diyat ke ehkaam aur qaidi ka chhudana aur musalman ka kaafir ke badley mein na maara jana (ye masayel us waraq mein likhe huey hain aur bas)."
3048,"Ansar ke kuchh logon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ijazat chahi aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap hamein uski ijazat de dein ke ham apne bhaanjey Abbas bin abdul-Muttalib ka fidya maaf kar dein, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya unke fidya mein se aik dirham bhi na chhodo ."
3049,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Bahrain ka khiraaj aaya to Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) khidmat nabwi mein hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! us maal se mujhey bhi dijiye kyonke ( badr ke mauqe par) maine apna aur Aqeel donon ka fidya ada kya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya '' phir aap ley lein '' chunanche Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein unke kapdey mein naqdii ko bandhwaa diya.
3050,wo badr ke qaidiyon ko chhudaaney Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaey (wo abhi Islam nahi laey they) unhon-ne bayan kya ke maine suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maghrib ki Namaz mein sura taur padhi.
3051,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas safar mein mushrikon ka aik jaasus aaya. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-Hawaazin ke liye tashrif ley ja rahe they) wo jaasus sahaba ki jamat mein baithaa, baatein kin, phir wo wapas chala gaya, to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey talash karke mar daalo. chunanche usey (Salma-bin-Akwa' (Raziallahu anhu) ne) qatl kar diya, aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne iske hathiyar aur auzaar qatl karne waley ko dilwaa diye."
3052,umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( wafat se thodi der pahley) farmaya ke main apne baad aaney waley khaleefa ko uski wasiiyat karta hun ke Allah Taala aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka (zimmiyon se) jo ahad hai usko wo pura karey aur ye ke unki himaayat mein unke dushmanon se jang karey aur unki taqat se zyada koi bojh un par na daala jaey.
3053,"jumerat ke din, aur malum hai jumerat ka din kya hai? phir aap itna roey ke kankariyaan tak bheeg gaiin. aakhir aap ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki bimari mein shiddat usi jumerat ke din hui thi. to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba se farmaya ke qalam dawaat laao, taake main tumharey liye aik aisi kitab likhwaa jaun ke tum ( mere baad is par chaltey raho to ( kabhi gumrah na ho sako is par sahaba mein ikhtilaf ho gaya. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke Nabi ke samney jhagadnaa munasib nahi hai. sahaba ne kaha ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( bimari ki shiddat se) hain. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke achchha, ab mujhey meri haalat par chhod do, mein jis haal mein us waqt hun wo us se behtar hai jo tum karaanaa chahtey ho. aakhir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni wafat ke waqt teen waseeyatein farmai thin. ye mushrekeen ko jazeera Arab se bahar kar dena. doosrey ye ke wufood se aisa hi sulook kartey rehna, jaisey main karta raha (unki khaatirdaarii ziyaafat wghaira) aur teesri hidayat mein bhool gaya aur Yaqoob bin-Muhammad ne bayan kya ke maine Mughira bin Abdur-Rehman se jazeera Arab ke barey mein puchha to unhon-ne farmaya kaha Makka, Madeena, Yamaama aur Yaman (ka naam jazeera arab) hai. aur Yaqoob ne kaha ke a'raj se tahaama shuru hota hai (a'raj Makka aur Madina ke rastey mein aik manzil ka naam hai)."
3054,"umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne dekha ke bazar mein aik reshamii joda bik raha hai. phir usey wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein laey aur arz kya ya Rasulullah ! ye joda aap khareed lein aur eid aur wufood ki mulaqat par us se apni zebaaish farmaya karein. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ye un logon ka libaas hai jinka ( aakhirat mein) koi hissey nahi ya (aap ne ye jumla farmaya ( usey to wahi log pahan saktey hain jinka ( aakhirat mein) koi hissey nahi. phir Allah ne jitney dinon chaha umr (Raziallahu anhu) khamosh rahe. phir jab aik din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unke paas aik reshamii jubba bheja to umr (Raziallahu anhu) usey lekar khidmat nabwi mein hazir huey aur arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! aap ne to ye farmaya tha ke ye unka libaas hai jinka ( aakhirat mein) koi hissey nahi, ya ( umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap ki baat is tarah dohraaii ke) usey wahi log pahan saktey hain jinka ( aakhirat mein) koi hissey nahi. aur phir aap ne yahi mere paas bhej diya. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke) mere bhejney ka maqsad ye tha ke) tum isey bech lo, ya ( farmaya ke) us se apni koi zarurat poori kar sako ."
3055,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath sahaba ki aik jamat jin mein umr (Raziallahu anhu) bhi shamil they, ibne-Sayyaad ( Yahudi ladka (ke yahan ja rahi they. aakhir banu-Maghaala (eik Ansari qabeeley (ke teelon ke paas bachchon ke sath kheltey huey usey un logon ne pa liya, ibne-Sayyaad baligh honey ke qareeb tha. usey ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aamad ka ( pata nahi hua. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (iske qareeb pahunch kar) apna hath uski peeth par maaraa, aur farmaya kya to uski gawahi deta hai ke main Allah ka rasool hun. ibne-Sayyaad ne aap ki taraf dekha, phir kehney laga. haan! main gawahi deta hun ke aap ummiyon ke Nabi hain. iske baad us ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha kya aap gawahi detey hain ke main Allah ka rasool hon? aap ne iska jawab ( sirf itna ( diya ke main Allah aur uske ( sachey ( anbiya par eman laya. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne malum farmaya, to kya dekhta hai? usne kaha ke mere paas aik khabar sachchii aati hai to dusri jhooti bhii. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ke haqiqat haal tujh par mushtabah ho gaee hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya ''achchha maine terey liye apne dil mein aik baat sochii hai (bataa wo kya hai?) '' ibne-Sayyaad bola ke dhuaan, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''zaleel ho, kambakht! to apni haisiyat se aagey na badh sakega.'' umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah! mujhey ijazat ho to main uski gardan mar dun lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''agar ye wahi (dajjaal) hai to tum is par qaadir nahi ho saktey aur agar dajjal nahi hai to uski jaan leney mein koi khair nahi.''"
3056,"(eik martaba ( Ubai-bin-Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ko sath lekar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us khajoor ke baagh mein tashrif laey jis mein ibne-Sayyaad maujood tha. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) baagh mein dakhil ho gaey to khajoor ke tanon ki aad letey huey Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aagey badhney lagey. aap chahtey ye they ke usey aap ki maujoodgii ka ehsas na ho sakey aur aap uski baatein sun lein. ibne-Sayyaad us waqt apne bistar par aik chadar odhey padaa tha aur kuchh gungunaa raha tha. itney mein uski maan ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekh liya ke aap khajoor ke tanon ki aad lekar aagey aa rahe hain aur usey aagah kar diya ke aey saaf ! ye iska naam tha. ibne-Sayyaad ye suntey hi uchhal padaa . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, agar uski maan ne usey yun hi rehney diya hota to haqiqat khul jati."
3057,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne sahaba ko khitab farmaya, aap ne Allah Taala ki sana bayan ki, jo uski shaan ke laaiq thi. phir dajjal ka zikr farmaya, aur farmaya ke main bhi tumhen iske (fitnon se) daraataa hun, koi Nabi aisa nahi guzra jisne apni qaum ko uske fitnon se na daraayaa ho, Nuh (Alaihissalam) ne bhi apni qaum ko us se daraayaa tha lekin main iske barey main tum se aik aisi baat kahunga jo kisi Nabi ne apni qaum se nahi kahi , aur wo baat ye hai ke dajjal kaana hoga aur Allah Taala us se paak hai."
3058,"maine Hijjatul-wada ke mauqe par arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! kal aap (Makka mein) kahan qiyam farmaaengey ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ! Aqeel ne hamarey liye koi ghar chhoda hi Kab hai. phir farmaya ke kal hamara qiyam Hanif bin kinaana ke maqam Muhassab mein hoga, jahan par Quraish ne kufr par qism khaaii thi. waqia ye hua tha ke bani kinaana aur Quraish ne ( yahin par) bani Hashim ke khilaf is baat ki qismein khaaii thin ke unse khareed w farokht ki jaey aur na unhein apne gharon mein aaney dein. Zohri ne kaha ke khaif wadi ko kehtey hain."
3059,"umr bin-Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne hanii naam ke apne aik ghulam ko (sarkaarii) charaagaah ka Hakim banaya, to unhein ye hidayat ki, aey hanii ! musalmanon se apne hath rokey rakhna (un par zulm na karnaa) aur mazloom ki baddua se har waqt bachtey rehna, kyonke mazloom ki dua qabool hoti hai. aur haan ibne- Auf aur ibne- Affaan aur un jaisey ( ameer sahaba (ke maweshiyon ke barey mein tujhey dartey rehna chahiye (yani unke ameer honey ki wjah se doosrey ghareebon ke maweshiyon par charaagaah mein unhein muqaddam na rakhna ( kyonke agar unke maweshii halaak bhi ho jaeinge to ye ruoosaa apne khajoor ke baghaat aur kheton se apna chaaraa hasil kar saktey hain. lekin giney-chuney oonton aur ginii-chunii bakriyon ka Malik ( ghareeb (ke agar iske maweshii halaak ho gaey, to wo apne bachchon ko lekar mere paas aayega , aur faryaad karega : ya ameerul-momineen! ya ameerul-momineen! to kya main unhein chhod doonga (yani unko paalnaa ( tumhara bap na ho? isliye (pahley hi se) unke liye chaarey aur pani ka intizam kar dena mere liye us se zyada aasan hai ke main unke liye soney chandi ka intizam karun aur Allah ki qasam! wo (ahal Madeena) ye samajhtey hongey ke maine unke sath zyadti ki hai kyonke ye zameenein unhiin ki hain. unhon-ne jahiliyat ke zamane mein uske liye ladaaiyaan ladiin hain aur Islam laney ke baad bhi unki milkiyat ko bahaal rakha gaya hai. us zaat ki qasam! jiske hath mein meri jaan hai agar wo amwaal (ghodey wghaira) na hotey jin par jihad mein logon ko sawar karta hun to unke ilaaqon mein aik baalisht zameen ko bhi mein charaagaah na banaataa."
3060,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''jo log Islam ka kalima padh chukey hain unke naam likh kar mere paas laao. '' chunanche ham ne dedh hazaar mardon ke naam likh kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kiye aur ham ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya hamari tadaad dedh hazaar ho gaee hai. ab ham ko kya dar hai. lekin tum dekh rahe ho ke (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad) ham fitnon mein is tarah ghir gaey ke ab musalman tanha Namaz padhtey huey bhi darney laga hai. ham se abdaan ne bayan kya, unse abu-Hamza ne aur unse Aamash ne ( uper zikr ki gaee sanad ke saath) ke ham ne panch so musalmanon ki tadaad likhi (hazaar ka zikr is riwayat mein nahi hua) aur abu-Muawia ne (apni riwayat mein) yun bayan kya, ke chh so se saat so tak."
3061,aik shakhs Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur arz kya ya Rasulullah ! mera naam falan jihad mein janey ke liye likha gaya hai. idhar meri biwi Haj karne ja rahi hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke phir ja aur apni biwi ke sath Haj kar aa.
3062,"ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik jang mein maujood they. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik shakhs ke mutaalliq jo apne ko musalman kehta tha, farmaya ke ye shakhs dozakh walon mein se hai. jab jang shuru hui to wo shakhs (musalmanon ki taraf) badi bahaadurii ke sath lada aur wo zakhmi bhi ho gaya. sahaba ne arz kya, ya Rasulullah ! jiske mutaalliq aap ne farmaya tha ke wo dozakh mein jaeyga aaj to wo badi be-jigrii ke sath lada hai aur (zakhmii ho kar) mar bhi gaya hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ab bhi wahi jawab diya ke jahannam mein gaya. Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, ke mumkin tha ke kuchh logon ke dil mein kuchh shuba paida ho jata. lekin abhi log usi ghaur w fikr mein they ke kisi ne bataya ke abhi wo maraa nahi hai. albatta zakhm kaarii hai. phir jab raat aai to usne zakhmon ki taab na la kar khudkushii kar li. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko uski khabar di gaee to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allaahu-akbar! mein gawahi deta hun ke main Allah ka banda aur uska rasool hun. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) ko hukm diya, aur unhon-ne logon mein elaan kar diya ke musalman ke siwa jannat mein koi aur dakhil nahi hoga aur Allah Taala kabhi apne Deen ki imdaad kisi faajir shakhs se bhi kara leta hai."
3063,"Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (Madina mein) Mautaa ki jang ke mauqe par khutba diya, (jab ke musalman sipaahii mautaa ke maidan mein bahaadurii dikhaa rahe they) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke ab Islami jhanda Zaid-bin-Haarisa ne sanbhaalaa aur unhein Shahid kar diya gaya, phir Jafar ne jhanda apne hath mein utha liya aur wo bhi Shahid kar diye gaey. ab Abdullaah-bin-Rawaaha ne jhanda thaamaa , ye bhi Shahid kar diye gaey. aakhir Khalid-bin Waleed ne kisi nai hidayat ke baghair Islami jhanda utha liya hai. aur unke hath par fateh hasil ho gaee, aur mere liye ismein koi khushi ki baat nahi thi ya Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya, ke unke liye koi khushi ki baat nahi thi ke wo (shohdaa) hamarey paas zinda hotey. (kyonke shahadat ke baad wo jannat mein aish kar rahe hain) aur Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke us waqt Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon se aansu jari they."
3064,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein Ra-al, Zakwaan, Usba aur banu-Lahyaan qabaayel ke kuchh log aaey aur yaqin dilaya ke wo log Islam la chukey hain aur unhon-ne apni kaafir qaum ke muqabil imdaad aur taleem w tableegh ke liye aap se madad chaahi. to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne 70 ansaariyon ko unke sath kar diya. Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya, ke ham unhein qaari kaha kartey they. wo log din mein jangal se lakdiyan jama kartey aur raat mein Namaz padhtey rehtey. ye hazraat un qabeele walon ke sath chaley gaey, lekin jab Maoona kunwey par pahunchey to unhein qabila walon ne un sahaba ke sath daghaa ki aur unhein Shahid kar dala. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aik mahina tak (namaz mein) qunoot padhi aur Ra'l w Zakwan aur banu- Lahyaan ke liye baddua kartey rahe. Qatada ne kaha ke ham se Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke (un shohdaa ke barey mein) Quran Majeed mein ham ye aayat yun padhtey rahe ''haan! hamari qaum ( muslim) ko bata do ke ham apne rab se ja miley aur wo ham se razi ho gaya hai aur hamein bhi us ne khush kya hai.'' phir ye aayat mansukh ho gaee thi."
3065,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab kisi qaum par fateh hasil hoti, to maidaane-jang mein teen raat qiyam farmatey. Rooh-bin-Ubaada ke sath us hadis ko Muaz aur Abdul-Aala ne bhi riwayat kya. donon ne kaha ham se Saeed ne bayan kya unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Anas se, unhon-ne abu-Talha se unhon-ne Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se."
3066,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne maqam Jaarana se, jahan Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne jange-Hunain ka maale-ghanimat taqseem kya tha, Umre ka ehram baandha tha."
3067,unka aik ghoda bhag gaya tha aur dushmanon ne usko pakad liya tha. phir musalmanon ko ghalba hasil hua to unka ghoda unhein wapas kar diya gaya. ye waqia Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ahade-mubaarak ka hai. isi tarah unke aik ghulam ne bhag kar Rome (mojooda Itly) mein panah hasil kar li thi. phir jab musalmanon ko us mulk par ghalba hasil hua to Khaalid-bin-Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ne unka ghulam unhein wapas kar diya. ye waqia Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke baad ka hai.
3068,"ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ghulam bhag kar Rome (mojooda Itly) ke kaafiron mein mil gaya tha. phir Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ki sarkardagi mein (Islaamii lashkar ne) is par fateh paai aur Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne wo ghulam unko wapas kar diya aur ye ke Abdullah-bin-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ka aik ghoda bhag kar Rome (mojooda Itly) pahunch gaya tha. Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) ko jab Rome (mojooda Itly) par fateh hui, to unhon-ne ye ghoda bhi Abdullah ko wapas kar diya tha."
3069,"jis din Islami lashkar ki mudbhed ( roomiyon se) hui to wo aik ghodey par Sawar they. saalaar fauj Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki taraf se Khalid-bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) they. phir ghodey ko dushmanon ne pakad liya, lekin jab unhein shikast hui to Khalid (Raziallahu anhu) ne ghoda Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko wapas kar diya."
3070,"maine ( jange-khandaq mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bhookaa pa kar chupkey se) arz kya : ya Rasulullah ! ham ne aik chhota sa bakri ka bachcha zabah kya hai. aur aik saa jo ka aata pakwaayaa hai. isliye aap 2 char aadmiyon ko sath lekar tashrif laaein. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne baa-aawaaz buland farmaya ''aey khandaq khodney waalo! Jaabir ne dawat ka khana taiyaar kar liya hai. aao chalo, jaldi chalo.''"
3071,"main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat main apne walid ke sath hazir hui, mein us waqt aik zard rang ki qamees pahney huey thi. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne is par farmaya ''san-san'' Abdullah ne kaha ye lafz habshi zaban mein umda ke matlab mein bola jata hai. unhon-ne bayan kya ke phir main mohare-nubuwat ke sath (jo aap ke pusht par thi) khelney lagi to mere walid ne mujhey daantaa, lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke usey mat daanto, phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne umme-Khalid ko (lambii umr ki) dua di ke us qamees ko khub pahan aur puraanii kar, phir pahan aur puraanii kar, aur phir pahan aur puraanii kar, Abdullah ne kaha ke chunanche ye qamees itney dinon tak baqi rahi ke zabanon par iska charcha aa gaya."
3072,Hasan-bin-Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne sadqa ki khajoor mein se (jo baitul-maal mein aai thi) aik khajoor utha li aur apne munh ke qareeb ley gaey. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unhein Farsi zaban ka ye lafz keh kar rok diya ke) كخ كخ ( kya tumhen malum nahi ke ham sadqa nahi khaya kartey hain.
3073,"mujh se Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne hamein Khattab farmaya aur khayanat ka zikr farmaya, us jurm ki holnaakii ko waazeh kartey huey farmaya ke main tum mein kisi ko bhi qiyamat ke din us haalat mein na paon ke uski gardan par bakri ladi hui ho aur wo chilla rahi ho ya uski gardan par ghoda lada hua ho aur wo chilla raha ho aur wo shakhs mujh se kahey ke ya Rasulullah ! meri madad farmaiye. lekin main ye jawab de dun ke main tumhari koi madad nahi kar sakta. main to ( Allah ka paigham ( tum tak pahuncha chuka tha aur uski gardan par oont lada hua ho aur chilla raha ho aur wo shakhs kahey ke ya Rasulullah ! meri madad farmaiye . lekin main ye jawab de dun ke main tumhari koi madad nahi kar sakta, main Allah ka paigham tumhen pahuncha chuka tha, ya (wo us haal mein aaey ke) wo apni gardan par sona , chandi , asbaab laadey huey ho aur wo mujh se kahey ke ya Rasulullah! meri madad farmaiye, lekin main us se ye keh dun ke main tumhari koi madad nahi kar sakta, main Allah Taala ka paigham tumhen pahuncha chuka tha. ya uski gardan par kapdey ke tukdey hon jo usey harkat de rahe hon aur wo kahey ke ya Rasulullah! meri madad kijiye aur main keh dun ke main tumhari koi madad nahi kar sakta, main to (Allah ka paighaam) pahley hi pahuncha chuka tha aur Ayub sakhtiyan ne bhi abu-Hayyan se riwayat kya hai ghoda laadey dekhun jo hinhinaa raha ho."
3074,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke saman w asbaab par aik sahib muqarrar they, jinka naam kar-kara tha. unka intiqal ho gaya, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke wo to jahannam mein gaya. sahaba unhein dekhney gaey to aik chadar jisey khayanat karke unhon-ne chipa liya tha unke yahan mili . abu-Adbullah (Imam Bukhari (Rahmatullahi-alaih) ( ne kaha ke Muhammad-bin salam ne ( ibne-Uena se naql kya aur) kaha ye lafz karkara hi likha hua hai."
3075,"maqam zul-Hulaifa mein ham ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath padao kya. log bhookey they. idhar ghaneemat mein hamein oont aur bakriyan mili thin. Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) lashkar ke peechhey hissey mein they. logon ne (bhook ke maarey) jaldi ki haandiyaan chadhaa din. baad mein Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke hukm se un haandiyon ko aundha diya gaya phir aap ne ghaneemat ki taqseem shuru ki das bakriyon ko aik oont ke barabar rakha ittifaq se maale-ghanimat ka aik oont bhag niklaa. lashkar mein ghodon ki kami thi. log usey pakadney ke liye daudey lekin oont ne sab ko thakaa diya. aakhir aik sahabi (khud Raafe (Raziallahu anhu)) ne usey teer maaraa. Allah Taala ke hukm se oont jahan tha wahin reh gaya. is par Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke un ( paaltu ( janwaron mein bhi janglii janwaron ki tarah kuchh baar wahshat ho jati hai. isliye agar unmein se koi qaabu mein na aaey to iske sath aisa hi karo. abaaya kehtey hain ke mere dada ( Raafe (Raziallahu anhu)) ne khidmat nabwi mein arz kya, ke hamein ummeed hai ya (ye kaha ke) khof hai ke kal kahin hamari dushman se mudbhed na ho jaey. idhar hamarey paas chhuri nahi hai. to kya ham baans ki khapchiyon se zabah kar saktey hain? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke jo cheez khoon baha de aur zabah kartey waqt is par Allah Taala ka naam bhi liya gaya ho, to uska gosht khana halal hai. albatta wo cheez (jis se zabah kya gaya ho) daant aur naakhun na hona chahiye tumharey samney mein uski wjah bhi bayan karta hun daant to isliye nahi ke wo haddi hai aur naakhun isliye nahi ke wo habshiyon ki chhuri hain."
3076,mujh se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ''zil-khalsaa (Yaman ke Kabey ( ko tabah karke mujhey kyon khush nahi kartey. ''ye zil-khalsaa( Yaman ke qabila ( Khasam ka but kada tha ( Kabey ke muqabil banaya tha) jisey Kaba al-yamaaniya kehtey they. chunanche main (apne qabeela) Ahmas ke dedh so sawaaron ko lekar taiyaar ho gaya. ye sab achchhey shehsawaar they. phir maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se arz kya ke main ghodey par achi tarah se jam nahi paata to aap ne mere seeney par hath maara aur maine Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ungliyon ka nishan apne seeney par dekha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne phir ye dua dii ( اللهم ثبته واجعله هاديا مهديا Mina padhi. . Mina فانطلق إليها فكسرها وحرقها )''aey Allah ! usey ghodey par jama de aur usey sahi rasta dikhaaney wala bana de aur khud usey bhi raah paya hua kar de. '' phir Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) muhim par rawaana huey aur zil-khalsa ko tod kar jalaa diya iske baad Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein khushkhabri bhijwaai Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) ke qaasid ( Husain bin Rabee ( ne (khidmat nabwi mein) hazir ho kar arz kya ya Rasulullah! us zaat paak ki qism jisne aapko sachcha paighambar bana kar maboos farmaya main us waqt tak aap ki khidmat mein hazir nahi hua jab tak wo but kada jal kar aisa ( siyah ( nahi ho gaya jaisa khaarish wala bimar oont siyah hua karta hai. ye sun kar Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne qabila Ahmas ke sawaaron aur unke paidal jawaanon ke liye panch martaba barkat ki dua farmai Musaddad ne us hadis mein yun kaha zil-khalsaa Khasam qabeeley mein aik ghar tha.
3077,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne fateh Makka ke din farmaya ''ab hijrat (Makka se Madina ke liye) baqi nahi rahi , albatta Husne-niiyat aur jihad baqi hai. isliye jab tumhen jihad ke liye bulaya jaey to fauran nikal jaao.''"
3078,majaashea' apne bhai majaalid bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko lekar khidmat nabwi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke ye majaalid hain. aap se hijrat par bait karna chahtey hain. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke fateh Makka ke baad ab hijrat baqi nahi rahi. haan main Islam par unse bait ley loonga.
3079,majaashea' apne bhai majaalid bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ko lekar khidmat nabwi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mein hazir huey aur arz kya ke ye majaalid hain. aap se hijrat par bait karna chahtey hain. lekin Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke fateh Makka ke baad ab hijrat baqi nahi rahi. haan main Islam par unse bait ley loonga.
3080,"mein Ubaid-bin-Umair ke sath Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. us waqt aap Sabeer pahaad ke qareeb qiyam farma thin. aap ne ham se farmaya ke jab Allah Taala ne apne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko Makka par fateh di thi, usi waqt se hijrat ka silsile khatm ho gaya tha (Sabeer mashhoor pahaad hai)."
3081,"main achi tarah janta hun ke tumharey sahib ( Ali (Raziallahu anhu)) ko kis cheez se khoon bahaney par jur'at hui, maine khud unse suna, wo bayan kartey they ke mujhey aur Zubair-bin-Awaam (Raziallahu anhu) ko Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bheja aur hidayat farmai ke rauza khaakh par jab tum pahuncho , to unhein aik aurat ( saara naam ke) milegii. jisey Haatib ibne- Balta' (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik khat de kar bheja hai (tum wo khat us se lekar aao ( chunanche jab ham us baagh tak pahunchey ham ne us aurat se kaha khat la . usne kaha ke Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey koi khat nahi diya. ham ne us se kaha ke khat khud b-khud nikal kar dedey warna ( talashi ke liye) tumharey kapdey utaar liye jaengey. tab kahin us ne khat apne nefey mein se nikal kar diya. (jab ham ne wo khat Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein pesh kya, to (aap ne Haatib (Raziallahu anhu) ko bula bheja unhon-ne ( hazir ho kar) arz kya. ya Rasulullah ! mere barey mein jaldi na farmaein ! Allah ki qism ! maine na kufr kya hai aur na main Islam se hata hun, sirf apne khandan ki mohabbat ne is par majbur kya tha. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke ashaab ( muhajireen ( mein koi shakhs aisa nahi jiske rishtedar wghaira Makka mein na hun. jinke zariey Allah Taala unke khandan walon aur unki jaaidaad ki hifazat na karaataa ho. lekin mera wahan koi bhi aadmi nahi, isliye maine chaha ke un Makka walon par aik ehsan kar dun, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bhi unki baat ki tasdeeq farmai. umr (Raziallahu anhu) farmaney lagey mujhey iska sar utaarney dijiye ye to munafiq ho gaya hai. lekin Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya tumhen kya ma'loom! Allah Taala ahale-badr ke halaat se khub waaqif tha aur wo khud ahal badr ke barey mein farma chuka hai ke ''jo chaho karo. abu-Abdur-Rehman ne kaha, Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ko usi irshad ne (ke tum jo chaho karo, khoon-rezii par) dilair bana diya hai."
3082,"Abdullah-bin-Zubair (Raziallahu anhu) ne Abdullah-bin Jafar (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha, tumhen wo qissa yad hai jab main aur tum aur Abdullah-bin-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) teenon aagey ja kar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se miley they (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jihad se wapas aa rahe they) Abdullah-bin Jafar ne kaha, haan yad hai. aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh ko aur Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ko apne sath sawar kar liya tha, aur tumhen chhod diya tha."
3083,"Saaib-bin-Yazeed (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, (jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jange-Tabook se wapas tashrif la rahe they, to ( ham sab bachchey saniiyatul-wadaa' tak Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka istiqbaal karne gaey they."
3084,"jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (jihad se) wapas hotey to teen baar Allahu-akbar kehtey, aur ye dua padhtey آيبون إن شاء الله تائبون عابدون حامدون لربنا ساجدون ، Mina صدق الله وعده ، Mina ونصر عبده ، Mina وهزم الأحزاب وحده''insha'allah ham Allah ki taraf lotney waley hain. ham tauba karne waley hain. apne rab ki ibadat karne waley hain. uski tareef karne waley aur uske liye sajda karne waley hain. Allah ne apna wada sachcha kar dikhaayaa, apne bandey ki madad ki, aur kaafiron ke lashkar ko usi akeley ne shikast de dii.''"
3085,"Asfan se wapas hotey huey ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they. aap apni ontni par Sawar they aur aap ne sawari par peechhey ( Ummul-Momenin ( Safiya-binte-Huyi (Raziallahu anhu) ko bithaya tha. ittifaq se aap ki ontni phisal gaee aur aap donon gir gaey. ye haal dekh kar abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) bhi fauran apni sawari se kood padey aur kaha, ya Rasulullah ! Allah mujhey aap par qurbaan karey, kuchh chot to nahi lagi ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''pahley aurat ki khabar lo.'' abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik kapda apne chehrey par daal liya, phir Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke qareeb aaey aur wahi kapda unke uper daal diya. iske baad donon ki sawari durust ki, jab aap Sawar ho gaey to ham Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke charon taraf jama ho gaey. phir jab Madina dikhai dene laga to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dua padhii آيبون تائبون عابدون لربنا حامدون‏''ham Allah ki taraf wapas hone-waale hain. tauba karne waale, apne rab ki ibadat karne waley aur uski hamd padhney waley hain.'' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye dua barabar padhtey rahe yahan tak ke Madina mein dakhil ho gaey."
3086,"wo aur abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, Ummul-Momenin Safiya (Raziallahu anhu) ko Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni sawari par peechhey bitha rakha tha. rastey mein ittifaq se aap ki ontni phisal gaee aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) gir gaey aur Ummul-Momenin bhi gir gaiin. abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne yun kaha ke main samajhta hun, unhon-ne apne aapko oont se gira diya aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb pahunch kar arz kya : aey Allah ke rasool! Allah mujhey aap par qurbaan karey koi chot to aapko nahi aai ? Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke nahi lekin tum aurat ki khabar lo. chunanche unhon-ne aik kapda apne chehrey par daal liya, phir Ummul-Momenin ki taraf badhey aur wahi kapda un par daal diya. ab Ummul-Momenin khadi ho gain . phir abu-Talha (Raziallahu anhu) ne aap donon ke liye ontni ko mazbut kya. to aap sawar huey aur safar shuru kya. jab Madina Munawra ke samney pahunch gaey ya rawi ne ye kaha ke jab Madina dikhai dene laga to Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye dua padhii آيبون تائبون عابدون لربنا حامدون‏''ham Allah ki taraf lotney waley hain. tauba karne waale, apne rab ki ibadat karne waley aur uski tareef karne waley hain ! '' Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ye dua barabar padhtey rahe, yahan tak ki Madina mein dakhil ho gaey."
3087,main Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath aik safar mein tha. jab ham Madina pahunchey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke pahley masjid mein ja aur 2 rakaat ( nafl ( Namaz padh .
3088,Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab din chadhey safar se wapas hotey to baithney se pahley masjid mein ja kar do rakaat nafl Namaz padhtey they.
3089,"Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab Madina tashrif laey (jange-Tabook ya zaatur-Riqaa' se) to oont ya gaaey zabah ki) rawi ko shuba hai) Muaz Anbari ne (apni riwayat mein) kuchh zyadti ke sath kaha, unse Shoba ne bayan kya, unse Mahaarib-bin-Dassaar ne, unhon-ne Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se oont khareedaa tha. 2 auqiya aur aik dirham ya ( rawi ko shuba hai ke 2 auqiya ( 2 dirham mein. jab aap maqam Saraar par pahunchey to aap ne hukm diya aur gaaey zabah ki gaee aur logon ne iska gosht khaayaa. phir jab aap Madina Munawra pahunchey to mujhey hukm diya ke pahley masjid mein ja kar do rakaat Namaz padhun , iske baad mujhey mere oont ki qeemat wazan karke inayat farmai."
3090,"main safar se wapas Madina pahuncha to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey hukm diya ke masjid mein ja kar do rakaat nafl Namaz padhun, saraar (Madina Munawra se teen mail ke faasley par mashriq mein) aik jagah ka naam hai."
